NK035(ci)001:0: g.yu yig can g.yu yig can po ti smug chung
NK035(ci)001:1: gi skor rnams bzhugs so ma yig bu yig bsdoms
NK035(ci)001:2: pas skabs don bcu gnyis dang thor bu'i skor rnams
NK035(ci)001:3: kham na / ga shwata mawaha&a&a&a sam skri ta'i skad
NK035(ci)001:4: e wam ma ya sh+ru ta e ka smin o
NK035(ci)001:5: rgyan skad b+ha du sar d+ham b+he la ki rgya
NK035(ci)001:6: nag po'i skad bee ro b+ha zha ti saka ti
NK035(ci)001:7: ko mkha' 'gro ma'i skad b+he ti b+h+ya gu lir
NK035(ci)001:8: ta sing ga la'i skad pa b+h+ya zhu ti da
NK035(ci)001:9: ros tu sog po'i skad phe ti bye la po
NK035(ci)001:10: tang ke bod skad du lo rgyus rin po che'i
NK035(ci)001:11: mdo byang bcom ldan 'das bya bral rdzogs pa nyid
NK035(ci)001:12: la phyag 'tshal lo gang zhig rmongs pa gdung ba
NK035(ci)001:13: sel ba'i don tshig dang gang zhig sems nyid rnal
NK035(ci)001:14: du 'bebs pa'i don tshig dang gang zhig rgyud lung
NK035(ci)001:15: don du 'god pa'i don tshig dang gang zhig lha
NK035(ci)001:16: rnams mngon du snang ba'i don tshig dang gang zhig
NK035(ci)001:17: skye med gding du 'dzud pa'i don tshig dang gang
NK035(ci)001:18: zhig chos sku cog gis 'jog pa'i don tshig dang
NK035(ci)001:19: gang zhig 'khrul pa thur du gzhug pa'i don tshig
NK035(ci)001:20: dang gang zhig nyon mongs sbar gyis 'dzin pa'i don
NK035(ci)001:21: tshig dang gang zhig lhag pa'i bsam gtan rdzogs pa'i
NK035(ci)001:22: don tshig dang gang zhig khams gsum g.yul ngo bzlog
NK035(ci)001:23: pa'i don tshig dang gang zhig bya byed lam du
NK035(ci)001:24: slong ba'i don tshig dang gang zhig bkod pa yongs
NK035(ci)001:25: su rdzogs pa'i don tshig rnams rnam par phye ste
NK035(ci)001:26: gsal ba 'dir ni bstan par bya'o +thii gakhamgarakan+aa&&& dab+aata
NK035(ci)001:27: rmongs pa gdung ba dag ni bsal ba'i phyir po
NK035(ci)001:28: ti smug gu la zangs kyi khyams bag tu bcug
NK035(ci)001:29: nas rgyas gdab nas sbas pa'i man ngag po ti
NK035(ci)001:30: smug chung zhes bya ste 'di la 'dra min gnyis
NK035(ci)001:31: yod de min pa la yin pa'i skad byas pa
NK035(ci)001:32: zhig kyang yod do 'di ni bse rin po che'i
NK035(ci)001:33: byang dmar la g.yu'i yi ge bris nas sog po
NK035(ci)001:34: g.yu'i smin ma can gyi yul nas bsgyur ba'o bkod
NK035(ci)001:35: pa lo rgyus rgyas 'bring gsum las 'di legs chen
NK035(ci)001:36: po'i don ni rgya che las rin chen lo rgyus
NK035(ci)001:37: mig 'bras 'dir spro'o don nyid gsang ba bsdus pa'i
NK035(ci)001:38: yi ge 'di sgra dang tha snyad bkod pa chen
NK035(ci)001:39: po las snying po 'di ni yongs su bsdus pa'o
NK035(ci)001:40: shin tu dkon pas sngon po'i g.yu yis bris gsang
NK035(ci)001:41: skor sogs gzhan dang thun mong dag tu ma byas
NK035(ci)001:42: pa 'di ni mchog tu gsang ba'i yi ge'o rgya
NK035(ci)001:43: rgya rgya rgya gar skad du b+ha du b+ha tri
NK035(ci)001:44: la bod skad du brgyud pa gsum pa sangs rgyas
NK035(ci)001:45: dgongs pas rig 'dzin brda brgyud gang zag snyan brgyud
NK035(ci)001:46: dpal gnyis med kyi rgyal po skye ba med pa'i
NK035(ci)001:47: lus can la phyag 'tshal lo 'jig rten yid ches
NK035(ci)001:48: bskyed pa mun pa'i blo dang yul can gyi ma
NK035(ci)001:49: rig mun pa'i dmag dpung gdams pa nyams len gyi
NK035(ci)001:50: gnad bzlog bya'i phyir gsang ba'i skyes bu rnams ye
NK035(ci)001:51: shes 'od kyi snang ba 'di bstan to bya rgod
NK035(ci)001:52: phung po'i ri la de nas dge slong dad dang
NK035(ci)001:53: rig mchog ldan zhu ba po sh+aa ri'i bu ste
NK035(ci)001:54: skar ma 'od bzang gis ston pa 'od srung nyid
NK035(ci)001:55: la du sku sprul pa 'di skad zhus ston pa'i
NK035(ci)001:56: mdzad spyod ji lta bu zhus pa kye kye 'jig
NK035(ci)001:57: rten mun pa snang byed pa sangs rgyas chos rdzogs
NK035(ci)001:58: chen gyi don 'di dag kyi bstan pa 'od 'bar
NK035(ci)001:59: 'di lo rgyus rin po che'i mdzod byang gis 'jig
NK035(ci)001:60: rten rigs drug mun pa sel ba'i phyir bstan pa'i
NK035(ci)001:61: ston pa dang po ji ltar byon bstan pa'i sgron
NK035(ci)001:62: ma gsang chen nges pa'i rgyud 'di rnams ji ltar
NK035(ci)001:63: bstan zhing gsungs snying po bsdus pa'i bka' gsang nges
NK035(ci)001:64: pa 'di tshig dang yi ge shad bar du yis
NK035(ci)001:65: bcad ljags la bkram pa'i theg rgyal a ti la
NK035(ci)001:66: sde dang 'bum tsho'i grangs ni ji tsam zhig shin
NK035(ci)001:67: tu bsdus pa'i thig le'i skor la bzhi yod pa
NK035(ci)001:68: las gsang ba bla na med pa 'di la snying
NK035(ci)001:69: po yang gsang la gsal ba'i tshig mtshon tsheg bar
NK035(ci)001:70: du dang ldan na bdun bdun bar bcad pa'oo shin
NK035(ci)001:71: tu thig le'i skor dkon pa gsang ba'i rgyud rgyal
NK035(ci)001:72: grags shin tu rgya che rnam par bkod pa las
NK035(ci)001:73: bsdus te gsang tig snying dang 'dra ba ru bla
NK035(ci)001:74: med phyi rgyud bcu bdun de ltar snying thig yang
NK035(ci)001:75: gab sbas pa yi mar gyi yang zhun lta bu'i
NK035(ci)001:76: rgyud gsang ba yang nas yang du bsdus par snying
NK035(ci)001:77: po 'di phyi rabs gang dang gang gis 'dzin par
NK035(ci)001:78: 'gyur mtha' ma ston pa'i bstan pa mi gnas chos
NK035(ci)001:79: gang gis byed nub pa'i tshe bstan pa'i btsas su
NK035(ci)001:80: gang gis me ro byed thig le mchog gsang bla
NK035(ci)001:81: med yongs rdzogs 'di'i bstan pa nyid la 'phel 'grib
NK035(ci)001:82: ji ltar 'byung skal dang ldan pa'i skyes bu lung
NK035(ci)001:83: rab can 'byung ba rang dengs blo ldan du zhig
NK035(ci)001:84: 'byung phung po lhag med snyigs ma rtsod ldan le
NK035(ci)001:85: los rab g.yengs pas 'di nyid goms par ma gyur
NK035(ci)001:86: gding med pa bar dor 'tshar rgya ba rang ngo
NK035(ci)001:87: bstan pa du zhig 'byung skye med rig pa'i snang
NK035(ci)001:88: ba mchog de goms par ma gyur yang 'di nyid
NK035(ci)001:89: mthong bas gar skye yon ngal bso'i sa gnas gang
NK035(ci)001:90: rmongs pa rnams kyi gdung ba bcad pa'i phyir ston
NK035(ci)001:91: pa thugs rje chen po nyid bzhengs la bdag ni
NK035(ci)001:92: don la yid ches 'jug phyir gsungs de nas ston
NK035(ci)001:93: drug pa rdo rje 'chad pa 'od srungs nyid su
NK035(ci)001:94: sprul na snang ba rnam par dag pa'i ting nge
NK035(ci)001:95: 'dzin las bzhes nas ni sh+aa ri'i bu la 'di
NK035(ci)001:96: skad gsungs kye ma tshe dang ldan pa nyon gdung
NK035(ci)001:97: ba dag ni sel ba'i tshig khyod theg chen gyi
NK035(ci)001:98: rigs min pa khyod kyis 'di dag gzung bar dka'
NK035(ci)001:99: theg pa dman la zhugs pa dang dge sbyong rtog
NK035(ci)001:100: ge ba dag gi gzugs 'dzin la skrag par 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:101: bas 'di ni rab gsang snying po'i don byang chub
NK035(ci)001:102: sems dpa' chen po yi spyod yul nyid las gzhan
NK035(ci)001:103: gyis mi de yi phyir na don 'di khyod kyis
NK035(ci)001:104: gzung ba daka'o de nas 'od bzang sh+aa ri'i bu
NK035(ci)001:105: bdag skal ba re chung snyam ste /
NK035(ci)001:106: rab tu brgyal nas 'dre ldog cing kye ma kyi
NK035(ci)001:107: hud e sha ka bdag ni 'jig rten 'khor ba'i
NK035(ci)001:108: las mi thar snyam nas rgyu dad pas rab tu
NK035(ci)001:109: mi spobs pas sdug bsngal 'ching bas dam du bcings
NK035(ci)001:110: theg chen gyi thar pa'i sa bon nyid dang bral
NK035(ci)001:111: da ni 'khor bar yun ring gnas ston pa'i thugs
NK035(ci)001:112: rje dpyangs thag mi skyob pas chad yun gyi mgon
NK035(ci)001:113: skyabs nyid dang bral kye ma 'jig rten yul 'di
NK035(ci)001:114: na mgo rkang lus sogs lha klu mi sogs su
NK035(ci)001:115: 'dod pas tshur shog tshur shog 'di longs shig khrag
NK035(ci)001:116: dang chu ser nang rol yang su 'dod su 'dod
NK035(ci)001:117: 'di longs shig de skad brjod cing lus sogs btang
NK035(ci)001:118: de ltar sdug bsngal nyid ldan pas sgrib pa zad
NK035(ci)001:119: de ston pas thugs rjes rab bzung ste nyid kyi
NK035(ci)001:120: mdzod spu'i bu ga nas bdud rtsi snang bar byed
NK035(ci)001:121: ces pa'i 'od zer rab tu spros nas ni nyon
NK035(ci)001:122: sh+aa ri'i bu'i mongs bag chags sgrib sbyangs te 'di
NK035(ci)001:123: skad thugs rje chen pos gsungs e ma rigs kyi
NK035(ci)001:124: bu nyid ni 'khor ba'i bag chags sbyang dka' ba
NK035(ci)001:125: 'di nyid du ni rab sbyangs pas da ni bstan
NK035(ci)001:126: pa'i snying po bzung 'di khyod la snang bar 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:127: ro de skad rab tu gsungs pa yis sh+aa ri'i
NK035(ci)001:128: bu ni dran rnyed nas mgo dang yan lag bral
NK035(ci)001:129: ba yang sngon du yod pa ji bzhin gyur yang
NK035(ci)001:130: ni thal mo rab sbyar nas kye kye thugs rje'i
NK035(ci)001:131: lcags kyus zungs thar pa'i lam la yang dag 'khod
NK035(ci)001:132: snang mdzad chen po a la la spros med bde
NK035(ci)001:133: chen a la la nyag gcig chen po a la
NK035(ci)001:134: la khyab brdal 'ub chub a la la nyid kyi
NK035(ci)001:135: mthu stobs 'od zer gyis bdag gi ji ltar gong
NK035(ci)001:136: zhus pa'i bcu gcig po tshig rnams ris mi par
NK035(ci)001:137: phye ste gsungs de nas nyid kyis 'di skad gsungs
NK035(ci)001:138: dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa khyod 'di nyid rab
NK035(ci)001:139: tu gzung dka' yang khyod kyi dad pa'i stobs kyis
NK035(ci)001:140: zungs zhus don dang ston pa'i byon lugs nga ni
NK035(ci)001:141: mi shigs rdo rje gzhi mi 'gyur bas las phyi
NK035(ci)001:142: rol sa chu la sogs dmigs pa gcig kyang med
NK035(ci)001:143: nang du yid g.yos rig rig ma rig pa chas
NK035(ci)001:144: 'byed med rgyud las ka dag yid kyis rlung gis
NK035(ci)001:145: phul mi rig pa rtog rtse gcig sa bon rgyu
NK035(ci)001:146: las 'phen pa'i ye shes nyid kyis bskyod mun 'khor
NK035(ci)001:147: dang snang 'das mtshams lhums su zhugs pha ni ma
NK035(ci)001:148: 'gags pa thabs cha shes rab stong pa shes rab
NK035(ci)001:149: ma lhun grub stong pa'i yul la shar de'i tshe
NK035(ci)001:150: rkyen bzhi'i 'khrul 'khor las 'dzin pa'i rgya dang bcas
NK035(ci)001:151: par gyur rlung chu me sa'i dngos po las rten
NK035(ci)001:152: dang yul gyi khyad par byung gzugs med rnams dang
NK035(ci)001:153: 'dod pa yi gnas bcu dag mtho ris ni thog
NK035(ci)001:154: mar byung gdul bya'i dang po bskal pa dga' ldan
NK035(ci)001:155: brtsegs par la skye dgu'i tshe lo dbag med dus
NK035(ci)001:156: skye bzhi'i sems can rigs rnams kyis shes pa'i rtags
NK035(ci)001:157: 'di 'dzin ba las rdzus skyes kyi sa chu 'byung
NK035(ci)001:158: ba'i dmigs rten las 'byung ba rang drod skyes pas
NK035(ci)001:159: bem po dag ni 'dod g.yos pas chu la me
NK035(ci)001:160: yi drod phebs pa'i dus bde ba skyes me la
NK035(ci)001:161: chu ste rlan gyis zhad sa la rlung g.yo ba'i
NK035(ci)001:162: cha de bzhin rlung dal gyi las las bde shar
NK035(ci)001:163: de'i tshe lus rdzu sa te dang po bem po'i
NK035(ci)001:164: gzugs gnyis rdzus skyes so rdzus nas shed bu dang
NK035(ci)001:165: shed grogs sgong skyes zer te ma yin par rin
NK035(ci)001:166: po che ni zil pa las rdzus te skyes bu
NK035(ci)001:167: gdul bya ni mi'i rgyu rkyen nyi ma rab tu
NK035(ci)001:168: snang byed dang pha'i rgyu zla ba dri med ces
NK035(ci)001:169: bya'o nga ni lta stangs ston pa yul gsum skye
NK035(ci)001:170: gnas gdul bya la gzigs dang bcas pad+ma chu yi
NK035(ci)001:171: snying po las skyes drod phebs pa me yis bde
NK035(ci)001:172: ba bzung nas 'ongs yul de shes pa drod kyis
NK035(ci)001:173: 'dren pa'i stobs kyi dga' ldan brtsegs par grags lo
NK035(ci)001:174: sa brgyad la dgongs brgyad mdzes pa'i zur phud can
NK035(ci)001:175: lnga pa rigs lnga mtshon pa kha dog dri ma
NK035(ci)001:176: med pa'i brdar dkar ba'i lus blangs so 'khor bskal
NK035(ci)001:177: pa bzang po 'di la sangs rgyas stong byung ba'i
NK035(ci)001:178: brda' ni sangs rgyas stong phrag gcig rang rang de'i
NK035(ci)001:179: bstan pa re res 'dul ba'i brdar 'dul ba'i phyag
NK035(ci)001:180: rgyar ldan 'dis 'dul ba'i gnyen po gnyis su 'byung
NK035(ci)001:181: ba'i brdar yid dang sems dang 'byung ba'i rgyu 'bum
NK035(ci)001:182: phrag dag ni drug cu bzhi 'od thig yang zhun
NK035(ci)001:183: bcu bdun ni rgyud bcu bdun nam mkhar 'od snang
NK035(ci)001:184: ye shes 'bar bstan pa'i bu gcig dgra dang bral
NK035(ci)001:185: yang tig snying po'i rtags su'o yul gyi yon tan
NK035(ci)001:186: mngon par brjod 'dod 'jo dang ni cang shes rta
NK035(ci)001:187: khrus rdzing ma btang lo thog dang lus la gos
NK035(ci)001:188: med gcer bu ni rang rang 'od dang bcas pa'o
NK035(ci)001:189: de ltar tshe lo dpag med nas brgyad khri dag
NK035(ci)001:190: gi bar dag tu stong stong gnyis las lo re
NK035(ci)001:191: bri de ltar bsod nams rab zad pas lus kyi
NK035(ci)001:192: 'od sogs rim gyi yal nyon mongs dag kyang babs
NK035(ci)001:193: kyis skye de nas tshe lo bye ba la 'byung
NK035(ci)001:194: bzhi'i sgong las skyes gzugs dag 'byung 'gro na nam
NK035(ci)001:195: mkhar bya ltar 'gro 'byung ba lnga las skyes pa'i
NK035(ci)001:196: gzugs sa rdo 'dus pa'i sha gzugs sa yi sgo
NK035(ci)001:197: nga las sha sla mgo che kha dog ser sa
NK035(ci)001:198: las skya pa'i mi drod shas me las skyes pas
NK035(ci)001:199: me las sha skam lhu gzugs phyed dmar po yan
NK035(ci)001:200: lag mched par 'byung rlung ni mang po 'dul ba
NK035(ci)001:201: mgo chung sha mdangs gnag chu'i rlangs pa 'dus pa'i
NK035(ci)001:202: zil ba las ni sngo sangs 'jigs pa'i gzugs nam
NK035(ci)001:203: mkha' yid 'dus pa'i sprin las byung ba mgo chung
NK035(ci)001:204: dkar po'i gzugs 'byung ba kun la yang lnga lnga
NK035(ci)001:205: tshang ba la shas che chung yod po'o lnga las
NK035(ci)001:206: byung ba yi sgo nga las ni skyes ba ste
NK035(ci)001:207: de tshe nga ni lta stangs yul gsum gdul bya
NK035(ci)001:208: rten 'byung lnga 'dus pa'i 'od lngas khyab pa sgo
NK035(ci)001:209: lnga ni yid dwangs ma shing zil tshul du 'od
NK035(ci)001:210: kha dog lnga ldan pa 'byung lnga rang sgra me'i
NK035(ci)001:211: sgra brlab pa chu sgra gshang ba sa sgra tig
NK035(ci)001:212: pa rlung sgra chag pa nam mkha' seng ba'o 'dod
NK035(ci)001:213: g.yos pas 'byung ba grang bas pha yi rgyu snyigs
NK035(ci)001:214: ma tsha ba las ni ma yi rkyen dwangs ma
NK035(ci)001:215: rgyu rkyen dwangs ma cha yi sgo ngar dril 'dzom
NK035(ci)001:216: nas bdag lus rdzogs lo bcu drug gzugs dang kha
NK035(ci)001:217: dog mdzes pa'i tshul du 'ongs mda' gang 'od kyis
NK035(ci)001:218: rang lus brgyan shes rab chags pa chags pas 'dul
NK035(ci)001:219: bar byed pas cha las skyes pa yi sangs rgyas
NK035(ci)001:220: pa de tsam 'byung ba'i brda mkha' 'gro'i tshogs ni
NK035(ci)001:221: 'bum tsho gnyis yul ni 'jig rten mi mjed ces
NK035(ci)001:222: 'byung ba bzhi yi dwangs ma dag sa'i dwangs ma
NK035(ci)001:223: zhag sogs zas su za zhing nyon mongs chung shing
NK035(ci)001:224: lo'i gos can dbang po med de nas lo yang
NK035(ci)001:225: rim gyis bri 'od sogs nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis
NK035(ci)001:226: dag kyang rim gyis nyams brgya bargya'am brtag brgyad brgya
NK035(ci)001:227: lon zhing nyid la lo re bri de nas tshe
NK035(ci)001:228: lo 'bum pa la de ltar 'byung lnga'i lus 'di
NK035(ci)001:229: dag las kyi rlung gis bteg nas 'dom gang gi
NK035(ci)001:230: steng du 'gro ngag las 'byung lnga nad sogs tsha
NK035(ci)001:231: grang ma snyoms pa nyon mongs kyi rgyu las byung
NK035(ci)001:232: drod dang gsher las lus gzugs grub 'byung lnga'i sa
NK035(ci)001:233: bon langs pa las me drod bsdus te chus rlan
NK035(ci)001:234: rlung gis bskyod nam mkha' 'dres gzugs ni tha dad
NK035(ci)001:235: du mar byung de tshe ston pa bdag ni drod
NK035(ci)001:236: brlan las lus bongs ldan zhing kha dog ldan sdud
NK035(ci)001:237: pa sa rlan pha rgyud rlung drod smin pa ma
NK035(ci)001:238: de ltar rgyu rkyen las skyed do thabs kyi rgyu
NK035(ci)001:239: las bskyed pa'i phyir chags med le lo can 'dul
NK035(ci)001:240: byang chub sems dpa' 'bum phrag drug 'di dag pha
NK035(ci)001:241: rgyud kyi tshim par byas rigs ldan 'khor gyi tshul
NK035(ci)001:242: du byung de tshe sems can de dag kyang ljon
NK035(ci)001:243: shing dag ni zas su'o lus 'od chags gang mun
NK035(ci)001:244: tshad mthong de nas nyon mongs bgas skyes nas drug
NK035(ci)001:245: brgya dag la lo re bzhin tshe yi lo ni
NK035(ci)001:246: khri pa dag lus kyi 'od zad nyi zla byung
NK035(ci)001:247: 'dod chags dug gi 'dod g.yos pas pho mo'i dbang
NK035(ci)001:248: po'i sgo yang 'dod gong gi drod brlan rgyu las
NK035(ci)001:249: ni khu dang khrag gi rang bzhin ni 'byung ba
NK035(ci)001:250: lnga yi gzugs can no bltas pas tshim pa lo
NK035(ci)001:251: brgya la dgod pa dag ni drug cu'i bar brgya
NK035(ci)001:252: phyed la ni lag bcangs so de nas gnyis gnyis
NK035(ci)001:253: 'khyud pa'o de las khye'u bu mo'i gzugs kun nas
NK035(ci)001:254: ras sam shing shun gyon zas su sa yi tshil
NK035(ci)001:255: zhag za ser sna'i gsog 'jog dag gis ni zhag
NK035(ci)001:256: rim blangs pas de yang nub de nas sa lu'i
NK035(ci)001:257: 'bras kyang spyad de la nga dang bdag bzung bas
NK035(ci)001:258: nga rgyal dag dang zhe sdang ste de yis zas
NK035(ci)001:259: kyang rim gyis nub stong phyed dag gis lo re
NK035(ci)001:260: bri brgyad khri dag gi dus kyi tshe bdag ni
NK035(ci)001:261: mngal skyes gzugs can te lha dbang mchog rab gtsug
NK035(ci)001:262: phud dang 'dod yum brtse ldan rgyu rkyen las bus
NK035(ci)001:263: pa dag gi gzugs su 'ong de tshe sems can
NK035(ci)001:264: de dag gi 'dod chags bzhi las byung ba'i gzugs
NK035(ci)001:265: skye ba bzhi gzugs tha dad de bardzusa nas skyes
NK035(ci)001:266: pa sa yi gzugs sgong skyes drod de me yi
NK035(ci)001:267: gzugs drod brlan sdud pa chu yi gzugs mngal skyes
NK035(ci)001:268: rlung gi gzugs su'o de ltar skyes bzhi'i lus len
NK035(ci)001:269: yang 'byung ba nyid las bskyed pa'o phal cher drod
NK035(ci)001:270: dang gsher las so thog mar 'byung bas bskyed pas
NK035(ci)001:271: na tha ma 'byung bas 'jig pa'o sum cu rtsa
NK035(ci)001:272: gsum zhes bya ba dga' dang ldan pa'i yul de
NK035(ci)001:273: ru gso bar byed pa'i sman gyi mchog skyes par
NK035(ci)001:274: byad pa sman gyi mchog skyed par byed pas gzhon
NK035(ci)001:275: nu la khyad par yid 'ong ldum ra der nga
NK035(ci)001:276: ni drug pa rdo rje 'chang byang chub sems dpa'i
NK035(ci)001:277: gzugs su 'khrungs sangs rgyas 'od srung la sogs te
NK035(ci)001:278: rab ni bdun po 'khor du'o 'bras bu gsum gyi
NK035(ci)001:279: zas zos so lha dbang brgya byin khang bzang kyi
NK035(ci)001:280: lho yi phyogs su de ltar ro lha dbang brgya
NK035(ci)001:281: byin btsun mo dang sum cu rtsa gnyis sras bcas
NK035(ci)001:282: pas nyi dang drag po yid bzhin dang lha mor
NK035(ci)001:283: bcas pa de dag gi nyon mongs zad par bya
NK035(ci)001:284: phyir 'ongs der ni bdun cu rtsa lnga lon de
NK035(ci)001:285: nas don med stong phrag bdun yang ni brtse ba'i
NK035(ci)001:286: sems skyes nas nyon mongs gdug rtsub mkha' 'gro'i gnas
NK035(ci)001:287: gsang chen rol pa'i dur khrod du gnod sbyin rak+sha
NK035(ci)001:288: seng gdong dang 'dod pa'i dbang mo'i lhums nas skyes
NK035(ci)001:289: yid khros 'jigs pa'i gzugs su byas gzhon nu dpa'
NK035(ci)001:290: bo'i stobs dang ldan 'khor ni byang chub sems dpa'
NK035(ci)001:291: bdun mkha' 'gro bu rna nyer zhi dang tshangs pa
NK035(ci)001:292: nyid ni dung gi mgrin drang srong zla 'od gzhon
NK035(ci)001:293: nu dang seng ge'i gdong can la sogs te 'di
NK035(ci)001:294: dag gdul ba'i yul du byas tshe lo drug khri'i
NK035(ci)001:295: dus su'o de nas stong du bstan pa btsugs de
NK035(ci)001:296: nas mya ngan 'das tshul ston de ltar rim pa
NK035(ci)001:297: gnyis ldan no de 'og ting 'dzin 'bum phrag gcig
NK035(ci)001:298: tshe lo stong gi dus dag du srin po bu
NK035(ci)001:299: rna'i yul du yang srin po rak+sha khro gdong dang
NK035(ci)001:300: srin mo sham sham nag mo'i bur nga ni drang
NK035(ci)001:301: srong khros par 'ongs 'khor ni srin po bye ba
NK035(ci)001:302: gcig de dag zhi ldan sems la bkod de don
NK035(ci)001:303: stong phrag gnyis kyi bar de nas mya ngan 'da'
NK035(ci)001:304: ba'i tshul stag spyang khros pa'i ri la'o ting 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:305: dag la 'bum phrag byed de nas lho phyogs 'dzam
NK035(ci)001:306: gling rgyan nyan thos rnams dang yid 'dres phyir rgyal
NK035(ci)001:307: po dza ri zhes bya ba'i khab kyi lho nas
NK035(ci)001:308: rgyang grags gcig bya rgod spungs pa zhes bya ba'i
NK035(ci)001:309: ri 'dir nga ni da lta'o tshe lo dag ni
NK035(ci)001:310: stong phyed la rigs ldan rgyal rigs bdag gi bu
NK035(ci)001:311: rgyal po seng ge bzang po dang mdzes ma 'od
NK035(ci)001:312: ldan yum gyi lhums nga skyes skyes bu lus shed
NK035(ci)001:313: can 'phongs dang sgyu rtsal kun la mkhas nyi shu
NK035(ci)001:314: rtsa lnga dag na ni nub phyogs bsags pa'i mchog
NK035(ci)001:315: rten rtsar rang gis rang byung rab tu byung kha
NK035(ci)001:316: dog ngur smrig gos gyon te nyan thos rnams kyi
NK035(ci)001:317: gdung ba bcad de nas 'di nas byang gi phyogs
NK035(ci)001:318: 'bras bu yongs su rdzogs pa yi byang chub snying
NK035(ci)001:319: po'i shing can du lo ni brgya dang nyi shu
NK035(ci)001:320: ru byang chub sesama dpa'i gdung ba bcad de 'og
NK035(ci)001:321: da lta phung po'i ris bdun cu rtsa gnyis bar
NK035(ci)001:322: du ni nyan thos byang chub sems dpa' yi gdung
NK035(ci)001:323: ba bcad phyir 'di ltar ro bram ze dag ni
NK035(ci)001:324: mtshan bzang dang dge slong ma ni pad+ma'i spyan gdul
NK035(ci)001:325: yul yon bdag 'di dag go dgra bcom bdun gyi
NK035(ci)001:326: 'khor snang ba thog ma'i sangs rgyas bdun la sogs
NK035(ci)001:327: dkyil 'khor gcig bsdus 'khor yin no da lta tshe
NK035(ci)001:328: lo sum brgya la gdul bya nyon mongs rnams bcad
NK035(ci)001:329: phyir 'od srung bsgres po zhes bya ba rgas pa'i
NK035(ci)001:330: sdug bsngal zhi bya'i phyir dge slong rdo rje 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:331: pa'o nga ni 'di nas nub byang mtshams rdo rje
NK035(ci)001:332: gdan drung byang chub gnas byang chub shing la rgyab
NK035(ci)001:333: gtad nas srod la bdud kyi dbus rnams btul nam
NK035(ci)001:334: phyed ting 'dzin mnyam bzhag nas skya rengs dag ni
NK035(ci)001:335: shar ba la nga ni mya ngan 'da' tshul ston
NK035(ci)001:336: ngas ni thog ma de ltar du bardzusa dang sgo
NK035(ci)001:337: nga drod dang brlan mngal las skyes pa'i gzugs dang
NK035(ci)001:338: ni rim pas sems can nyid dang bstun de ltar
NK035(ci)001:339: sprul nas don byas so bkod pa chen po 'bum
NK035(ci)001:340: tsho drug gi bdag nyid las dus gsum sangs rgyas
NK035(ci)001:341: dgongs pas brgyud pa'i don tshig ces bya ba rdzogs
NK035(ci)001:342: so +thii rgya rgya rgya de nas nyid kyi sku
NK035(ci)001:343: dang gsung dang thugs las byung ba'i lo rgyus zhes
NK035(ci)001:344: bya ba rnam par spros so tshe dang ldan pa
NK035(ci)001:345: khyod nyon cig nga ni bardzusa nas skyes pa'i tshe
NK035(ci)001:346: khye'u gzhon nu 'khrul med la 'jig rten nyi mas
NK035(ci)001:347: rab dga' phyir rgyud kyi rgyal po thal 'gyur te
NK035(ci)001:348: nam mkha'i mi 'byed bar snang nas ka la ping
NK035(ci)001:349: ka'i mchus bsgyur nas 'gro ba gdul phyir 'di dag
NK035(ci)001:350: bstan 'di ni bstan pa 'byung ba'i 'go nga ni
NK035(ci)001:351: sgo nga las skyes tshe sku dang gsung dang thugs
NK035(ci)001:352: kyi rgyud yon tan phrin las rgyus lnga ni 'byung
NK035(ci)001:353: ba 'gyur ba'i bar dag nas 'byung ba'i rang sgra
NK035(ci)001:354: dag gis bsgyur des ni sems can lus sogs grol
NK035(ci)001:355: nga ni drod brlan las skyes tshe dong sprugs rma
NK035(ci)001:356: bya mjing bsnol dang 'byung ba zad pa'i rgyud rnams
NK035(ci)001:357: ni bar snang gzung dang bral ba las rlung gi
NK035(ci)001:358: sgra las drangs te bsgyur 'dis ni 'dod pa'i zhes
NK035(ci)001:359: chags gcod de nas sum cu rtsa gsum gyi rnam
NK035(ci)001:360: par rgyal ba'i khang bzangs su rigs drug nyon mongs
NK035(ci)001:361: gdung bcad phyir gdung ba sel ba'i dam chos drug
NK035(ci)001:362: blo rim gnyis su snang ba'i phyir rtsol sgrub 'bad
NK035(ci)001:363: pas grol ba dang 'bad med rang sar grol ba
NK035(ci)001:364: gnyis 'bad bcas dag ni tshig gi don 'bum tsho
NK035(ci)001:365: gnyis su rnam bshad do de yang rgyas pa 'bum
NK035(ci)001:366: dang gcig bzhi khro stong phrag brgyad du bstan 'bad
NK035(ci)001:367: med yongs su bshad pa dang kun gsal dang ni
NK035(ci)001:368: rigs gsum rgyud rnam par phye ste bstan pa'o de
NK035(ci)001:369: nas dur khrod gsang chen du shes rab chags pa
NK035(ci)001:370: can dag la 'dod chags nyid kyis 'dul ba'i phyir
NK035(ci)001:371: mi yi rgyud ni bye ba gnyis chags pa can
NK035(ci)001:372: gyi don du bstan thabs kyis skyes pa 'dul ba'i
NK035(ci)001:373: phyir pha yi rgyud ni bye ba dgu skyes pa
NK035(ci)001:374: rnams kyi don du gsungs ma yi rgyud las rnam
NK035(ci)001:375: bsdus pa 'bum tsho lnga yi bdag nyid do pha
NK035(ci)001:376: las khyad par rnam bsdus pa gsang mchog bla na
NK035(ci)001:377: med pa yi bkod pa gsang ba'i rgyud rnams bstan
NK035(ci)001:378: de nas srid po'i yul dag tu rags pa 'dul
NK035(ci)001:379: ba'i rgyud bcu bstan sog po'i yul du phra rgyud
NK035(ci)001:380: bdun 'dir ni mdo sde 'bum phrag ni nyi shu
NK035(ci)001:381: rtsa lnga nyid du bstan sngags ni khri phrag gnyis
NK035(ci)001:382: su bstan lung ni khri phrag phyed dang brgyad de
NK035(ci)001:383: ltar rnam par phye ba'o zhes bkod pa chen po
NK035(ci)001:384: 'bum tsho drug gi bdag nyid las bstan pa'i chos
NK035(ci)001:385: ji ltar gsungs pa'i don tshig bstan pa ste gnyis
NK035(ci)001:386: pa'o rdzogs so rgya rgya rgya de nas rdo rje'i
NK035(ci)001:387: chen por rnam par rol pa zhes bya ba'i tshig
NK035(ci)001:388: dag rnam par spros so de ltar bstan pa'i chos
NK035(ci)001:389: rnams la shad ni brgyad kyis gcig byas pa'o brgyad
NK035(ci)001:390: 'gyur bcu phrag 'bum phrag 'gyur de rdzogs tshig rnams
NK035(ci)001:391: rnam phye bas gsal byed sgron ma'i rim pa'o stong
NK035(ci)001:392: pa nyid ni mtshon pa yi rim dang rim min
NK035(ci)001:393: phye nas bstan 'di rdzogs chos kyi 'khor lo'o zhes
NK035(ci)001:394: bkod pa chen po 'bum phrag drug pa las gcad
NK035(ci)001:395: par bya ba 'bras bu'i don tshig bstan pa ste
NK035(ci)001:396: gsum pa rdzogs so +thii rgya rgya rgya de nas
NK035(ci)001:397: nyid kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs las sde rnams
NK035(ci)001:398: par 'byed pa zhes bya ba'i tshig rnam par phyung
NK035(ci)001:399: ngo kye kye nyon cig dge sbyong khyod rigs ldan
NK035(ci)001:400: rigs bu sh+aa ri'i bu rdzu 'phrul mchog dang ldan
NK035(ci)001:401: pa nyon ngas bstan pa yi chos rnams ni sems
NK035(ci)001:402: can blo yi rim ba las che dang chung ba'i
NK035(ci)001:403: khyad par gyis rim pa gnyis kyi tshul du bstan
NK035(ci)001:404: rang rang lta dang sor bzhag go rang rang nyid
NK035(ci)001:405: ni rim pa gnyis phyin ci log dang yang dag
NK035(ci)001:406: lta log par rtogs pas 'khor la gnas yang dag
NK035(ci)001:407: pa ni rim gsum ste chung ba'i blo dang chen
NK035(ci)001:408: po la de bzhin 'bring po'i blo can la'o rim
NK035(ci)001:409: pa gsum gyi tshul du bstan chung ba'i rim pa
NK035(ci)001:410: rnam gsum ste de yi blo dang mthun pa'i chos
NK035(ci)001:411: rtog pas sbags la nyan thos te 'du shes can
NK035(ci)001:412: la rang rgyal nyid rtog 'jug can la byang sems
NK035(ci)001:413: so 'bring po gsum la bstan pa ni rab tu
NK035(ci)001:414: dman la bya ba ste dman pa rnams la spyod
NK035(ci)001:415: pa'o rnam shes can la rnal 'byor nyid chen po
NK035(ci)001:416: rim ldan gsum dag la sems yas pa la bskyed
NK035(ci)001:417: pa ste sems bcud can la rdzogs pa'o mchog gsang
NK035(ci)001:418: rab la rdzogs pa che de yi rnam par dbye
NK035(ci)001:419: ba ni 'on kyang de 'das 'og dag tu 'di
NK035(ci)001:420: ltar rnam par snang bar 'gyur yid can rnams la
NK035(ci)001:421: sems kyi sde nam mkha' can la klong gi sde
NK035(ci)001:422: rim rtsol bral la man ngag go de ltar rdzogs
NK035(ci)001:423: chen a ti la 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi
NK035(ci)001:424: las sems sde nyi shu rtsa gcig ste klong ni
NK035(ci)001:425: nyi shu gnyis yin no man ngag nyi shu rtsa
NK035(ci)001:426: gcig pa de las rgyud sde rim gsum la pha
NK035(ci)001:427: dang ma dang ma ning ngo a ti pha rgyud
NK035(ci)001:428: chen po ni bkod pa chen po gsang ba'i rgyud
NK035(ci)001:429: 'bum phrag drug pa 'di nyid do ma rgyud 'bum
NK035(ci)001:430: phrag bcu gsum la ma ning dag ni rnam pa
NK035(ci)001:431: gnyis 'dir ni pha ma ma ning gsum rnam par
NK035(ci)001:432: bsdus nas gcig tu ste de yi don tshig rnams
NK035(ci)001:433: spros pas spros bcas rnams la bzhi nyid de spros
NK035(ci)001:434: med rnam grangs bcu bdun no shin tu spros pa
NK035(ci)001:435: med pa ni rdo rje bkod pa nyid yin no
NK035(ci)001:436: rab tu spros dang bral ba la 'das rjes gsum
NK035(ci)001:437: gyis grol ba yin gal te tshig la rab 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:438: na thig le'i rgyud ni sum cu dgu 'di dag
NK035(ci)001:439: rnams ni ngas bstan pas de dag rnams la yid
NK035(ci)001:440: ches bya bco lnga gsum phyed ming rgyud la khri
NK035(ci)001:441: phrag gnyis dang stong phrag lnga thig le mchog gi
NK035(ci)001:442: rgyud rnams so khyad par mchog tu gsang ba'i rgyud
NK035(ci)001:443: bstan pa 'dzin skyong bsrung ba yi rim gsal snying
NK035(ci)001:444: dang 'dra ba'i rgyud rnam pa bco brgyad dag bstan
NK035(ci)001:445: la stong phrag dag ni bcu bdun yin bstan pa
NK035(ci)001:446: kun gyi bu gcig po brgya phrag gnyis dang phyed
NK035(ci)001:447: dang brgyad sde dang lung rab de ltar snang 'di
NK035(ci)001:448: ni mchog tu gsang ba las kun gyi spyod yul
NK035(ci)001:449: ma yin pas 'byung ba'i dgra bral sangs rgyas 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:450: 'di las sde bzhi dag tu 'phro nam mkha' nyid
NK035(ci)001:451: la 'phar ba dang sa rnams la yang thogs med
NK035(ci)001:452: 'gyur des ni sangs rgyas gdung 'dzin pa'o de ltar
NK035(ci)001:453: ngas bstan rgyud chen rnams bardzusa skyes dus kyi byin
NK035(ci)001:454: brlabs la sgong skyes thar pa'i rgyud tsam mtshon drod
NK035(ci)001:455: skyes la ni drang ba'i don mngal skyes dga' ldan
NK035(ci)001:456: yul dag tu 'ga' zhig stong par gtan la phab
NK035(ci)001:457: kha cig de bas nye bar bstan dur khrod nyid
NK035(ci)001:458: du rnam bshad pa po mo ma ning rnams kyi
NK035(ci)001:459: don sna tshogs thabs kyis mtshon nas bstan khyad par
NK035(ci)001:460: mchog gsang zab par bstan 'dir ni drang zhing 'dul
NK035(ci)001:461: bar bstan nges pa'i snying po 'ga' tsam mo srin
NK035(ci)001:462: po'i yul du zhi rgyas dbang tshar gcod don du
NK035(ci)001:463: mngon spyod bstan sog po'i yul du sems rgyud bcang
NK035(ci)001:464: de ltar rgyud rnams rab phye ba sems can rnams
NK035(ci)001:465: kyi don du ste de yi don rnams rgya che
NK035(ci)001:466: bas bstan pa'i lugs ni rnam pa gsum ji ltar
NK035(ci)001:467: skas kyi rim pa bzhin dbang po'i don du bstan
NK035(ci)001:468: pa dang 'o ma las ni mar bzhin du bsdu
NK035(ci)001:469: ba'i don du bstan pa dang tsha ba'i nad la
NK035(ci)001:470: ga bur bzhin gnyen po'i don du bstan pa'o dbang
NK035(ci)001:471: po'i don du bstan pa ni rim dgu blo dang
NK035(ci)001:472: bstun nas ni che longs dang ni zhib tshegs so
NK035(ci)001:473: bsdu ba brgyad khri bzhi stong las sde bzhi dag
NK035(ci)001:474: tu rnam par bsdus gnyen po sems can rang rgyud
NK035(ci)001:475: la nyon mongs brgyad khri bzhi stong ste de yi
NK035(ci)001:476: snying por chos kyang ngo de ltar bshad pas sems
NK035(ci)001:477: can gyi rang rgyud bcings pa dag las grol tshig
NK035(ci)001:478: gis mtshon pa'i rgyud rnams ni sde dang 'bum tsho
NK035(ci)001:479: gangs su bcad ces a ti bkod pa chen po
NK035(ci)001:480: 'bum phrag drug pa las bstan pa'i chos rnams kyi
NK035(ci)001:481: sde dang grangs gtan la phab pa ste bzhi pa
NK035(ci)001:482: rdzogs so +thii rgya rgya rgya de nas dam tshig
NK035(ci)001:483: rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:484: las langs te 'di skad ces ched du brjod do
NK035(ci)001:485: de ltar bstan pa'i snying po bkod pa'i don rgya
NK035(ci)001:486: che rab tu spros te bsdus pa dang mchog tu
NK035(ci)001:487: bsdus dang shin tu rab bsdus pas sems can blo
NK035(ci)001:488: yi gdung ba las grol te stong pa chen po'i
NK035(ci)001:489: ngang du mtshon pa'i phyir tsheg bar bdun gyis rnam
NK035(ci)001:490: par bcad pa 'di shwa lo 'bum tsho'i grangs dang
NK035(ci)001:491: tshig du bcad nyi shu brgyad la shwa lo gcig
NK035(ci)001:492: tu bstan de nyid gong nas gong du bgrangs pa
NK035(ci)001:493: yis 'bum dang bye ba sa ya rgya cher 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:494: snyigs ma dus kyi mtha' la dgos srid pas rabs
NK035(ci)001:495: bdun bstan pa smin par bya ba'i phyir tshig bar
NK035(ci)001:496: bdun gyis rnam par bcad nas bstan rgyud kyi gzung
NK035(ci)001:497: la phri gzhug mi bya'i phyir 'di ni snying po'i
NK035(ci)001:498: don du bkod pa'o zhes bkod pa chen po 'bum
NK035(ci)001:499: tsho drug pa las tshigs su bcad pa'i don bstan
NK035(ci)001:500: pa ste lnga ba rdzogs so rgya rgya rgya de
NK035(ci)001:501: nas nyid kyi rgyud rnam par 'byed pa zhes bya
NK035(ci)001:502: ba'i ting nge 'dzin las bzhengs nas yang ched du
NK035(ci)001:503: brjod pa 'di brjod do e ma ho bka' gsang
NK035(ci)001:504: nges pa'i snying po'i don rnams ni shin tu rgya
NK035(ci)001:505: che grangs su chod pa las 'bum phrag nyid ni
NK035(ci)001:506: drug cu rtsa bzhi la le'u 'bum phrag gsum dang
NK035(ci)001:507: ldan yang dag nges pa'i sar bsgral phyir rnam par
NK035(ci)001:508: bkod nas nga yis bstan de nas mchog tu bsdus
NK035(ci)001:509: pa ni khri phrag gnyis dang stong phrag lnga'o de
NK035(ci)001:510: nyid rnam par bshad pa'i rgyud bskyed dang bsdus dang
NK035(ci)001:511: gnas pa dang gsal dang byams dang nyid dang ni
NK035(ci)001:512: gsum bzhi drug dang yang gnyis dang bshad dang rdzogs
NK035(ci)001:513: dang spungs pa'o de nyid las ni shin tu gsang
NK035(ci)001:514: yang gab med pa'i gsang tshig la stong phrag dag
NK035(ci)001:515: ni bcu bdun no de don rab tu gsang ba
NK035(ci)001:516: ni babs dang rtogs par byed pa'o de don snying
NK035(ci)001:517: po'i rgyud rnams ni gnyis dang gnyis 'brel yang gnyis
NK035(ci)001:518: dang de yi yang gsum don rnams dang de ni
NK035(ci)001:519: bsdus pa gsum yin no de las rnam par rab
NK035(ci)001:520: spros pas rtsa ba brgyad kyi tshul las ni go
NK035(ci)001:521: rim 'jug phyir rnam bshad pa bskyed dang bshad dang
NK035(ci)001:522: yan lag dang lung dang man ngag dgongs pa dang
NK035(ci)001:523: 'jug dang mkhas ba cho ga yis bstan pa 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:524: dang skyong dang bsrung spros pa bco brgyad tshul du
NK035(ci)001:525: byung gu h+ya bstan pa'i bu gcig po snying po
NK035(ci)001:526: yang gsang rab tu gsang 'di dag nams ni rab
NK035(ci)001:527: tu bsdus de yi don rnams rgya cher bkod pa
NK035(ci)001:528: las snying po nges pa'i lung ni 'di dag go
NK035(ci)001:529: 'di dag rtag tu goms par gang byed pa dam
NK035(ci)001:530: pa rnams kyi gsang chen 'di yis thob a ti
NK035(ci)001:531: bkod pa chen po 'bum phrag drug pa las gsang
NK035(ci)001:532: ba snying dang 'dra ba'i rgyud rnams bsdus te rnam
NK035(ci)001:533: par bstan pa ste drug pa rdzogs so rgya rgya
NK035(ci)001:534: rgya +thii de nas lung bstan rjes su 'dzin pa
NK035(ci)001:535: zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin las bzhengs nas sku
NK035(ci)001:536: gsung thugs rdo rje bkod pa chen po las 'di
NK035(ci)001:537: skad ched du brjod do kye sh+aa ri'i bu nyid
NK035(ci)001:538: dang ldan pa 'di nyon rigs kyi bu khyod bzung
NK035(ci)001:539: nga ni 'di na mi gnas tshe phyi rabs nga
NK035(ci)001:540: yi bstan pa 'di snying po yang nas yang bsdus
NK035(ci)001:541: pa nges gsang mchog gi snying po'i rgyud 'di dag
NK035(ci)001:542: rnams kyis 'dzin par 'gyur nga ni 'di nas mi
NK035(ci)001:543: gnas nas sum brgya dang ni drug cu na nub
NK035(ci)001:544: phyogs o rgyan dag gi yul d+ha na ko sha
NK035(ci)001:545: zhes bya bar thabs kyi cha med shes rab las
NK035(ci)001:546: u pa r+aa tsa zhes pa dang snang ba gsal
NK035(ci)001:547: ba'i 'od ldan yum gnyis las bskyed pa chos kyi
NK035(ci)001:548: sde'i lhums su pha yi rgyu med zhugs chos kyi
NK035(ci)001:549: sde yi rmi lam duh shel las grub pa'i mi
NK035(ci)001:550: dkar ni gzugs dang lang tsho ldan pa zhig shes
NK035(ci)001:551: gyi bum pa 'od 'bar ba yi ge lnga dang
NK035(ci)001:552: bcas pa thogs spyi bo'i steng du bzhag pa rmis
NK035(ci)001:553: de nas dus tshod rdzogs pa la nges pa'i snying
NK035(ci)001:554: po 'di 'dzin pa'i khye'u bde ba'i bag ldan pa
NK035(ci)001:555: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs kyi sras de ming badz+ra
NK035(ci)001:556: pra he zhes mi lus rnam dag sems can 'byung
NK035(ci)001:557: des ni bstan pa 'dul ba yi thabs ni rnam
NK035(ci)001:558: pa du ma yi mdzad pa dag ni spros byas
NK035(ci)001:559: nas lo ni sum cu rtsa gnyis na nga yis
NK035(ci)001:560: bstan pa'i chos rnams ni ma la ya yi rtse
NK035(ci)001:561: mo la rdo rje dbyings kyi mkha' 'gro ma 'jig
NK035(ci)001:562: rten bde ba'i ro can dang bde byed ser mo
NK035(ci)001:563: zhes bya ba bas tshig dang yi ger 'god par
NK035(ci)001:564: 'gyur rang byung dag gi yi ge ni bstan pa
NK035(ci)001:565: kun gyi bu gcig po de nas rjes 'jug sprul
NK035(ci)001:566: pa de bsil ba tshal gyi dur khrod du shes
NK035(ci)001:567: rab kyis ni gdul bya la bstan pa dam pa
NK035(ci)001:568: 'di nyid ston de tshe nub phyogs rim gnyis grong
NK035(ci)001:569: bram ze legs ldan ston pa dang snang ba'i sgron
NK035(ci)001:570: ma'i yum lhums su zhugs te skal ldan rjes 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:571: pa de ming many+dzu sh+r+ai pra ti rig pa'i gnas
NK035(ci)001:572: rnams kun sbyangs pa skyes bu nyid ni mchog de
NK035(ci)001:573: la 'jam dpal gyis ni lung bstan nas bstan pa
NK035(ci)001:574: dam pa 'di la gzung sprul pa po ni lo
NK035(ci)001:575: brgya dgu de tshe rjes 'jug de dang 'phrad de
NK035(ci)001:576: yang shes pa'i rgyud dag nas shel kyi gong bu
NK035(ci)001:577: bzhin du 'gyur 'di ltar 'bum tsho'i dbye ba dang
NK035(ci)001:578: bsdus dang rgyas dang rab rgyas su rnam par phye
NK035(ci)001:579: nas ston pa'o de nas bdun cu rtsa lnga na
NK035(ci)001:580: de yang mya ngan 'da' tshul ston chu bo dan
NK035(ci)001:581: tig ces bya'i mgor zag bcas phung po nyid dang
NK035(ci)001:582: bral nam mkha' 'od phung gis bkang ste gdung ba
NK035(ci)001:583: bcad phyir zhal chems so de nas rjes 'jug many+dzu
NK035(ci)001:584: des bstan pa kun gyi snying po 'di rdo rje
NK035(ci)001:585: gdan du sbed par 'byung de dus man ngag sde
NK035(ci)001:586: gnyis su de nyid kyis ni rnam par 'byed so
NK035(ci)001:587: sa gling gi dur khrod du rjes 'jug de nyid
NK035(ci)001:588: nyams su len bstan pa'i snying po 'di ston 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:589: de lo brgya dang rtsa dgu na rgya nag ko
NK035(ci)001:590: sha'i gling zhes par khyim bdag dge ldan yid can
NK035(ci)001:591: dang snang gsal mkhyen ma bya ba'i yum gnyis kyi
NK035(ci)001:592: rgyu rkyen las 'khrungs pa'i de ming dpal gyi seng
NK035(ci)001:593: ge zhes mkhas pa sbyangs pa'i don ldan pa'i skal
NK035(ci)001:594: ldan skyes bu de nyid la spyan ras gzigs kyis
NK035(ci)001:595: lung bstan nas brgya dang sum cu rtsa gnyis na
NK035(ci)001:596: many+dzu nyid dang 'dzom par 'gyur de yang sngon sbyangs
NK035(ci)001:597: skal ldan pas shel gyi gong bu bzhin du 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:598: de nas nyi shu rtsa lnga na many+dzu mya ngan
NK035(ci)001:599: 'da' tshul ston 'byung ba dag ni rang dengs su
NK035(ci)001:600: nam mkha' 'od kyi phung por gyur gdung ba bcad
NK035(ci)001:601: phyir zhal chems so sgra dang bcas te lung bstan
NK035(ci)001:602: thob de nas bstan pa'i snying po ni skal dang
NK035(ci)001:603: ldan pa des khyer nas rgya nag yul du snang
NK035(ci)001:604: bar 'gyur byang chub 'byung ba'i shing drung du dgongs
NK035(ci)001:605: pa rtse gcig don chod nas rigs bzhi dag tu
NK035(ci)001:606: nges 'byed 'gyur sde gsum don rnams gter sped 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:607: yang gab gsang ba snying thig 'di bkra shis khri
NK035(ci)001:608: sgo zhes byar sbed des ni lo brgya nyi shu
NK035(ci)001:609: lo na dgongs pa dag la rab tu gnas de
NK035(ci)001:610: tshe rgya gar nub phyogs yul glang po sgang zhes
NK035(ci)001:611: rgyud rings par khyim ba dag de ni dge ldan
NK035(ci)001:612: las rab tu rgyu dang rkyen las 'khrungs de ming
NK035(ci)001:613: phyag rgya rgya chen dang shar phyogs ka ma sh+ai
NK035(ci)001:614: la'i grong gdol pa shan ting lag pa dang dge
NK035(ci)001:615: ba'i sems can yum gyi lhums rgyu dang rkyen las
NK035(ci)001:616: 'khrungs pa yi de ming dz+ny+aa na s+au tra zhes
NK035(ci)001:617: de gnyis sbyangs pa'i yon tan rdzogs de dus rdo
NK035(ci)001:618: rje gdan nyid na pan+di ta ni lnga brgya bzhugs
NK035(ci)001:619: de dag rnams las mchog tu mkhas ye shes mdo
NK035(ci)001:620: dang bye ma lar nub phyogs 'dam bu'i tshal zhes
NK035(ci)001:621: par rdo rje sems dpa' lung ston 'gyur sing ha
NK035(ci)001:622: nyid dang zhal 'phrad de des kyang dam pa'i don
NK035(ci)001:623: rnyed 'gyur yang gsang snying po'i bstan pa 'di dz+ny+aa
NK035(ci)001:624: na s+au tra skal ldan par de yi slob mar
NK035(ci)001:625: de 'gyur ro de nas lo na bcu bdun na
NK035(ci)001:626: de yang mya ngan 'da' tshul ston 'byung ba dag
NK035(ci)001:627: ni rang deng su nam mkha' 'od kyis bka' ste
NK035(ci)001:628: 'gro gdung ba dag ni bcad pa'i phyir bstan pa'i
NK035(ci)001:629: btsas su zhal chems so skal pa nyid dag rab
NK035(ci)001:630: ldan pa'i ye shes mdo ni b+ha seng du mkha'
NK035(ci)001:631: 'gro'i gdung ba gcod par 'gyur mkha' 'gro ma yis
NK035(ci)001:632: lung bstan nas mu dra nyid kyang skal ldan 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:633: gnyis kyis lo ni brgya dang gsum de nas lo
NK035(ci)001:634: lnga'i bar du gnas skal ldan mchog de rang dengs
NK035(ci)001:635: su nam mkha' 'od snang de bzhin no gdung ba
NK035(ci)001:636: bcad phyir zhal chems so phyag rgya rgya chen zhes
NK035(ci)001:637: bya ba'i mkhas pa mchog de kam rur gnas de
NK035(ci)001:638: nas dur khrod rab snang du dgongs la gnas shing
NK035(ci)001:639: spyod pa skyong de dus b+ho ta'i rgyal khams su
NK035(ci)001:640: rgyal po byang chub sems dpa'i rigs sprul pa phyag
NK035(ci)001:641: brnyan bcas pa 'byung de yis bstan pa'i snying po
NK035(ci)001:642: 'di bi ma la dang skal ldan par gyur nas
NK035(ci)001:643: snying po'i don 'di ni rab tu gsang zhing 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:644: par gyur mu dra nyid ni rgya nag yul b+he
NK035(ci)001:645: la sha kra zhes bya bar de nas snang ste
NK035(ci)001:646: skye shi bral 'di nyid mya ngan 'da' ba min
NK035(ci)001:647: de nas lnga bcu rtsa lnga na de yi phyag
NK035(ci)001:648: brnyan dge slong gzugs rang rgyud rnam par dag nas
NK035(ci)001:649: ni b+hi la ki zhes bya ba yi gtsugs lag
NK035(ci)001:650: khang du sped par 'gyur lo brgya'i bar du der
NK035(ci)001:651: gnas te de 'og dge slong dad brtson ldan de
NK035(ci)001:652: dang 'phrad nas bskal ldan 'gyur de nas lo ni
NK035(ci)001:653: bco lnga na yang ni dge sbyong gzugs 'dzin pa
NK035(ci)001:654: skal ldan de la snang bar 'gyur des ni shing
NK035(ci)001:655: ldan ri rgyud las bstan pa dam pa 'di sbed
NK035(ci)001:656: 'gyur de nas lo ni sum cu na pan+di ta
NK035(ci)001:657: ni gnas dum zhes des ni sde gnyis dag la
NK035(ci)001:658: sprod de nas lo ni brgya phyed na bstan pa
NK035(ci)001:659: yang gsang nges pa yi don rgyud man ngag gsang
NK035(ci)001:660: tig 'di sa la gnas pa gcig gis spyod de
NK035(ci)001:661: yi rjes 'dzin slob ma ni lag na rdo rje'i
NK035(ci)001:662: sprul pa po 'dis ni bstan pa dar bar 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:663: de nas de dag 'das 'og tu dge sbyong dag
NK035(ci)001:664: gis gzugs 'dzin pa lus nag yan lag rags pa
NK035(ci)001:665: yis bstan pa 'di ni bzung ba'i tshe dam chos
NK035(ci)001:666: 'di ni lo brgya ru 'di dag rnams ni nub
NK035(ci)001:667: par 'gyur de nas yang ni bod yul du rgyal
NK035(ci)001:668: po dge ba'i sems ldan pa kha dog dmar po
NK035(ci)001:669: gser gyi so rigs ldan 'khor g.yog ldan pas ni
NK035(ci)001:670: bstan pa'i me ro slong nas ni mkhas pa lce
NK035(ci)001:671: yi rdzu 'phrul can zhig gis yi ge'i brda bsgyur
NK035(ci)001:672: te 'di nyid me lce 'bar ba bzhin bstan pa'i
NK035(ci)001:673: snying po lo stong du yo gi yo gi'i gzugs
NK035(ci)001:674: dag gis rim nas rim gyis 'dzin par 'gyur de
NK035(ci)001:675: nas lo ni nyis brgya na yang ni rgyal po
NK035(ci)001:676: bongs chung ba mgo la ral gri'i chun po 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:677: 'di dang 'phrad nas mun par 'gyur de nas dge
NK035(ci)001:678: slong dpal dang ldan bram ze dag gi rigs mchog
NK035(ci)001:679: gis kha che'i yul nas 'di rnyed nas de nyid
NK035(ci)001:680: yul du bstan pa 'di spang la me mched bzhin
NK035(ci)001:681: du ste snying po lo brgya'i bar du gnas de
NK035(ci)001:682: nas lo ni sum cu ru yang ni rgyal po
NK035(ci)001:683: snying stobs can de dang 'phrad nas mun par 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:684: de nas nub phyogs o rgyan yum gling dang ldan
NK035(ci)001:685: pa zhes bya bar mkha' 'gro dpal 'dzin zhes bya
NK035(ci)001:686: bas rgya mtsho'i gling nas phyung nas ni yang ni
NK035(ci)001:687: bstan pa dar bar byed de nas rim dang rim
NK035(ci)001:688: gyis ni skal dang ldan pa'i skyes bu ni don
NK035(ci)001:689: dam rim pa nyid ldan 'gyur tshe lo bcu pa'i
NK035(ci)001:690: dus dag tu 'dis ni sgron ma 'bar bar byed
NK035(ci)001:691: de nas bstan pa'i snying po rnams nam mkha' dag
NK035(ci)001:692: la 'phar bar 'gyur bstan pa kun gyi bu gcig
NK035(ci)001:693: po 'byung ba'i sgra dang bral ba'i phyir rdo rje
NK035(ci)001:694: gdan nas me ro byed ces a ti bkod pa
NK035(ci)001:695: chen po 'bum phrag drug pa las phyi rabs skal
NK035(ci)001:696: pa dang ldan pa'i gang zag ji lta bu 'byung
NK035(ci)001:697: ba lung bstan pa ste bdun pa rdzogs so rgya
NK035(ci)001:698: rgya rgya de nas nyid kyi sku dang gsung dang
NK035(ci)001:699: thugs dang yon tan dang phrin las mi zad pa
NK035(ci)001:700: rgyan gyi 'khor lo las 'di dag phyungs te rnam
NK035(ci)001:701: par spros so nyon cig dge sbyong rdo rje yang
NK035(ci)001:702: 'dzin pa 'di ni sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang rdo
NK035(ci)001:703: rje theg par rab grags pa khyad par chen po'i
NK035(ci)001:704: chos rnams ni 'jig rten bkod pa'i zhing khams 'dir
NK035(ci)001:705: bstan pa dag ni gnas mi gnas ye thog dang
NK035(ci)001:706: po'i sangs rgyas dang dam pa stong gi dkyil 'khor
NK035(ci)001:707: 'dus de nas bstan pa gnyis pa la spyi phud
NK035(ci)001:708: 'jig rten mgon zhes pas dam pa stong gis 'di
NK035(ci)001:709: phyag mdzad bstan pa dag ni gsum pa la tshangs
NK035(ci)001:710: pa stong gi spyi phud mgon sangs rgyas stong gi
NK035(ci)001:711: thugs nyid dril de nas bstan pa bzhi pa la
NK035(ci)001:712: nyi ma stong gi rgyal po dang sangs rgyas stong
NK035(ci)001:713: gi mnga' dbang bskur bstan pa nyid ni lnga pa
NK035(ci)001:714: la 'jig rten dra ba mgon zhes pa'i dam pa
NK035(ci)001:715: stong gi thugs la sbas bstan pa drug gi sangs
NK035(ci)001:716: rgyas ni 'od zer stong gi mu khyud mgon rigs
NK035(ci)001:717: can stong gis 'di nyid sbas de nas bstan pa
NK035(ci)001:718: bdun pa la ye khyab 'khor 'jig tshangs pa'i mgon
NK035(ci)001:719: bde chen stong gi spyi bor bzung de lta de
NK035(ci)001:720: ltar bstan pa ni 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi
NK035(ci)001:721: ru sangs rgyas grags ni de nyid kyis gsang chen
NK035(ci)001:722: 'di ni yongs bzung ba'o bstan pa'i sangs rgyas nges
NK035(ci)001:723: pa yi sa ya phrag ni bcu dgu yis 'di
NK035(ci)001:724: nyid phyag mdzad bcud dril ba'o de phyir bstan pa'i
NK035(ci)001:725: sa bon ni nges pa'i snying po zhes bya ba
NK035(ci)001:726: bstan pa kun gyi bu gcig bu 'byung ba lnga
NK035(ci)001:727: yi dgra dang bral rang byung dag gi yi ge
NK035(ci)001:728: ni gang gi rkyen gyis 'jig pa med nyi ma
NK035(ci)001:729: spungs pa'i sgron ma 'dis sangs rgyas kun gyi sa
NK035(ci)001:730: bon 'debs ston pa dag ni re re'o bstan pa
NK035(ci)001:731: dag ni nub pa'i tshe 'di na ston pa gang
NK035(ci)001:732: 'byung ba'i sngon du lo brgya'i dang po la 'byung
NK035(ci)001:733: ste sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud 'di nyid las ni
NK035(ci)001:734: 'phro bar 'gyur 'di nyid gang gis bzung ba de
NK035(ci)001:735: bzo dang sgyu rtsal thams cad dang bstan bcos kun
NK035(ci)001:736: dang sgra rnams ni ji ltar 'dod bzhin shes par
NK035(ci)001:737: 'gyur gsang mchog bla na med pa de mchod dang
NK035(ci)001:738: bstod dbang bskur byas na mchog dang thun mong dngos
NK035(ci)001:739: grub rnams ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du 'byung 'di
NK035(ci)001:740: nyid bcangs pa tsam gyis ni lung dang man ngag
NK035(ci)001:741: 'dzin par 'gyur 'jig rten mun sel nor bu'i 'od
NK035(ci)001:742: snang bar byed pa'i sgron ma 'di gang la snang
NK035(ci)001:743: bar gyur pa de de ni 'byung ba ra dengs
NK035(ci)001:744: su skal ldan 'gyur bar the tshom med ces a
NK035(ci)001:745: ti bkod pa chen po 'bum phrag drug pa las
NK035(ci)001:746: bstan pa'i snying po byung khungs bstan pa te brgyad
NK035(ci)001:747: pa rdzogs so rgyargya rgya de nas yang nyid kyi
NK035(ci)001:748: sku gsung thugs las 'di dag byung ngo kye kye
NK035(ci)001:749: nyon cig rig ldan sh+aa ri'i bu bstan pa'i dam
NK035(ci)001:750: pa rgya che rab bkod las mchog tu snying po
NK035(ci)001:751: yang nas yang bsdus pa gser gyi snying po nyi
NK035(ci)001:752: ma snang bya 'di thun mong 'chol bar dar ba
NK035(ci)001:753: ma yin te gsang chen rigs dang ldan pa 'gal
NK035(ci)001:754: la 'byung snyigs ma rtsod ldan nyon mongs rags pa'i
NK035(ci)001:755: dus sde pa nang 'thab dben gnas kun kyang 'jig
NK035(ci)001:756: rgyal khrims mi gnas rang dga' 'dod rgyal spyod pha
NK035(ci)001:757: dang bu 'thab mtshon gyis lus rnams bsrung bsags pa'i
NK035(ci)001:758: tshogs yal sa yi bcud rnams zad mi mthun lta
NK035(ci)001:759: spyod dag kyang grangs mang 'byung snyigs ma lnga brgya
NK035(ci)001:760: tshe lo rim gyis bri bsod nams skal chung tshe
NK035(ci)001:761: lo drug cu'o tshe snying po 'di ni lo ni
NK035(ci)001:762: drug cur gnas de nas 'og tu lo brgya'i bar
NK035(ci)001:763: du ni rtog ge dpyod cing gsang ba 'di mi
NK035(ci)001:764: gnas de 'das 'og tu lo stong nyid du yang
NK035(ci)001:765: thos bsam bral ba'i gang zag yal nas ni gsang
NK035(ci)001:766: ba mchog 'di nyi ma bzhin du 'gyur de 'das
NK035(ci)001:767: 'og tu nyis brgya mun par 'gyur de nas tshe
NK035(ci)001:768: lo dag ni bzhi bcu na snying po 'di ni
NK035(ci)001:769: lo brgya'i bar du gnas de 'das sum cu'i bar
NK035(ci)001:770: du mun par 'gyur de 'og lo brgya'i bar du
NK035(ci)001:771: gnas pa la de 'das tshe lo sum cu'i dus
NK035(ci)001:772: na 'di nub nas rgyang 'phen lo brgya'i bar du
NK035(ci)001:773: dar de nas yang ni lo bcu'i bar du gnas
NK035(ci)001:774: tshe lo nyi shu pa la 'di mi 'byung bcu
NK035(ci)001:775: pa'i dus su snying po 'di 'byung bas 'di dang
NK035(ci)001:776: gang 'phrad 'byung ba rang gdengs 'gyur de nas yal
NK035(ci)001:777: te mi snang bstan pa'i btsas yang ni bstan pa'i
NK035(ci)001:778: me ro bzhin du 'gyur zhes bkod pa chen po
NK035(ci)001:779: 'bum phrag drug pa las bstan pa dam pa'i 'phel
NK035(ci)001:780: 'grib ji ltar 'byung ba ste zhus don dgu ba
NK035(ci)001:781: rdzogs so rgya rgya rgya de nas yang sku'i 'od
NK035(ci)001:782: zer rnam par spros te 'di skad ces rngams par
NK035(ci)001:783: bsgrags so nyon cig rigs ldan dge spyod dpal nga
NK035(ci)001:784: ni 'di nas mi gnas nas tshe lo drug cu
NK035(ci)001:785: yan chad la 'bras bu grol ba stong phrag gcig
NK035(ci)001:786: 'byung ba rang dengs dag tu ste dge sbyong gzugs
NK035(ci)001:787: ni de yi phyed lhag ma byang chub sems dapa'o
NK035(ci)001:788: de nas lnga bcu la thug bar 'byung bar rang
NK035(ci)001:789: sar dengs pa ni 'bum phrag gnyis kyis skye med
NK035(ci)001:790: thob phal cher bud med dag gi gzugs skyes ba
NK035(ci)001:791: dag ni stong phra gnyis de nas tshe lo sum
NK035(ci)001:792: cu'i bar 'bum phrag dag ni drug pa ste 'di
NK035(ci)001:793: dag phal cher skyes pa bud med gzugs ni 'bum
NK035(ci)001:794: gcig yin 'byung ba dag ni rang dengs so de
NK035(ci)001:795: dag sngon byung nga yi 'khor snyigs ma'i dus na
NK035(ci)001:796: sangs rgyas thob nges gsang snying po yang bsdus pa'i
NK035(ci)001:797: 'bras bu nyid ni thob pa las bstan pa gzhan
NK035(ci)001:798: gyi 'bras bu min gal te bstan pa gzhan dag
NK035(ci)001:799: la mngon par sangs rgyas 'byung 'dod na 'di nyid
NK035(ci)001:800: phrad de de bzhin no de phyir 'bras bu'i dus
NK035(ci)001:801: ka ruh 'di nyid dag tu bstan pa'o zhes bkod
NK035(ci)001:802: pa chen po 'bum phrag drug pa las nges pa'i
NK035(ci)001:803: 'bras bu thob pa 'byung ba rang dengs su song
NK035(ci)001:804: ba'i grangs lung bstan pa ste bcu pa rdzogs so
NK035(ci)001:805: rgya rgya rgya de nas yang nyid kyi thugs kyi
NK035(ci)001:806: dal nas mgur gyi bum par dril ljags kyi dbang
NK035(ci)001:807: po la bkram nas ched du brjod pa 'di dag
NK035(ci)001:808: brjod do e ma gsang ba'i gsang mchog nges pa'i
NK035(ci)001:809: snying po 'dis 'khor bar brgyud pa'i bag chags kun
NK035(ci)001:810: bcad nas ye shes mdzod kyi snang ba rab bstan
NK035(ci)001:811: te snyigs ma'i yang snyigs tshe lo sum cu la
NK035(ci)001:812: le los g.yengs nas de 'das 'og tu ni skye
NK035(ci)001:813: gnyis bar du mngon par sangs rgyas pa tshe lo
NK035(ci)001:814: bcu pa'i bar la 'di rnams 'byung stong phrag bdun
NK035(ci)001:815: ni snang ba ma dang phrad skyes pa dag ni
NK035(ci)001:816: stong phrag drug nyid la bud med gzugs ni stong
NK035(ci)001:817: phrag gcig yin no de ltar skyes dang bud med
NK035(ci)001:818: khyi dang mo ji ltar gyur pa'i gzugs su 'dug
NK035(ci)001:819: kyang sla'i 'di dang phrag pa rnam par gro ba'o
NK035(ci)001:820: gzhan gyi rigs las byung yang 'di nyid du des
NK035(ci)001:821: na gsang mchog nges pa'i snying po 'di gzhan gyi
NK035(ci)001:822: yul min skal ldan shugs kyis phrad bde gsal snying
NK035(ci)001:823: po'i don du 'di bkod pa'o zhes bkod pa chen
NK035(ci)001:824: po 'bum phrag drug pa las skye gnyis mtshams su
NK035(ci)001:825: sangs rgyas pa 'byung bar lung bstan pa ste bcu
NK035(ci)001:826: gcig pa rdzogs so rgya rgya rgya de nas yang
NK035(ci)001:827: ting nge 'dzin seng ge rnam par rol pa zhes
NK035(ci)001:828: bya ba las bzhengs nas yang ched du brjod pa
NK035(ci)001:829: 'di dag gsang ba'i snying po 'di rnams mi yul
NK035(ci)001:830: du snang ba rnam par brjod do snyigs ma lnga
NK035(ci)001:831: brgya tshe lo drug cu pa'i dus nas dus kyi
NK035(ci)001:832: tha ma la gsang ba'i snying po chos 'di ni
NK035(ci)001:833: mi yul snang de rjes 'dzin pa'i gang zag skal
NK035(ci)001:834: ba can snying po 'di ni su la snang gyur
NK035(ci)001:835: pa de dag rnams ni mi 'gyur sa la 'da'
NK035(ci)001:836: mya ngan las gal te snyigs mar tshe thung nad
NK035(ci)001:837: mang bas snying po'i don 'di goms pa chung bas
NK035(ci)001:838: gding du ma gyur kyang 'di nyid kyi ngo sprod
NK035(ci)001:839: mthong bas 'khor ba las dbugs chen nyid 'byin pa
NK035(ci)001:840: bcu gcig kun pha rol tu phyin pa ltar na
NK035(ci)001:841: tu 'od de sprul pa'i zhing rdzu skyes dag pa
NK035(ci)001:842: mnga' gyi rgya dang bral shar phyogs mngon dga' mi
NK035(ci)001:843: 'gyur rdo rje'i zhing mi bskyod ston pas 'khor gyi
NK035(ci)001:844: chos 'di bstan pas rgyu grol gdul bya rang snang
NK035(ci)001:845: yon tan bsam mi khyab ste sa bcu gsum /
NK035(ci)001:846: lho dpal dang ldan dang nub pad+ma brtsegs pa dang
NK035(ci)001:847: las rab byang nyid ni yongs su rdzogs pa'i zhing
NK035(ci)001:848: rin chen 'byung dang pad+ma gar dbang rta ston pa'i
NK035(ci)001:849: bstan pas 'khor gyi shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyong shar
NK035(ci)001:850: dkar lho ser nub dmar dang byang ljang gu'i kha
NK035(ci)001:851: dog gsal mtho dman med pas khod snyoms yod 'ong
NK035(ci)001:852: ri skeg sogs bya skad sna tshogs sgrogs dri bsung
NK035(ci)001:853: ngad 'jam lta bas chog mi shes dbang po tshim
NK035(ci)001:854: byed yon tan kun dang ldan kha dog lus rdzogs
NK035(ci)001:855: zas gos dus gcig rdzogs lus kyi rtsol bral las
NK035(ci)001:856: kyi rlung gis bskyod nas bar snang la 'gro dang
NK035(ci)001:857: 'dug 'byung bas ma bskyed pa'i gnad kyis rlung mkhris
NK035(ci)001:858: bad kan 'dus pa'i nad rnams med yan lag brgyad
NK035(ci)001:859: ldan ro brgya 'dus pa'i chu 'thungs pas lus sems
NK035(ci)001:860: tshim byed reg na lus kyang 'jam sa chu me
NK035(ci)001:861: rlung 'byung bas phan gnod bral bkres yid la 'dod
NK035(ci)001:862: pa'i dang skom dang tsha grang sdug bsngal med 'dod
NK035(ci)001:863: chags zhe sdang gti mug nyon mongs rnams skye ba'i
NK035(ci)001:864: rgyu med shes pa bag yangs so blta dgod lag
NK035(ci)001:865: bcangs gnyis 'khyud 'dod chags med chog shes sred bral
NK035(ci)001:866: rtag tu chos la nyan sgrib gnyis bral nas skye
NK035(ci)001:867: ba gcig gis thogs mchod pa'i lha mos yid 'ong
NK035(ci)001:868: bkra shis brjod gzhal yas khang mdzes sgo bzhi rta
NK035(ci)001:869: babs ldan shel dkar dang gser ser dang mar dmar
NK035(ci)001:870: ljang gad an+d+ra sngo n+ai la bkra phyogs rnams shis
NK035(ci)001:871: gdugs dang 'khor lo rgyal mtshan mdzes de ltar phyogs
NK035(ci)001:872: bcu rang bzhin sprul pa'i zhing rang rang ston pas
NK035(ci)001:873: rang rang 'khor rgyun 'grol mdun gyi nam mkha' mi
NK035(ci)001:874: 'byed brtsegs pa na 'jigs pa'i khro gnas dur khrod
NK035(ci)001:875: me ri 'bar 'jigs pa'i sgra h+aum phata sogs dang
NK035(ci)001:876: khro gzugs a la la 'di nyid mthong ba tsam
NK035(ci)001:877: gyis gang zag de grol 'gyur skal ldan ma goms
NK035(ci)001:878: pas stobs med snying po'i 'dzin pa der ni rang
NK035(ci)001:879: bzhin sprul pa'i zhing dbugs phyung skye ba gcig ba
NK035(ci)001:880: ste lnga brgya dag na nges pa'i sar grol lo
NK035(ci)001:881: zhes bkod pa chen po 'bum tsho drug gi bdag
NK035(ci)001:882: nyid las rmongs pa'i gdung ba rnam par gsal ba
NK035(ci)001:883: brgyud pa gsum du gtan la phab pa ste sh+aa
NK035(ci)001:884: ri'i bu skar ma 'od bzang gis ston pa 'od
NK035(ci)001:885: srung nyid la zhus pa'i lam gyi le'u ste bcu
NK035(ci)001:886: gnyis pa rdzogs so rdo rje legs pa mgon po
NK035(ci)001:887: gres thag can bka' 'di gtad do khyod kyis bya
NK035(ci)001:888: ra gyis sa ma ya rgya rgya rgya gzhan yang
NK035(ci)001:889: bkod pa chen po 'bum tsho drug pa las lus
NK035(ci)001:890: dang 'dra ba'i le'u stong phrag bzhi brjod bya mchog
NK035(ci)001:891: tu zab cing rgya che yang sum brgya gsung ba'i
NK035(ci)001:892: le'u 'di med na gzugs kyi phung po snying med
NK035(ci)001:893: ro dang 'dra de nas snying dang 'dra ba'i le'u
NK035(ci)001:894: 'di 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bdag gis phyung nam zhig
NK035(ci)001:895: snyigs ma lnga brgya'i dus tshe lo nyid ni drug
NK035(ci)001:896: cu la bstan pa'i btsas su 'di nyid ni skal
NK035(ci)001:897: ldan de dang 'phrad par shog rgya rgya rgya rgya
NK035(ci)001:898: gar nub phyogs glang po sgang gi grong 'bum tsho'i
NK035(ci)001:899: grangs las khyad par bdag gi blo nyid sbyangs skad
NK035(ci)001:900: dang yi ge mi mthun grangs mang bdag gi blo
NK035(ci)001:901: la snang de yi phyir na sgra dang bstan bcos
NK035(ci)001:902: tshad ma kun la mkhas rgyud lung man ngag mang
NK035(ci)001:903: por blo sbyangs kyang snying po yang bsdus gsang mchog
NK035(ci)001:904: 'di med na bdag blos mthong ba'i don med brag
NK035(ci)001:905: ca'i sgra la sbyod dam pa'i brgyud pa rnams kyis
NK035(ci)001:906: rtsa ba nges shes can b+ha seng nags su bdag
NK035(ci)001:907: gi blo yi mun pa kun bsal nas de nas
NK035(ci)001:908: dur khrod chen po rab tu snang byed du thig
NK035(ci)001:909: le mchog gi rgyud lung man ngag rnams dpe gsum
NK035(ci)001:910: nyid du bdag gis bris pa las dpe gcig o
NK035(ci)001:911: rgyan yul gyi rgya mtsho'i gling la sbas dpe gcig
NK035(ci)001:912: kha che'i yul gyi mtha' 'khob rigs ngan dag gi
NK035(ci)001:913: yul gser gyi gling zhes mkha' 'gro 'du ba'i gnas
NK035(ci)001:914: phyi rabs bstan pa'i btsas su dgos srid nas rang
NK035(ci)001:915: rgyas btab ste mkha' 'gro rnams la gtad dpe gcig
NK035(ci)001:916: bod kyi rgyal po'i bka' nan rab che bas bod
NK035(ci)001:917: yul dbus kyi bsam yas sgra bsgyur gling mtshan mo
NK035(ci)001:918: thor rangs skal ldan ska cog gnyis smra byed lce
NK035(ci)001:919: la dbang thob gnyis kyis phal cher bsgyur rtsa ba'i
NK035(ci)001:920: rgyud lnga gnyags kyis sngon du bsgyur de dag skal
NK035(ci)001:921: ldan rje blon gnyis la gtad de nas mchims phu
NK035(ci)001:922: brag dmar dge gong du rgya yi dpe las bod
NK035(ci)001:923: kyi yi ge ru gsang ba'i man ngag 'di ni
NK035(ci)001:924: bdag gis bsgyur ra gan sbyangs pa'i byang bu lnga
NK035(ci)001:925: bcu la dkar po dung bzhus yi ger btab ste
NK035(ci)001:926: bsgyur yang ni ra gan sbyangs pa'i byang bu drug
NK035(ci)001:927: cu lnga zangs bzhus yi ger btab ste bsgyur ba'i
NK035(ci)001:928: pu tig gcig dmar po zangs sbyangs byang bu brgya
NK035(ci)001:929: dang sum cu la sngon po g.yu sbyangs yi ger
NK035(ci)001:930: btab ste bsgyur ba'i bu tig cig chu dar bsgrigs
NK035(ci)001:931: pa'i ldeb ma nyi shu la phra men yi ge
NK035(ci)001:932: sngo dmar btab ste bsgyur ba'i pu ti gcig rgya
NK035(ci)001:933: yi dpe las 'di dag bsgyur nas ni su la'ang
NK035(ci)001:934: ma bstan bstan pa'i btsal su bzhag rgya gar yul
NK035(ci)001:935: du slar log bdag mi 'gro rgya nag ri bo'i
NK035(ci)001:936: rtse la sdod snyam nas bdag gis ma khyer lam
NK035(ci)001:937: la gdug rtsub pas bdag gi don snying phyung nas
NK035(ci)001:938: 'di ru sbas dam pa bstan pa'i bdag pos 'di
NK035(ci)001:939: rnyed shog yi ge mi mthun brgya dang drug cu
NK035(ci)001:940: las gsang ba'i rgyud lung man ngag yi ge rnams
NK035(ci)001:941: n+aa ga ra yi yi ge bkod nas ni 'di
NK035(ci)001:942: nas byang shar 'dom tshad nyi shu'i bar pha bong
NK035(ci)001:943: dmar po stag nyal 'dra ba'i 'og yi ge a
NK035(ci)001:944: yi mtshan ma btab nas ni lcags kyi sgrom bur
NK035(ci)001:945: bcug nas sbas te yod snyigs ma'i dus na gsang
NK035(ci)001:946: ba'i rgyud lung rnams tshong 'dus 'o ma bzhin du
NK035(ci)001:947: bslad nas ni bod kyi rgyal khams 'di yis khengs
NK035(ci)001:948: pa'i tshe 'di nyid longs la rgya la goms pas
NK035(ci)001:949: bsgyur lhag dang chad pa rnams ni 'di yis bskangs
NK035(ci)001:950: 'di las lhag pa gzhan na gcig kyang med des
NK035(ci)001:951: ni bstan pa'i sgron me byas nas ni 'di nyid
NK035(ci)001:952: spyod pa'i skal ldan du ma 'byung bstan pa'i dam
NK035(ci)001:953: pa yang nas yang bsdus snying po 'di rang gi
NK035(ci)001:954: snying la phur la gzhan la bstan pa min 'jig
NK035(ci)001:955: rten yid dga' nor gyi phyir nga yi dpral mig
NK035(ci)001:956: khong snying 'di btang na snying khrag 'dzag cing mig
NK035(ci)001:957: 'bras thang la lhung de bas rang gi snying la
NK035(ci)001:958: rgyas gdab la rig pa goms pas gnad du 'di
NK035(ci)001:959: phur zhig mgon po nag po chos skyong srung ma
NK035(ci)001:960: khyod bka' 'di gtad do khyod kyis thub par srungs
NK035(ci)001:961: skal ldan man ngag bdag po byung ba'i tshe khyod
NK035(ci)001:962: kyis zhen pa thong la 'di byin cig ban dgra
NK035(ci)001:963: dam med dag gis 'di khyer na tshe la bar
NK035(ci)001:964: chod kyis la 'gyu ba'i srog dbugs chod rgya rgya
NK035(ci)001:965: rgya bdag gi blo la 'khrul pa'i snang ba rang
NK035(ci)001:966: dag kyang man ngag 'di la blo ni breng chags
NK035(ci)001:967: nas rgya nag yul du khyed te 'gro snyam pas
NK035(ci)001:968: lam du bstan pa'i snod med gdug cor mon pa
NK035(ci)001:969: dang tshal dang gdug pa'i gcan gzan chu chen dang
NK035(ci)001:970: 'jigs pa'i rog khung dmigs pa'i lam ma byang brag
NK035(ci)001:971: dang chu 'thab 'jigs pa'i shing nags khrod 'di dag
NK035(ci)001:972: rnams su 'di nyid brlag dogs nas rang rgyas btab
NK035(ci)001:973: ste bstan pa'i btsas su bzhag de ltar lam na
NK035(ci)001:974: gdug rtsub grangs mang yang bdag rang gcig pur rdzu
NK035(ci)001:975: 'phrul thabs kyis 'gro skal ldan snying gi bu dang
NK035(ci)001:976: 'phrad par smon rgya rgya rgya dad ldan rnams kyi
NK035(ci)001:977: snying gi dkyil du zhog 'di las lhag pa'i bzhag
NK035(ci)001:978: thabs gzhan na yod re kan bdag ni thos chung
NK035(ci)001:979: rtog ge ma yin pas theg pa spyi yi don
NK035(ci)001:980: rnams bdag gis shes de yi phyir na thabs 'di
NK035(ci)001:981: snying gi bu yang mdzod dmar po'i nang du rgyas
NK035(ci)001:982: thob la rang gi yid la brnag cing zhe dag'i
NK035(ci)001:983: yid kyis 'grogs 'phangs pa'i nor bzhin ser snas dam
NK035(ci)001:984: du zungs de ltar byas na dngos grub cig car
NK035(ci)001:985: thob pan+di ta chen po bi ma la mi tras
NK035(ci)001:986: bsgyur ba rdzogs so +thii rgya rgya rgya ma yig
NK035(ci)001:987: rin po che gdug ba bcad pa'o dge'o bu yig
NK035(ci)001:988: rin po che gser gyi sgrom bu rgya gar skad
NK035(ci)001:989: du sa t+wa nam ki gu ru bod skad du
NK035(ci)001:990: sems kyi gnad bstan pa rang sangs rdzogs pa bde
NK035(ci)001:991: ba la phyag 'tshal lo gang zhig glang chen myos
NK035(ci)001:992: 'dri'i sems mi rtog bde ba'i lcags kyus ni de
NK035(ci)001:993: nyid 'dzin par su 'dod pa mi rtog chen po
NK035(ci)001:994: rnal du phebs gnas pa sems nyid kyi rgyan du
NK035(ci)001:995: bkod pa dang bzhag pa sems kyi ra bar gzhug
NK035(ci)001:996: pa dang 'phro ba sems kyi rol bar shar ba'o
NK035(ci)001:997: +thii gang zhig dur khrod wa yi sems rtog sangs
NK035(ci)001:998: chen po'i gal gyis ni de nyid 'dzin par su
NK035(ci)001:999: 'dod pa rgyu med 'bras med rnal du phebs byung
NK035(ci)001:1000: khungs 'gags pa sems kyi gnas btsal ba dang gnad
NK035(ci)001:1001: gzir bas sems kyi rta bsad pa rtag bcag pas
NK035(ci)001:1002: sems ro mchog ji ltar 'dug bstan pa'o gang zhig
NK035(ci)001:1003: zo chu lta bu'i sems 'khrul pa rang dengs tho
NK035(ci)001:1004: ba yis 'di nyid 'joms par su 'dod pa 'khrul
NK035(ci)001:1005: 'khor rang ldan rnal du phebs ltos ba zad par
NK035(ci)001:1006: byas pas sems kyi grangs zad pa dang 'gro 'ong
NK035(ci)001:1007: la brtags pas sems ngos bzung ba dang de nyid
NK035(ci)001:1008: bzlog pas sems lam du bor ba'o +thii gang zhig
NK035(ci)001:1009: nam mkha' lta bu'i sems ngo bo gcig pa'i phyags
NK035(ci)001:1010: shing gis de nyid sdud par su 'dod pa chos
NK035(ci)001:1011: sku gcig par rnal du phebs sgo 'gags pas sems
NK035(ci)001:1012: kyi byung tshor stongs pa dang yul phyug pas sems
NK035(ci)001:1013: kyi rten stongs pa dang rgya bskyed pas sems nyid
NK035(ci)001:1014: dbus su dril ba'o gang zhig sems la dga' ba'i
NK035(ci)001:1015: gang zag spros pa can 'di nyid goms nas snying
NK035(ci)001:1016: po'i don la 'jug de yi phyir na 'di la
NK035(ci)001:1017: 'bad par bya 'bad de goms na rig pa mthong
NK035(ci)001:1018: bar 'gyur zhes bkod pa chen po 'bum phrag drug
NK035(ci)001:1019: pa las sems nyid rnal du dbab pa'i dum bu
NK035(ci)001:1020: zhes bya ba rdzogs so rgya rgya rgya rgya gar
NK035(ci)001:1021: skad du tan+t+ra b+he la kra bod skad du rgyud
NK035(ci)001:1022: lung gsal ba'i me long stong pa mngon byung nyid
NK035(ci)001:1023: la phyag 'tshal lo rol pa chen po'i lta stangs
NK035(ci)001:1024: kyis gcig par snang ba'i ye shes thob sgra don
NK035(ci)001:1025: shes pa'i rnal 'byor gyis 'byung ba rnams la ci
NK035(ci)001:1026: dgar rol 'khrul pa 'chos pa'i rnal 'byor gyis ngo
NK035(ci)001:1027: bo thams cad rnal du 'bebs lta sgom mthong ba'i
NK035(ci)001:1028: rnal 'byor gyis ye shes nyid la ci bder sbyod
NK035(ci)001:1030: nyon mongs 'ching ba'i mdud pa 'grol dbyings rig shes
NK035(ci)001:1031: pa'i rnal 'byor gyis sangs rgyas rnas dang rgyun du
NK035(ci)001:1032: gnas bzhag thabs shes pa'i rnal 'byor gyis rig pa
NK035(ci)001:1033: nyid ni btson du zin bkol don shes pa'i rnal
NK035(ci)001:1034: 'byor gyis chos can dum bu rtse ru grol gol
NK035(ci)001:1035: sgrib shes pa'i rnal 'byor gyis rang gi de nyid
NK035(ci)001:1036: yid ches skyes rnal 'byor shes pa'i rnal 'byor gyis
NK035(ci)001:1037: lta spyod don rnams bdag por 'gyur gal mdo shes
NK035(ci)001:1038: pa'i rnal 'byor gyis rgyud tshig rnams la ci dgar
NK035(ci)001:1039: rol dbyings don shes pa'i rnal 'byor gyis chos kyi
NK035(ci)001:1040: dbyings rnams dbang du 'dus skyes mtshams shes pa'i rnal
NK035(ci)001:1041: 'byor gyis skye gnyis bar la ci bder spyod rang
NK035(ci)001:1042: snang shes pa'i rnal 'byor gyis ye shes rtags la
NK035(ci)001:1043: thugs phrad grol snga phyi shes pa'i rnal 'byor gyis
NK035(ci)001:1044: goms shugs byin rlabs mngon du 'byin dpe 'byed shes
NK035(ci)001:1045: pa'i rnal 'byor pas yid ces 'bras bu gtan la
NK035(ci)001:1046: 'bebs yon tan shes pa'i rnal 'byor pas ma btsal
NK035(ci)001:1047: bzhag pa'i don rnams shes grol smin shes pa'i rnal
NK035(ci)001:1048: 'byor gyis spyi yi don rnams rang dbang bsgyur dmod
NK035(ci)001:1049: sngags shes pa'i rnal 'byor gyis gdug pa rnams ni
NK035(ci)001:1050: tshar gcod 'gyur nges pa'i snying po yongs bsdus pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1051: rtsa ba brgyad las rnam 'phros pa yan lag grangs
NK035(ci)001:1052: ni de snyed do pha dang ma dang ma ning
NK035(ci)001:1053: las khyad par 'di ni nges bsdus so nges gsang
NK035(ci)001:1054: snying po'i don du'o nyon mongs bag chags bral bar
NK035(ci)001:1055: ni 'di dag rnams dang 'phrad na 'gyur zhes bkod
NK035(ci)001:1056: pa chen po las rgyud lung gsal ba'i me long
NK035(ci)001:1057: zhes bya ba rdzogs so las can gcig dang 'phrad
NK035(ci)001:1058: par shog rgya gar skad du b+ha ka la de
NK035(ci)001:1059: wa bod skad du lha sgom pa bde ba chen
NK035(ci)001:1060: po nyid la phyag 'tshal lo e wam ma ya
NK035(ci)001:1061: zhes bya ba mtshon dang gzhi dang dngos por brjod
NK035(ci)001:1062: khyab phyir rtogs dang lam du'o phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor
NK035(ci)001:1063: bsgom 'dod pas thog mar lus sogs dngos po ni
NK035(ci)001:1064: rnam par sbyang bar bya ba'i phyir sngon 'gro dngos
NK035(ci)001:1065: gzhi mjug dang rjes cho ga rnam pa bzhi ldan
NK035(ci)001:1066: pas lha yi dkyil 'khor nyid la 'jug sngon du
NK035(ci)001:1067: rang gi lus sbyong ba yi ge ram gyis 'jigs
NK035(ci)001:1068: chags nas spro dang bsdu ba mkhas pas brtag phung
NK035(ci)001:1069: po lnga po rgyud sbyong ba dang +aah dang h+aum
NK035(ci)001:1070: s+w+aa h+aa 'jig dang chags pa nyid du bsgom de
NK035(ci)001:1071: nas dbang po'i rten sbyong ba dzi brum dz+ha dzu
NK035(ci)001:1072: b+ha yis ni 'jig dang chags pa mkhas pas bsgom
NK035(ci)001:1073: 'byung ba'i lus rten dbral ba'i phyir ram yam kham
NK035(ci)001:1074: dang lam gyis ni 'jig dang chags pa nyid kyang
NK035(ci)001:1075: bsgom dbang po'i yul rnams rnam sbyong ba sa ma
NK035(ci)001:1076: ta ke ra yis ni 'jig dang chags pa sngon
NK035(ci)001:1077: bzhin no nyon mongs lnga yi gzhi sbyong ba ka
NK035(ci)001:1078: g+ha b+ha dz+nya k+sha yig gis yang ni 'jig dang
NK035(ci)001:1079: chags par rol sems kyi rtog pa rnam sbyong ba
NK035(ci)001:1080: e zhes rngam pa'i sgra yis ni yod dang med
NK035(ci)001:1081: pa'i dngos po sbyong de ltar dngos po nyi shu
NK035(ci)001:1082: drug yi ge de yis grags kyis sbyong de kun
NK035(ci)001:1083: rnam grangs rgyas gdab pa shu dang dz+nya dang ta
NK035(ci)001:1084: dz+nya dang ham zhes yod med dngos po rnams 'jig
NK035(ci)001:1085: pa nyid de chags pa med gal te dngos po
NK035(ci)001:1086: ma sbyangs na stong pa nyid ni skye mi 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:1087: 'on te stong rgyas ma btab na lha rnams ji
NK035(ci)001:1088: ltar bsgoms byas kyang dngos grub 'byung ba ma yin
NK035(ci)001:1089: no des na sngon 'gro'i man ngag gces ram a&a&a&ab+aama
NK035(ci)001:1090: r+g+ga buka ta th+ra c+aa gu +thii nam tram +aahh+aum
NK035(ci)001:1091: s+w+aa h+aa dzi brum dz+ny+aa dzu b+he ram yam kham
NK035(ci)001:1092: lam sa ma ta ke ra ka g+ha b+ha dz+ha
NK035(ci)001:1093: k+sha e shu dz+nya ta dz+ny+aa na ham de ltar
NK035(ci)001:1094: dngos po sbyangs nas ni rang lus lha yi rnal
NK035(ci)001:1095: 'byor 'jug cig dang rim gyis mthar chags dang thod
NK035(ci)001:1096: rgal dag gis skye bar 'dod cig char 'od kyi
NK035(ci)001:1097: gong bu las chu yi la ba ji bzhin du
NK035(ci)001:1098: snang gzugs reg dang bral bar bsgom rim gyi pa
NK035(ci)001:1099: ni yi ge ste mi 'gyur yi ge dbus gnas
NK035(ci)001:1100: par sems kyi dngos po 'od dkar po snang med
NK035(ci)001:1101: reg pa'i gzugs su ste reg ste sdud pa'i yi
NK035(ci)001:1102: ge yis bsdus te 'od kyi gong bur ro de
NK035(ci)001:1103: dkyil sems kyi nam mkha'i yig de dbus mi 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:1104: yi ge las rigs lnga'i yi ge dag las ni
NK035(ci)001:1105: gang mos zhal phyag rnam par bsgom yi ge gzhan
NK035(ci)001:1106: gyi cho 'phrul gyis lha rnams bskyed na 'jig par
NK035(ci)001:1107: 'gyur de phyir 'di ltar shes par bsgom mthar chags
NK035(ci)001:1108: nyid ni bslab bya'i don dang po stong pa nyid
NK035(ci)001:1109: du ste gnyis pa tshangs pa'i gnas bzhi'o gsum pas
NK035(ci)001:1110: mchod dang bstod pa brtsam bzhi pas sdig bshags gsol
NK035(ci)001:1111: ba 'debs rjes su yi rang smon lam gdab lnga
NK035(ci)001:1112: pa dngos po rtsa drug sbyong drug pa zhal phyag
NK035(ci)001:1113: rnam pa ste rang sems mi 'gyur yig dbus su
NK035(ci)001:1114: 'od lnga'i rang bzhin dbus gnas par khro bo la
NK035(ci)001:1115: ni nam mkha'i yig zhi ba rnams ni sdud byed
NK035(ci)001:1116: yig zhal phyag ji ltar 'dod pa bsgom thod rgal
NK035(ci)001:1117: 'od lnga'i gong bu las rang lha'i kha dog ji
NK035(ci)001:1118: lta bu'o 'od ni thig le'i tshul can las skad
NK035(ci)001:1119: cig gis ni zhal phyag tu ji ltar 'dod pa
NK035(ci)001:1120: sems kyi yul rnal 'byor pas ni gang bsgoms pa
NK035(ci)001:1121: mi shigs rdo rje go dang ldan skye gnyis mtshams
NK035(ci)001:1122: su sgyu ma'i lus ji ltar lha yi sku la
NK035(ci)001:1123: 'jug 'di ni dngos po med snang ba'o nyi shu
NK035(ci)001:1124: drug ni ma sbyangs na gang gis lha yi sku
NK035(ci)001:1125: bsgoms kyang chu yi ri mo ji bzhin du 'jug
NK035(ci)001:1126: cing chags pa ma yin no +thii de ltar zhal
NK035(ci)001:1127: phyag rnam pa las stong pa nyid du ma yin
NK035(ci)001:1128: te rang rang kha dog ji 'dra'i 'od sems kyi
NK035(ci)001:1129: yul du gang gyur pa rgya che gzhan snang med
NK035(ci)001:1130: par bsgom de blo brtan par ma 'gyur bar yang
NK035(ci)001:1131: nas yang du rnam bsgoms na rang gis gang 'dod
NK035(ci)001:1132: yi dam de 'od kyi zhal phyag rnam par ni
NK035(ci)001:1133: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du mthong de nyid mthong
NK035(ci)001:1134: ba'i dus dag tu kha dog lnga yis rgyas btab
NK035(ci)001:1135: pas ji ltar 'dug kyang de mi 'bral rang lus
NK035(ci)001:1136: 'od lnga'i thi le la shes pa je phra je
NK035(ci)001:1137: phrar bzhag de nyid goms pa'i rnal 'byor gyis rtag
NK035(ci)001:1138: tu rang lus phya rgyar mthong 'jug la de ltar
NK035(ci)001:1139: su goms pa 'di ni yang dag don la nye
NK035(ci)001:1140: +thii de rjes goms pa'i yo gi ni rdzogs chen
NK035(ci)001:1141: lha yi bskyed rim pas phyi nang lha ru gsal
NK035(ci)001:1142: ba'i phyir gzhal byung bzang ngan blang dor bral rang
NK035(ci)001:1143: lus zhal phyag rnams gsal bas mchod dang bstod pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1144: gnas gzhan med 'od kyis phyi yul snang goms pas
NK035(ci)001:1145: ji ltar spyad kyang dge sdig bral thig le phra
NK035(ci)001:1146: la shes pa gtad shes pa'i rgyu ni phra gyur
NK035(ci)001:1147: pas nyon mongs bdag 'dzin dngos po stongs de la
NK035(ci)001:1148: goms te tshad phyin pas lta dang sgom dang spyod
NK035(ci)001:1149: pa'o lus ngag smyon pa'i gding thob pas bde sdug
NK035(ci)001:1150: rgyu las rnam par grol reg pa'i gzugs med rang
NK035(ci)001:1151: snang bas dge sdig skyabs dang 'jigs pa med 'di
NK035(ci)001:1152: ltar rgyun du sus shes pa'i a ti nyid kyi
NK035(ci)001:1153: rnal 'byor te chu rgyun bzhin du rtag tu spyod
NK035(ci)001:1154: de phyir lha yang rang ngo bas rig pa'i sku
NK035(ci)001:1155: ni mngon sum mo de phyir lha yang mngon du
NK035(ci)001:1156: snang rjes su skyes na brtan pa yin dngos po
NK035(ci)001:1157: mthong na goms pa yin rang bzhin med na 'bras
NK035(ci)001:1158: bu'o // bkod pa chen po las lha'i sgom lugs
NK035(ci)001:1159: gnad kyi man ngag gi lha mngon du snang bar
NK035(ci)001:1160: bstan pa ste bzhi pa rdzogs so sa ma ya
NK035(ci)001:1161: las can de dang 'phrad par shog rgya gar skad
NK035(ci)001:1162: du a d+ha na yo gi bod skad du skye
NK035(ci)001:1163: ba med pa'i don dpal gnyis su med pa la
NK035(ci)001:1164: phyag 'tshal lo rang snang rtogs pa'i gding can su
NK035(ci)001:1165: 'dod pa snying po yang bsdus bstan pa 'di la
NK035(ci)001:1166: 'dud stong pa nyid la mtshon pa'i tshig med kyang
NK035(ci)001:1167: spros pa'i rim pa rnam grangs 'di nyid do kye
NK035(ci)001:1168: sems dpa' chen po nyon cig mi shigs pa rdo
NK035(ci)001:1169: rje'i man ngag gi de nyid bstan par bya ba
NK035(ci)001:1170: la bdun te rkyen gyis mi 'jigs pa'i rig pa
NK035(ci)001:1171: phugs rdugs la rgyab gtad pas bsnyen pa'i lha skye
NK035(ci)001:1172: med du grol ba'i man ngag dang kun tu zang
NK035(ci)001:1173: thal ba'i rig pa sna sel med pa la sna
NK035(ci)001:1174: gtad na ma bsgoms par rang sar dwangs pa'i man
NK035(ci)001:1175: ngag dang gzhan gyis bskyod par mi nus ba lci
NK035(ci)001:1176: ba'i rig pa la 'phang gis btab na 'dus byas
NK035(ci)001:1177: ma spangs bar 'gyur med du grol ba'i man ngag
NK035(ci)001:1178: dang 'phrang bsal bas dgra dang bral ba 'jigs pa
NK035(ci)001:1179: med pa'i rig pa la brten bcas na rkyen rnams
NK035(ci)001:1180: rkyen gyis grol ba'i man ngag dang khod snyoms pa
NK035(ci)001:1181: mtho dman med pa'i rig pa la lam gtod na
NK035(ci)001:1182: chos kyi dbyings thams cad la mngon du spyod pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1183: man ngag dang sras 'dzud pa 'gyur ba med pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1184: rig pa la srab bcug na nyams gong nas gong
NK035(ci)001:1185: du 'phel ba'i man ngag dang mtha' dpyad pas dbus
NK035(ci)001:1186: zad pa'i rig pa la phugs brten na chos kyi
NK035(ci)001:1187: sku la tshad zin pa'i man ngag go kye sems
NK035(ci)001:1188: dpa' chen po mi 'gyur ba ri bo'i gzhi la
NK035(ci)001:1189: lnga ste dran pa sad pas dran med rang dag
NK035(ci)001:1190: pa'i gzhi dang blo yi spyod yul rang zad pas
NK035(ci)001:1191: skye med rang dag pa'i gzhi dang blo ma bu
NK035(ci)001:1192: phrad pas skyes pa thams cad rang snang du grol
NK035(ci)001:1193: ba'i gzhi dang skye med rang sar grol bas 'bras
NK035(ci)001:1194: bu rgyun chad med pa'i gzhi dang 'bras bu rgyun
NK035(ci)001:1195: chad pas zad pa nyid zad pa la sbyor ba'i
NK035(ci)001:1196: gazhi'o kye sems dpa' chen po snang ba chen po
NK035(ci)001:1197: rang sar snang ba la bzhi ste snang srid thams
NK035(ci)001:1198: cad gzhi la bzhengs pas sprul pa'i sku rtsol sgrub
NK035(ci)001:1199: dang bral ba'i lam dang snang srid thams cad gzhir
NK035(ci)001:1200: bzhag pas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yi gzugs mthong
NK035(ci)001:1201: ba'i lam dang khams gsum dus gcig la grol bas
NK035(ci)001:1202: chos kyi sku ngos zin pa'i lam dang srid pa
NK035(ci)001:1203: gsum ka dag pas sku gsum gtan sprugs pa'i lam
NK035(ci)001:1204: mo kye sems dpa' chen po dag pas dag pa
NK035(ci)001:1205: nyid mthong nas zang thal ba'i 'bras bu la gsum
NK035(ci)001:1206: ste rgyu thams cad rang sar dengs pas 'byung ba
NK035(ci)001:1207: lnga las grol ba'i 'bras bu dang rkyen thams cad
NK035(ci)001:1208: rang yul du chod pas snang ba thug phrad du
NK035(ci)001:1209: grol ba'i 'bras bu dang gcig tshad zin pas snang
NK035(ci)001:1210: ba thams cad gtan la phebs pa'i 'bras bu'o man
NK035(ci)001:1211: ngag kun gyi lus dang tshad med na bsgoms kyang
NK035(ci)001:1212: don med rang la yi re chad chos rnams kun
NK035(ci)001:1213: gyi zad pa'i tshad me na 'bras bu rnams ni
NK035(ci)001:1214: dngos dang khyad me 'gyur zhes bkod pa chen po
NK035(ci)001:1215: las skye med kyi man ngag gtan la phab pa
NK035(ci)001:1216: ste lnga pa rdzogs so rgya rgya rgya las can
NK035(ci)001:1217: gcig dang 'phrad par shog rgya gar skad du d+har+m+aa
NK035(ci)001:1218: k+aa ye b+he la bod skad du chos kyi sku
NK035(ci)001:1219: yi don bstan pa chos sku bde sangs 'dzin la
NK035(ci)001:1220: phyag 'tshal lo 'jig rten mun pa'i dmag dpung bzlog
NK035(ci)001:1221: pa'i phyir ye shes 'od kyi dpa' bo mtshon thogs
NK035(ci)001:1222: pas bdag 'dzin sdug bsngal rgya mtsho las brgal te
NK035(ci)001:1223: dran bsam 'ching ba'i dgra rnams gshad bar bya'o e
NK035(ci)001:1224: ma ho rdo rje 'dzin pa nyon cig stong pas
NK035(ci)001:1225: stong pa'i grong khyer bcom pa'i tshe nga ni dus
NK035(ci)001:1226: gsum 'gyur me bdag nyid can lta sgom bcings pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1227: gol sa gcad pa'i phyir rno mnyen ngar dang ldan
NK035(ci)001:1228: pa'i ral gri ni shes rab brtul shugs chen pos
NK035(ci)001:1229: rab bzung nas the tshom log rtog mdud pa gcad
NK035(ci)001:1230: par bya'o e ma hoh rdo rje 'dzin pa nyon
NK035(ci)001:1231: cig gsal ba'i ye shes kyi snang ba 'phrogs pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1232: tshe nga ni lung kun gyi bdag nyid du bzhugs
NK035(ci)001:1233: so chos can grangs kyi ba thag 'dzings pa dag
NK035(ci)001:1234: 'gyur med gsang 'dzin spu gri so rgal gyis dad
NK035(ci)001:1235: brtson de ni goms pas bzung nas ni chags bral
NK035(ci)001:1236: 'byung ba rang dengs dbyings su gcad e ma rdo
NK035(ci)001:1237: rje 'dzin pa nyon cig dag pa nyid kyis dag
NK035(ci)001:1238: pa bkrus pa'i tshe nga ni snang ba thams cad
NK035(ci)001:1239: kyi bdag por ye thog ma nyid nas gnas pa
NK035(ci)001:1240: yin no rkyen gyis bcom pa'i 'du 'phro du ma
NK035(ci)001:1241: rnams 'du shes gcig pa'i stong nyid ra ba ru
NK035(ci)001:1242: dran pa rang sangs rgya yis bzung nas ni rkyen
NK035(ci)001:1243: bzhi rang sar grol ba'i sgo mo bcad e ma
NK035(ci)001:1244: ho rdo rje 'dzin pa nyid cig 'dzin pas 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:1245: pa rang bzung ba'i tshe nga ni 'byed pa med
