NK035(ci)001:1246: pa'i chos can du ye thog ma nas gnas so
NK035(ci)001:1247: dbyings dang rig pa'i snang ba yul shar ba dag
NK035(ci)001:1248: byed rkyen dang bral ba'i nam mkhar ni rang gnad
NK035(ci)001:1249: rnal du phab pa'i lus gcun nas bcom pa med
NK035(ci)001:1250: pa'i mig gis blta bar bya'o e ma ho rdo
NK035(ci)001:1251: rje 'dzin pa nyon cig rdo rje lu gu rgyud
NK035(ci)001:1252: yul kun tu shar pa'i tshe nga ni snang ba
NK035(ci)001:1253: thams cad kyi phung por bzhugs nas so bya byed
NK035(ci)001:1254: rang bra snang ba yul shar ba snying po nges
NK035(ci)001:1255: pa'i thabs dang ldan pa yis stong pa cir yang
NK035(ci)001:1256: snang ba'i gzhi bltas na ye shes nyid ni sngar
NK035(ci)001:1257: med yang yang mthong e ma ho rdo rje 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:1258: pa nyon cig nam mkha' gcig la gsal ba'i nyi
NK035(ci)001:1259: zla dus cig la shar ba'i tshe nga ni yul
NK035(ci)001:1260: gang gis kyang ma bsgribs par ye thog ma nas
NK035(ci)001:1261: de ltar gnas so kye rigs kyi bu de las
NK035(ci)001:1262: 'das pa'i 'og tu ci yang ma yin pa'i shes
NK035(ci)001:1263: pa nyams su myong bar 'gyur ro zhes bkod pa
NK035(ci)001:1264: chen po las chos sku cog bzhag tu gtan la
NK035(ci)001:1265: phab pa ste drug pa rdzos so +thii rgya gar
NK035(ci)001:1266: skad du pra ba b+he la bod skad du 'khrul
NK035(ci)001:1267: pa gcod pa'i gal mdo bde chen nyid ni rgya
NK035(ci)001:1268: che rab zab la chod na zer ba brtag sku
NK035(ci)001:1269: gsum phyag rgyar dran pas phyag 'tshal lo gzhi dang
NK035(ci)001:1270: lam ni ma rig 'khrul sogs su sgra dang dri
NK035(ci)001:1271: ro rnal 'byor kun gyi rgyan ma skyes mi skye
NK035(ci)001:1272: gdod nas skye dang bral mi skye mi 'gag skye
NK035(ci)001:1273: ba'i cho 'phrul can ma skyes gdod nas skye ba'i
NK035(ci)001:1274: don rnams shes gang gis skye ba shes na skye
NK035(ci)001:1275: med thur du 'jug gang gis 'gag pa shes na
NK035(ci)001:1276: 'gag me thur du 'jug gang gis 'khrul pa shes
NK035(ci)001:1277: na 'khrul med zang ka ma'o 'khrul pa'i sa bon
NK035(ci)001:1278: bsregs na myu gu lo 'dab rgyas dran pa'i phreng
NK035(ci)001:1279: thag bcad na dran med chen po 'grub mtho dman
NK035(ci)001:1280: dal khod snyoms na dma' ba'i lung mi snang rang
NK035(ci)001:1281: shar rang rkyen phrad na bla ma'i lung yang yin
NK035(ci)001:1282: goms shugs sngon du byas na 'chi ba'i 'jigs pa
NK035(ci)001:1283: bral bla ma'i lung bzhin spyad na rtags rnams myur
NK035(ci)001:1284: du 'byung gnas su dur khrod brten na mkha' 'gro'i
NK035(ci)001:1285: byin rlabs 'jug smra brjod 'khrul gtam bkag na zhe
NK035(ci)001:1286: sdang skye mi srid gcig pur dal bar 'dug na
NK035(ci)001:1287: yi dam mngon du snang ri dwags bzhin du byas
NK035(ci)001:1288: na zas dang gos mi dgos 'khor 'das ru shan
NK035(ci)001:1289: phyed na phyis kyi bag chags bral rtag tu rlung
NK035(ci)001:1290: sems gcun na nam mkha'i bya bzhin 'gyur rten 'brel
NK035(ci)001:1291: nyid la goms na dngos grub sna tshogs 'byung zhes
NK035(ci)001:1292: bkod pa chen bo las 'khrul pa'i don nyams su
NK035(ci)001:1293: blang ba dang sbyar ba ste bdun pa rdzogs so
NK035(ci)001:1294: rgya gar skad du b+ha la ka ka ba bod
NK035(ci)001:1295: skad du rtog tshogs nyon mongs gzhom pa rdo rje
NK035(ci)001:1296: lus kun rdzogs la phyag 'tshal lo drang srong lta
NK035(ci)001:1297: bu'i 'dug stangs kyiis 'byung ba tsha grang 'dus pa
NK035(ci)001:1298: mnan seng ge lta bu'i 'dug stangs kyis dran pa
NK035(ci)001:1299: rnams kyi thag pa bcad glang po lta bu'i 'dug
NK035(ci)001:1300: stangs kyis 'khrul pa de nyid dbang du bsdu skyes
NK035(ci)001:1301: bu lta bu'i 'dug stangs kyis 'byung ba'i dri ma
NK035(ci)001:1302: cham la dbab wa mo lta bu'i 'dug stangs kyis
NK035(ci)001:1303: phyi yi yul rnams rgya yis gdab lcags sdong lta
NK035(ci)001:1304: bu'i 'dug stangs kyis sgo lnga'i shes pa gcig tu
NK035(ci)001:1305: dril de ltar 'dug stangs rnam pa drug skyes chen
NK035(ci)001:1306: skal pa rab ldan pas goms nas gzhan rtsol bya
NK035(ci)001:1307: mi dgos kye ma nyon cig rdo rje 'dzin seng
NK035(ci)001:1308: ge lta bu'i lta stangs kyis 'khrul pa'i yul rnams
NK035(ci)001:1309: dus gcig blta glang po lta bu'i lta stangs kyis
NK035(ci)001:1310: rang gi de nyid rgyun du blta ri bo lta
NK035(ci)001:1311: bu'i lta stangs kyis rig pa'i snang ba mched pa
NK035(ci)001:1312: blta mda' srong lta bu'i lta stangs kyis rig pa
NK035(ci)001:1313: mi 'gyur bsrongs su gzhug thi bya lta bu'i lta
NK035(ci)001:1314: stangs kyis phyi yi chos can dum bur blta lce
NK035(ci)001:1315: spyang lta bu'i lta stangs kyis nyin dang mtshan mo
NK035(ci)001:1316: med par blta'o kye rdo rje 'dzin pa yang nyon
NK035(ci)001:1317: cig mdud pa lta bu'i shes pa yis lus dang
NK035(ci)001:1318: dbang po gcig tu gsal mda' srong lta bu'i shes
NK035(ci)001:1319: pa yis rlung dang shes pa nang du drang dung
NK035(ci)001:1320: khyim lta bu'i shes pa yis dbang po'i mdo ni
NK035(ci)001:1321: gcig tu gsal gcud phur lta bu'i shes pa yis
NK035(ci)001:1322: lus dang dbang po'i gnad rnams gcun rgyal mtshan lta
NK035(ci)001:1323: bu'i shes pa yis lu gu rgyud ni yul la
NK035(ci)001:1324: gtad me long lta bu'i shes pa yis de nyid
NK035(ci)001:1325: gong nas gong du blta'o kye ma rdo rje 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:1326: pa khyod nyon cig de dag rnams la su goms
NK035(ci)001:1327: pa nyon mongs rnams ni rang dag go rtog pa
NK035(ci)001:1328: nyid kyang rtogs med du rnam par dag pa lam
NK035(ci)001:1329: yin no ma rig la sogs nyon mongs drug 'dug
NK035(ci)001:1330: stangs drug gi gcun nas ni lta stangs drug gis
NK035(ci)001:1331: rtsad bcad nas shes pa drug gis gtan med dag
NK035(ci)001:1332: de phyir nyon mongs rang dag pa'o chu yis chu
NK035(ci)001:1333: rnams khyer ba dang me yis me rnams bsregs ba
NK035(ci)001:1334: dang rlung gis rlung rnams ded pa dang sa yis
NK035(ci)001:1335: sa rnams mnan pa bzhin rang gi gnyen po rang
NK035(ci)001:1336: gis so zhes bkod pa chen po las nyon mongs
NK035(ci)001:1337: rang dag gi gnad gtan la pab pa ste brgyad
NK035(ci)001:1338: pa rdzogs so rgya gar skad du sa ma ti
NK035(ci)001:1339: pa tam kih bod skad du lhag pa'i bsam gtan
NK035(ci)001:1340: dgongs pa rang sar gnas la phyag 'tshal lo gshis
NK035(ci)001:1341: gnas pa la dran pa med mngon snang rtogs la
NK035(ci)001:1342: spang blang med sems rgyud zad la 'du shes med
NK035(ci)001:1343: cig car ba la blo dngos med e ma ho
NK035(ci)001:1344: dran pa rgyun zad kyi man ngag gis yid bsam
NK035(ci)001:1345: gtan la gnas par bya ba dang bsam pa rgyun
NK035(ci)001:1346: zad kyi man ngag gis ngag bsam gtan la gnas
NK035(ci)001:1347: par bya ba dang dngos po rgyun zad kyi man
NK035(ci)001:1348: ngag gis lus bsam gtan la gnas par bya ba
NK035(ci)001:1349: dang 'byung ba rgyun zad kyi man ngag gis nyon
NK035(ci)001:1350: mongs pa rang zad de de dag gi rtags mngon
NK035(ci)001:1351: du 'byin par bstan pa'o phyi yul la brten pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1352: bsam gtan gyis phyi'i zhen pa gcad nang sems la
NK035(ci)001:1353: brten pa'i bsam gtan gyi nang gi zhen pa gcad
NK035(ci)001:1354: bar lus la brten pa'i bsam gtan gyis phyi nang
NK035(ci)001:1355: gnyis ka'i zhen pa gcad pa'o rdo rje bkod pa
NK035(ci)001:1356: chen po las lhag pa'i bsam gtan gtan la phab
NK035(ci)001:1357: pa ste dgu pa rdzogs so rgya rgya rgya rgya
NK035(ci)001:1358: gar skad du sarba pa gu li bod skad du
NK035(ci)001:1359: zhing khams yul gyi gnad snang ba rang sangs che
NK035(ci)001:1360: la phyag 'tshal lo dri ma rnams ni rang dag
NK035(ci)001:1361: pas ye nas sku gsum rdzogs pa'i zhing rang gi
NK035(ci)001:1362: lha rnams mngon snang bas yi dam lha ni ma
NK035(ci)001:1363: bskyed rdzogs kye ho rdo rje 'dzin pa che snang
NK035(ci)001:1364: ba goms par gang byed pa 'khor 'das gting nas
NK035(ci)001:1365: bzlog pa'i phyir ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa yis
NK035(ci)001:1366: 'khor 'das ru shan ma phyed na rtag tu 'khor
NK035(ci)001:1367: ba la gnas 'gyur lus ngag rnal du ma phab
NK035(ci)001:1368: na rtag tu bya byed g.yeng bar 'gyur lus kyi
NK035(ci)001:1369: gnad rnams ma gzir na ye shes mngon du 'byin
NK035(ci)001:1370: mi nus lug rgyud goms par ma byas na tha
NK035(ci)001:1371: mal rnams dang khyad med 'gyur snang ba gong du
NK035(ci)001:1372: ma spel na 'byung ba'i sgra dang bral mi 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:1373: rig pa tshad la ma phab na yid dbyod 'bras
NK035(ci)001:1374: bu thug med 'gyur chos rnams zad sar ma bskyal
NK035(ci)001:1375: na dngos po rnams dang khyad ci yod kye kye
NK035(ci)001:1376: rdo rje 'dzin pa nyon de ltar gtan la ma
NK035(ci)001:1377: phab na yid dbyod 'dzin pa rnams dang ni khyad
NK035(ci)001:1378: par ci yang med par 'gyur de phyir nges gsang
NK035(ci)001:1379: snying po 'di mun pa las ni mar me'am ba
NK035(ci)001:1380: glang rnams las glang chen nam gcan gzan rnams las
NK035(ci)001:1381: seng ge'am rkang thang las ni rta pa bzhin kun
NK035(ci)001:1382: gyi nang nas khyad par ro zhes bkod pa chen
NK035(ci)001:1383: po las rang bzhin zhing khams kyi gnad gtan la
NK035(ci)001:1384: dbab pa ste bcu pa rdzogs so rgya rgya rgya
NK035(ci)001:1385: las can gcig dang 'phrad par shog rgya gar skad
NK035(ci)001:1386: du pra b+ha sa ra ya bod skad du bya
NK035(ci)001:1387: byed lam snang bcom ldan 'das rdo rje bkod pa
NK035(ci)001:1388: che la phyag 'tshal lo rnal 'byor 'bras bu gang
NK035(ci)001:1389: 'dod pa rtag tu lag gi 'du byed bsgom brda'
NK035(ci)001:1390: la goms par byed pa yis snang dang mi snang
NK035(ci)001:1391: la sogs bsgom rnam 'byor de ltar gang bsgoms pa
NK035(ci)001:1392: yan lag rnams ni phyag rgyar grol sgra yi 'du
NK035(ci)001:1393: byed gang bsgoms pa dbang po rnams ni phyag rgyar
NK035(ci)001:1394: grol kha dog nyid la su goms pa lus ni
NK035(ci)001:1395: phyag rgya chen por grol ngag gi sgra la gang
NK035(ci)001:1396: goms pa ngag ni phyag rgya chen por grol yi
NK035(ci)001:1397: ge'i 'phro 'du gang goms pa sems ni phyag rgya
NK035(ci)001:1398: chen por grol rlung la goms par gang byed pa
NK035(ci)001:1399: bla med gsang ba mchog la spyod 'di dag rnams
NK035(ci)001:1400: ni su goms pa phyag rgya chen po nyid thob
NK035(ci)001:1401: bo zhes bkod pa chen po las lus ngag gi
NK035(ci)001:1402: bya phyed gtso bor byed pa gtan la phab pa
NK035(ci)001:1403: ste bcu gcig pa rdzogs so +thii rgya gar skad
NK035(ci)001:1404: du pra wa ra sa ra sa tu ting bod
NK035(ci)001:1405: skad du bkod pa yongs su rdzogs pa bcom ldan
NK035(ci)001:1406: 'das sku gsum gyi bdag nyid la phyag 'tshal lo
NK035(ci)001:1407: gang 'dir rdo rje bkod pa'i lung bstan pa rgyud
NK035(ci)001:1408: rnams bkod dang lung tshig bkod man ngag bkod dang
NK035(ci)001:1409: don sdebs bkod 'byung ba rnams dang phung po bkod
NK035(ci)001:1410: khams dang skye mched yul rnams dang 'jig rten 'das
NK035(ci)001:1411: dang ma 'das bkod pha rol phyin dang lha rnams
NK035(ci)001:1412: bkod thabs rnams yan lag du ma bkod de sogs
NK035(ci)001:1413: bkod don rgya che las snying po yang nas yang
NK035(ci)001:1414: bsdus pa nges pa bkod pa'i don 'di dag gang
NK035(ci)001:1415: gis gang bkod gang las bstan gang byung gang gi
NK035(ci)001:1416: don du dang khyad par gang yin snying po dang
NK035(ci)001:1417: snod dang bcud kyi rim pa yis gang mos blo
NK035(ci)001:1418: la 'di nyid bstan sgra dang brda dang rten 'brel
NK035(ci)001:1419: dang dmigs pa'i rten dang dmigs med pa ji ltar
NK035(ci)001:1420: goms dang de blo dang de yi thabs dang gnad
NK035(ci)001:1421: dang yang rlung dang rtsa dang thig le dang yi
NK035(ci)001:1422: ge dbyibs dang kha dog dang gnad ni rnam pa
NK035(ci)001:1423: du ma yis blo rim ji ltar gnas pa bzhin
NK035(ci)001:1424: skas kyi rim pa ji ltar bar gong 'og rnam
NK035(ci)001:1425: par phyed pa ltar gsal ba de ltar bkod pa
NK035(ci)001:1426: las 'di dag rnams ni yongs su rdzogs rnal 'byor
NK035(ci)001:1427: spyod pa rnams brtson pas 'di ltar rgyud du gnas
NK035(ci)001:1428: par bya ri dwags lta bu'i sems shugs kyis rtag
NK035(ci)001:1429: tu ri las grong yul min stag spyang lta bu'i
NK035(ci)001:1430: sems shugs kyis rgyud du dur khrod gnas su rgyu
NK035(ci)001:1431: seng ge lta bu'i sems shugs kyis skabs su gangs
NK035(ci)001:1432: kyi stongs su gnas ce spyang lta bu'i sems shugs
NK035(ci)001:1433: kyis mtshan dus dur khrod rnams su nyul 'byung po
NK035(ci)001:1434: lta bu'i sems shugs kyis skabs su chu brag 'dzoms
NK035(ci)001:1435: sar bsdad de ltar gnas ni rnam pa lngar rnal
NK035(ci)001:1436: 'byor spyod pa la gnas tshe lus kyi las su
NK035(ci)001:1437: 'dug stangs gnas ngag ni lkug pa bzhin du sdom
NK035(ci)001:1438: sems ni nam mkha' nyid dang ngo de ltar rnal
NK035(ci)001:1439: 'byor gang spyod pa des ni bkod pa'i don tshig
NK035(ci)001:1440: shes rnal 'byor 'bras bu rang sar grol 'di ltar
NK035(ci)001:1441: bkod pa'i don 'di yis sangs rgyas rnams kyi +aa
NK035(ci)001:1442: li ka gsang ba zab mo mngon du'o zhes bkod
NK035(ci)001:1443: pa chen po 'bum tsho drug pa le'u stong phrag
NK035(ci)001:1444: bzhi pa las rim pa mngon bstan ldan zer brtag
NK035(ci)001:1445: gsang ba snying gi le'u zhes bya ba le'u sum
NK035(ci)001:1446: brgya pa las 'di 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis phyungs
NK035(ci)001:1447: pa'o rdzogs so bkod pa chen po ni kha che'i
NK035(ci)001:1448: yul rigs ldan gyi mtha' 'khor mkha' 'gro gser gling
NK035(ci)001:1449: bya bar mkha' 'gro ma rnams la gtad nas de
NK035(ci)001:1450: na yod do nam zhig de yang snang bar 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:1451: ro +thii rgya rgya rgya rgya gar skad du sarba
NK035(ci)001:1452: d+har+m+aa s+au tra bod skad du chos thams cad kyi
NK035(ci)001:1453: mdo bcom ldan 'das byams pa chen po mngon du
NK035(ci)001:1454: slong ba la phyag 'tshal lo chos nyid drag pos
NK035(ci)001:1455: rang gi rgyud rnams gcod dad pa drag pos sdug
NK035(ci)001:1456: bsngal las yid dbyung brtson 'grus drag pos gang 'do
NK035(ci)001:1457: don rnams grub bsgrub pa drag pos dngos grub myur
NK035(ci)001:1458: du thob nyams len drag pos rtags rnams myur du
NK035(ci)001:1459: 'byung sarba ta th+aa ga ta +aa b+h+ae sha g+hash+te
NK035(ci)001:1460: sha ta na y+ye chos thams cad kyi rang sgra
NK035(ci)001:1461: nye bar bcad pa bde ba nas bde bar rang
NK035(ci)001:1462: gi ngo bo la spyad pa'i thabs ni 'di lta
NK035(ci)001:1463: ste thog ma mthong ba ma 'gas par rang shar
NK035(ci)001:1464: nas yid byed pa po kun tu bzang po dang
NK035(ci)001:1465: chos kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' dbyings su thams cad
NK035(ci)001:1466: sangs rgyas pa'i tshe yid kyi khye'u snang ba rig
NK035(ci)001:1467: byed du rang byung nas chos can du mas sna
NK035(ci)001:1468: drangs nas 'byung ba kun gyi bdag por byung bas
NK035(ci)001:1469: rang gi lus ngag la rang gis rgyas btab pa
NK035(ci)001:1470: dang de yang rdo rje sems dpa' man ngag thams
NK035(ci)001:1471: cad kyi bdag por byung nas sgra du ma gtan
NK035(ci)001:1472: la phab ste nam mkha' rnam par dag pa dang
NK035(ci)001:1473: gnyis su med par khyab gdal 'ub chub ting 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:1474: dbang du 'dus pas yul drug cham la phab pa'o
NK035(ci)001:1475: spyad pa'i yul lnga la sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK035(ci)001:1476: dgongs pa shar nas nub pa med pa'i gter 'chang
NK035(ci)001:1477: ba zhes rdo rje snying po'i tshig tu'o yang rgyud
NK035(ci)001:1478: lung kun gyi gol sa bcad pas yid ches kyi
NK035(ci)001:1479: spros pa chos pa dang snang ba thams cad ltab
NK035(ci)001:1480: rang byung gi rgyal por gtan la phab pas chos
NK035(ci)001:1481: can grangs kyi zhen pa chod pa dang rig pa
NK035(ci)001:1482: nyid dri ma kun las 'das par rang grol ba'i
NK035(ci)001:1483: tshe nyon mongs pa thams cad rang thog tu grol
NK035(ci)001:1484: ba'o 'dod pa'i yon tan rnams rgyan ma bkod pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1485: nang du thim pa'i tshe chos kyi dbyings thams cad
NK035(ci)001:1486: spros pa dang bral ba'o 'byed pa med pa'i shes
NK035(ci)001:1487: rab kyis snang ba'i blo log pa'i tshe ring ba
NK035(ci)001:1488: nyid rgyud lung gi tshig dang bral ba'o sangs rgyas
NK035(ci)001:1489: kyi thugs rje klong gcig tu dril nas mi snang
NK035(ci)001:1490: ba'i tshe rig pa nyid 'dus ma byas par bzhugs
NK035(ci)001:1491: so thabs las byung ba'i dran pa yul la 'jug
NK035(ci)001:1492: nas pa'i tshe skye ba med pa'i chos rnams rgyud
NK035(ci)001:1493: dag pa'o stong pa nyid kyi spyod pa mngon du
NK035(ci)001:1494: byung na 'khrul pa rgya yis thebs pa zhes bya'o
NK035(ci)001:1495: 'gyu byed rang sar dag pa'i tshe 'gro drug gi
NK035(ci)001:1496: g.yang sa chod pa zhes bya'o blo yin min gyi
NK035(ci)001:1497: rtsis dang bral tsa na sgro 'dogs thams cad nang
NK035(ci)001:1498: du chod pa zhes bya'o dbang po rnams yul gang
NK035(ci)001:1499: la'ang mi 'jug na rig pa ma dang bu phrad
NK035(ci)001:1500: pas chos can dum bur rtogs pa zhes bya'o stong
NK035(ci)001:1501: pa nyid la cho 'phrul chen po'i ting nge 'dzin
NK035(ci)001:1502: bstan pa'i tshe sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa chen po
NK035(ci)001:1503: ste 'byed pa med pa'i shes rab kyis dpyad na
NK035(ci)001:1504: chos thams cad ngo bo nyid du mar snang ba
NK035(ci)001:1505: zhes bya ste yang dag pa'i lam dang yang dag
NK035(ci)001:1506: pa'i shes rab dang yang dag pa'i snying rje la
NK035(ci)001:1507: goms pas theg pa chen po la byan tshud pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1508: skyes bu blo rab can de ni mi gnas pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1509: yongs su mya ngan las 'da' bar 'gyur ro de
NK035(ci)001:1510: ni mya ngan las 'das nas kyang phyogs bcu thams
NK035(ci)001:1511: cad du rdo rje rol pa'i lta stangs mdzad de
NK035(ci)001:1512: chos thams cad kyi sgra de bzhin nyid la dbang
NK035(ci)001:1513: bsgyur te nam mkha' mi phyed kyi bdag por 'gyur
NK035(ci)001:1514: ro rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin stong la
NK035(ci)001:1515: dbang bsgyur nas lam du mi 'jigs pa dang rdzu
NK035(ci)001:1516: 'phrul dang stobs dang so so yang dag par rig
NK035(ci)001:1517: pa rnams mngon du byas te sku gsung thugs kyi
NK035(ci)001:1518: bdud rtsir gyur nas yang 'dzin pa thams cad kyi
NK035(ci)001:1519: bdag por gyur te de yi phyir nam mkha' stong
NK035(ci)001:1520: las cho 'phrul 'byung ba zhes bya'o gces pa'i snying
NK035(ci)001:1521: po zhes bya ba man ngag gi rgyal po slob
NK035(ci)001:1522: dpon chen po 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis kha che'i
NK035(ci)001:1523: yul du mdzad pa mkha' 'gro ma nam mo ral
NK035(ci)001:1524: pa can la gdams pa rdzogs so rgya rgya rgya
NK035(ci)001:1525: las can de dang 'phrad par shog rgya gar skad
NK035(ci)001:1526: du bra k+aa tsha b+aa b+he ka ram bod skad
NK035(ci)001:1527: du dpe rnams bsdus pa'i sgron ma bcom ldan 'das
NK035(ci)001:1528: bya bral rang dag ngang la phyag 'tshal lo sarba
NK035(ci)001:1529: a pa ya pra b+ha lo g+ni chos nyid spros
NK035(ci)001:1530: dang bral ba'i ye shes de sna tshogs thabs kyis
NK035(ci)001:1531: de nyid mtshon pa'i phyir dpe yi sgo nas gtan
NK035(ci)001:1532: la dbab pa ni ston pa'i lung bzhin bdag gis
NK035(ci)001:1533: bstan par bya'o phyi ma'i gang zag dpe la yid
NK035(ci)001:1534: ches bye pa'i dus na 'di dgos pas 'di nyid
NK035(ci)001:1535: rigs kyi bu rnams kyis gzung bar bya'o bkod pa
NK035(ci)001:1536: chen po'i rgyud las ngo sprad pa'i le'u nyi shu
NK035(ci)001:1537: rtsa dgu gsungs pa yang mdo nyi shu rtsa gcig
NK035(ci)001:1538: tu 'dus de yang bdun du 'dus de yang le'u
NK035(ci)001:1539: gsum pa dran pa gzhi 'tshol gyi le'ura bsdus nas
NK035(ci)001:1540: bstan te de dag gi don rnam par bshad na
NK035(ci)001:1541: gnyis phyi yul la ngo spad pa dang nang sems
NK035(ci)001:1542: la ngo sprad pa'o phyi la gsum ste snang ba
NK035(ci)001:1543: 'od la ngo sprad pa dang dran pa shes pa
NK035(ci)001:1544: la ngo sprad pa dang gzhi rig pa la ngo
NK035(ci)001:1545: sprad pa'o snang ba 'od la ngo sprad pa ni
NK035(ci)001:1546: rigs kyi bu las dang skal bar ldan pa rnams
NK035(ci)001:1547: kyis gangs sam mtsho chen po'i gling ngam sa yi
NK035(ci)001:1548: snying po'am brag sngon po'i them bar nas byung ba'i
NK035(ci)001:1549: rin po che zur brgyad pa'am bcu drug pa'am nyi
NK035(ci)001:1550: shu rtsa gcig pa'am nyi shu rtsa brgyad pa dag
NK035(ci)001:1551: shin tu mchog yin te de lta bu shin tu
NK035(ci)001:1552: gsal ba la ma chags pa dri ma'i skyon gyis
NK035(ci)001:1553: ma gos pa che ba ni khyi dkar po'i mgo
NK035(ci)001:1554: bo tsam bya ngang pa'i sgo nga tsam sor bzhi
NK035(ci)001:1555: pa'am gsum pa'am tshon gang ba'am tha ma yang skyes
NK035(ci)001:1556: bu'i mig tshad tsam blangs te 'di ni rdo rje
NK035(ci)001:1557: sems dpa' gsal byed kyi me long zhes bya ste
NK035(ci)001:1558: dpe thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro ba yin no
NK035(ci)001:1559: de ltar gsal byed kyi me long de la mchod
NK035(ci)001:1560: par bya ste de nyid ston pa rdo rje 'chang
NK035(ci)001:1561: gi skur dri ma med par skye bu'i blos byas
NK035(ci)001:1562: te tsan dan dang ga bur dang gla rtsis sogs
NK035(ci)001:1563: dri bzang po'i sman gyis bran pa'i rgya mtsho'i chu
NK035(ci)001:1564: la gzungs sngags mang po bzlas te de nyid khrus
NK035(ci)001:1565: nas bton la 'khar gzhong ngam bse phor nang du
NK035(ci)001:1566: dar tshon sna lngas dril la bzhugs su gsol la
NK035(ci)001:1567: phyag 'tshal ba dang mchod pa 'bul ba dang sdig
NK035(ci)001:1568: pa bshags pa la sogs pa tshogs bsags pa ji
NK035(ci)001:1569: ltar rigs pa byas la de nas mkha' 'gro dang
NK035(ci)001:1570: chos skyong la gtor ma rgya chen po byin la
NK035(ci)001:1571: de nyid dar nas phyung la za 'og gi gur
NK035(ci)001:1572: khyim khar bzhag ste phyogs kun nas skal ba dang
NK035(ci)001:1573: ldan pa kun gyis bltas na de nyid khra lam
NK035(ci)001:1574: gyis 'gro te de yang phyi nang med par zang
NK035(ci)001:1575: thal ba'i dpes bar do'i snang ba mched pa ngos
NK035(ci)001:1576: bzung ngo de yang kha dog dkar po btsal na
NK035(ci)001:1577: dkar dmar po btsal na dmar de bzhin du ser
NK035(ci)001:1578: po dang sngon po la sogs pa gang btsal ba'i
NK035(ci)001:1579: mdog tu 'gro zhing de dag bral na rang gi
NK035(ci)001:1580: ngo bo chu'i snying po lta bur reg gzugs zang
NK035(ci)001:1581: thal du 'dug pa bzhin du rig pa yang 'byung
NK035(ci)001:1582: ba lnga'i rkyen dang bral nas nyams su blangs na
NK035(ci)001:1583: de bzhin no de ltar rig pa chos kyi sku'i
NK035(ci)001:1584: snying po dri ma med pa de las rang 'od
NK035(ci)001:1585: phyi yi yul du snang ba'i dpe ni yid mthun
NK035(ci)001:1586: pa'i skal ldan gnyis nas gsum las mang du mi
NK035(ci)001:1587: rung de yang gnas khang shar nub phyogs phyed pa
NK035(ci)001:1588: zhig la shar du skar khung gtad de lhag ma
NK035(ci)001:1589: rnams bsgribs la rjes su 'jug pa'i skal ldan gyis
NK035(ci)001:1590: nyi ma'i zhur la bzung ste 'phyar bas phyir man
NK035(ci)001:1591: shes las 'od lnga'i snang ba shar te yong bas
NK035(ci)001:1592: de ni rang gi snang ba thams cad du yod
NK035(ci)001:1593: pa'i rtags kyis mtshon pa'i dape'o de nas rjes su
NK035(ci)001:1594: 'jug pa zhig gi mig gi steng du 'od de
NK035(ci)001:1595: phog par byas la lag pa gcig gis mig ya
NK035(ci)001:1596: gcig bkab ste rdo rje sems dpa'i gsal byed lam
NK035(ci)001:1597: 'gul bar bltas na gsal byed dang bar gyi 'od
NK035(ci)001:1598: kyi zer thag dang nam mkha'i nyi ma'i snying po
NK035(ci)001:1599: gsum dus gcig la mthong ba ni sku gsum gyi
NK035(ci)001:1600: 'brel ba gtan la 'bebs pa'i dper shes par bya'o
NK035(ci)001:1601: yang de ltar skyes bu de'i mig gcig gi steng
NK035(ci)001:1602: du man shel bzhag ste gong ltar bltas na sngar
NK035(ci)001:1603: bas lhag pa'i 'od zer gyi thag pa mthong ste
NK035(ci)001:1604: de las 'od zer phra mo grangs med pa 'phro
NK035(ci)001:1605: ba yang 'ong ste de ni sku las sku'i 'od
NK035(ci)001:1606: zer sku ji ltar 'phro ba'i dpe yin no yang
NK035(ci)001:1607: shel de skyes bu'i mig gi steng du bzhag na
NK035(ci)001:1608: bltas tshad 'od kyi snang bar mthong ste de ni
NK035(ci)001:1609: rig pa nang gsal yin no yang mkhas pas mig
NK035(ci)001:1610: gi steng du bzhag ste mar me'i snang ba la
NK035(ci)001:1611: bltas na de bzhin te longs sku'i 'od gtan la
NK035(ci)001:1612: phab nas longs sku'i ngo bo ni mar me dang
NK035(ci)001:1613: 'dra bas khyim du de ltar mar me lnga'am drug
NK035(ci)001:1614: gam brgyad nas bcu la sogs pa bstan pa de
NK035(ci)001:1615: bzhin no rgyal ba'i sku yang de ltar ro de
NK035(ci)001:1616: ni snang ba 'od la ngo sprod pa zhes bya'o
NK035(ci)001:1617: dran pa ye shes la ngo sprad pa ni shin
NK035(ci)001:1618: tu gnam dwangs pa'i tshe shar phyogs kyi thad las
NK035(ci)001:1619: ras dkar dmar gyi snam bu'i steng du me long
NK035(ci)001:1620: bzhag ste yang man shel gi steng du bzhag ste
NK035(ci)001:1621: ma yengs par zur gyis de nyid la blta zhes
NK035(ci)001:1622: thabs mkhas pa gyen la btegs na 'od snang dang
NK035(ci)001:1623: thig le 'char te ye shes rang gi ngo bo
NK035(ci)001:1624: gtan la phab pa'o yang skal ldan gyis nam dwangs
NK035(ci)001:1625: pa'i tshe 'khar phor brtsegs ma lnga'am dgu btsod chus
NK035(ci)001:1626: bkang ste yang man shel gyis gong ltar ba ltas
NK035(ci)001:1627: na thig le'i ngo bo yang gtan la phebs so
NK035(ci)001:1628: yang skal ldan gyis nam dwangs pa'i tshe shar phyogs
NK035(ci)001:1629: kyi rdzing chus bltams pa la nub nas gong ltar
NK035(ci)001:1630: bltas na ye shes kyi 'od gtan la phebs so
NK035(ci)001:1631: yang 'khar phor che chung rim pa can lnga'am bdun
NK035(ci)001:1632: byas te dbus nas srog shing gcig zhabs la chas
NK035(ci)001:1633: sbyar la de ltar brtsegs la nang tshon chu mi
NK035(ci)001:1634: mthun pas bkang la yang gong ltar bltas na thig
NK035(ci)001:1635: le rigs mi mthun brtsegs mar 'char te rigs lnga'i
NK035(ci)001:1636: thig le gtan la phebs pa yin no yang nam
NK035(ci)001:1637: dwangs pa'i tshe rang gi mdun du 'dom gsum tsam
NK035(ci)001:1638: tshod du bar thag kyang de tsam la shing 'dom
NK035(ci)001:1639: re ba re phyogs bzhir btsug ste de rnams kyi
NK035(ci)001:1640: bar du dung gi phreng ba'am rus pa'i phreng ba
NK035(ci)001:1641: bkrag che bas d+r+wa ba'i tshul du sprel te ste
NK035(ci)001:1642: du phreng ba'i d+r+wa ba byas nas de'i dbus su
NK035(ci)001:1643: rang 'dug ste sa gzhi rnams kyang me long dang
NK035(ci)001:1644: 'khar gzhor gi gcal bkrams la yang man shel gyis
NK035(ci)001:1645: gong ltar yas na d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed
NK035(ci)001:1646: pa mthong bar 'gyur ro de ye shes kyi pho
NK035(ci)001:1647: brang gtan la phab pa'o yang nam dwangs pa'i tshe
NK035(ci)001:1648: rang gi mdun du shing gcig la rta rnga la
NK035(ci)001:1649: bya'i sgo nga mang po brgyus te bar bar du
NK035(ci)001:1650: dar sna'i phur lce yang btags la gong ltar bltas
NK035(ci)001:1651: te skal ldan cig gis de dag skabs su bskyod
NK035(ci)001:1652: par bya'o des ni bar do la ye shes rlung
NK035(ci)001:1653: gi thig le gtan la phebs pa yin no yang
NK035(ci)001:1654: nam dwangs pa'i tshe rang gi mdun du za 'og
NK035(ci)001:1655: gi gding ba bzhag ste yang gong ltar bltas na
NK035(ci)001:1656: snang ba khra bor mthong ste des ni ye shes
NK035(ci)001:1657: kyi rtsal gtan la phab pa'o de bzhin du dar
NK035(ci)001:1658: gyi yug dmar po bting ste bltas na so sor
NK035(ci)001:1659: rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi 'od gtan la phebs so
NK035(ci)001:1660: de bzhin du ser pos mnyam pa nyid dkar pos
NK035(ci)001:1661: me long lta bu ljang gus bya ba grub pa
NK035(ci)001:1662: mthing khas chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes gtan la
NK035(ci)001:1663: phab pa ste nye bar mtshon pa'o yang dar de
NK035(ci)001:1664: dag dbyug pa la 'phyar te bltas na ye shes
NK035(ci)001:1665: rlung dang 'dres pa'i tshad gtan la phebs pa yin
NK035(ci)001:1666: no de dag gis dran pa'i ye shes ngo sprad
NK035(ci)001:1667: pa'i dpe yin no rig pa la ngo sprad pa
NK035(ci)001:1668: ni yang nam dwangs pa'i tshe khang pa phyed phub
NK035(ci)001:1669: pa kha lhor lta ba'i nang du skyes bu zhig
NK035(ci)001:1670: la gos kha dog dkar dmar gang yang rung ba
NK035(ci)001:1671: kha dog gsal ba gyon te de la rus pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1672: rgyan btab la me long la sogs pas brgyan te
NK035(ci)001:1673: yang gong ltar bltas na nam mkhar sku 'gro 'ong
NK035(ci)001:1674: dang bcas par snang ste rig pa gzhon nu bum
NK035(ci)001:1675: pa'i sku gtan la phebs pa yin no yang khyim
NK035(ci)001:1676: mun pa dang ldan pa zhig gi sgo yi nyi
NK035(ci)001:1677: mas phog pa zhig tu skyes bu gos nag po
NK035(ci)001:1678: gyon pa skra spyi bor bcings pa zhig la rgyan
NK035(ci)001:1679: gdab ste gong ltar bltas na rig pa gzhon nu
NK035(ci)001:1680: dpa' bo stobs ldan gyi sku gtan la phebs so
NK035(ci)001:1681: yang khyim phyed snang gi sar skyes pa'i rgyan gong
NK035(ci)001:1682: ltar byas te lus phyed grib ma la 'dug pa
NK035(ci)001:1683: la phyed snang ba la bstan te 'phyar ba de
NK035(ci)001:1684: gong ltar byas na sku phyed 'gro 'ong dang bcas
NK035(ci)001:1685: pa mthong ste rig pa'i phye sku gtan la phebs
NK035(ci)001:1686: pa yin no yang khyim snang ba dang ldan pa
NK035(ci)001:1687: der skyes bu rgyan dang ldan pa phyed krung du
NK035(ci)001:1688: 'dug ste yang gong ltar bltas na rig pa gzhug
NK035(ci)001:1689: sku gtan la phebs pa yin no yang skal ba
NK035(ci)001:1690: dang ldan pa'i skyes bu thabs la mkhas pa des
NK035(ci)001:1691: ras la tshon bkrag dang ldan pas rigs lnga'i sku
NK035(ci)001:1692: yi 'dra 'bag legs par bris te nam dwangs tshe
NK035(ci)001:1693: rang gi mdun du sku bkram ste yang gong ltar
NK035(ci)001:1694: bltas na rig pa'i gzugs sku gtan la phebs pa
NK035(ci)001:1695: yin no yang de ltar bkram pa'i steng du me
NK035(ci)001:1696: long chung ngu dang dril bu g.yer kha rnams kyis
NK035(ci)001:1697: gcal du bkram ste bltas na sku la thig les
NK035(ci)001:1698: brgyan pa gtan la phebs pa yin no yang khyim
NK035(ci)001:1699: gyi shar gyi skar khung gi bug pa nas me
NK035(ci)001:1700: long brgyus pa'i phreng ba'i thag pa 'then te bltas
NK035(ci)001:1701: na thig le'i zer thag gtan la phebs pa yin
NK035(ci)001:1702: no yang de las phreng ba dkar po 'then te
NK035(ci)001:1703: bltas na rnam par snang mdzad kyi thugs rje gtan
NK035(ci)001:1704: la phebs so mthing khas mi bskyod pa'o ser pos
NK035(ci)001:1705: rin chen 'byung ldan no dmar pos snang ba mtha'
NK035(ci)001:1706: yas so ljang gus don yod grub pa'i thugs rje
NK035(ci)001:1707: gtan la phebs so yang zangs sam 'khar gzhon chen
NK035(ci)001:1708: po 'o mas bkang ste de yi nang du me
NK035(ci)001:1709: tog kha dog mi 'dra ba'i tshom bu lnga byas
NK035(ci)001:1710: te yang gong ltar bltas na rdo rje rigs kyi
NK035(ci)001:1711: tshom bu gtan la phebs so yang zangs sa ma
NK035(ci)001:1712: 'khar gzhong du skyer ba'i khu bas bkang nas me
NK035(ci)001:1713: tog gi tshom bu gong ltar bkod de bltas na
NK035(ci)001:1714: rin po che'i rigs kyi tshom bu gtan la phebs
NK035(ci)001:1715: so yang btsod chus bkang nas bltas na pad+ma rigs
NK035(ci)001:1716: kyi tshom bu gtan la phebs so yang tsan dan
NK035(ci)001:1717: gyi lo ma gdus pa'i khu bas bkang ste bltas
NK035(ci)001:1718: na las kyi rigs kyi tshom bu'o de bzhin du
NK035(ci)001:1719: ram gyi khu bas bkang ste bltas na de bzhin
NK035(ci)001:1720: rigs kyi'o yang na dwangs ba'i tshe skal ldan gyis
NK035(ci)001:1721: lag g.yas pas shel gyi lugs ma'i sku bzung ste
NK035(ci)001:1722: lag pa g.yon pas mig g.yon pa'i steng du gsal
NK035(ci)001:1723: byed bzhag ste bltas na rdo rje sems dpa' sku
NK035(ci)001:1724: gtan la phebs so yang gser gyi sku tshon gang
NK035(ci)001:1725: ba la bltas na rin chen 'byung ldan rang rkya
NK035(ci)001:1726: ba mthong bar 'gyur ro zangs sam byi ru'i sku
NK035(ci)001:1727: la byas na snang ba mtha' yas kyi sku rang
NK035(ci)001:1728: rkya ba mthong ba yin no mu men gyi sku
NK035(ci)001:1729: la byas na don yod grub pa'i sku mthong ba
NK035(ci)001:1730: yin no lcags sam beed+aur+ya las byas pa'i sku la
NK035(ci)001:1731: bltas na rnam snang gi sku mthong ba yin no
NK035(ci)001:1732: yang shel gcig las gcig bltas na rig pa dri
NK035(ci)001:1733: ma dang bral ba'i sku gtan la phebs pa'i dape'o
NK035(ci)001:1734: yang rang gi mdun du rma bya'i mdongs gcal du
NK035(ci)001:1735: bkram ste bltas na thig phran rnams gtan la phebs
NK035(ci)001:1736: so yang nyi grib mtshams su nub phyogs kyi grib
NK035(ci)001:1737: ma'i ngos nas skyes bu zhig gis rnga yab chur
NK035(ci)001:1738: bcug pa g.yabs nas skal ldan gyis shar ngos nas
NK035(ci)001:1739: bltas na 'od lnga'i snang ba'i rang bzhin du mthong
NK035(ci)001:1740: ste de nyid nyams su blangs na 'byung ba'i rtsal
NK035(ci)001:1741: nub pa'i tshe de ltar du snang ba'i dape'o yang
NK035(ci)001:1742: nam dwangs pa'i tshe skal ldan shing ta la'i sdong
NK035(ci)001:1743: po'i rtsar song ste gcig gi dbyug pas ta la'i
NK035(ci)001:1744: lo ma rnams phab ste skal ldan gyis nub nas
NK035(ci)001:1745: shel gyis gong ltar bltas na 'od kyi me long
NK035(ci)001:1746: nam mkha' la 'bab par mthong ste des ni rig
NK035(ci)001:1747: pa'i yon tan gtan la phebs so yang nam dwangs
NK035(ci)001:1748: pa'i tshe shar phyogs su bum pa chu yis bkang
NK035(ci)001:1749: ba bzung ste bar snang nas sa la chu'i rgyun
NK035(ci)001:1750: spreng skal ldan gyis kha shar du bltas nas bar
NK035(ci)001:1751: do'i dbang gi chu bo gtan la phebs so yang
NK035(ci)001:1752: skal ldan zhig gis mdun du dar sna tshogs las
NK035(ci)001:1753: byas pa'i phye ma phur mas g.yab ste gcig gis
NK035(ci)001:1754: bltas na bar do'i mchod pa'i lha mo rnams gar
NK035(ci)001:1755: byed pa gtan la phebs so yang rang gi mdun
NK035(ci)001:1756: du skal ldan rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa zhig
NK035(ci)001:1757: 'dug ste rang yang rgyan gyis brgyan nas de gnyis
NK035(ci)001:1758: kyi snying khar dar sna tshogs thag pa 'then te
NK035(ci)001:1759: de'i mdo mdor me long yang btags la skyes bu
NK035(ci)001:1760: gnyis kyis shel re bzung ste bltas pas gcig la
NK035(ci)001:1761: gcig 'od kyi snye tshan du mthong ste bar do
NK035(ci)001:1762: la rigs lnga yab yum gyi byang chub kyi sems
NK035(ci)001:1763: rgyun gtan la phebs so yang nam dwangs pa'i tshe
NK035(ci)001:1764: skal ldan de gan rkyal du nyal te rang gi
NK035(ci)001:1765: snying khar gdugs gser gyi yu ba can gcig bzung
NK035(ci)001:1766: ste mig g.yon pas gsal byed kyis bltas na rig
NK035(ci)001:1767: pa ma bu 'brel ba dang lhun grub kyi snang
NK035(ci)001:1768: ba gtan la phebs so yang nam dwangs pa'i tshe
NK035(ci)001:1769: gser gyi dril bu g.yer kha'i phreng ba skyes bu
NK035(ci)001:1770: gcig gis spyi bor 'then te yang skal ldan gyis
NK035(ci)001:1771: bltas nas de la yang gcig gis dbyug pa dal
NK035(ci)001:1772: bus brgyab cing gong ltar bltas na rig pa 'gyu
NK035(ci)001:1773: ba rlung gi sgra dang bcas pa gtan la phebs
NK035(ci)001:1774: so de rnams ni gzhi rig pa la ngo sprad
NK035(ci)001:1775: pa'o don de dag gsum gyi phyi yul la ngo
NK035(ci)001:1776: sprad pas bar dor lam la brtan pa thob pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1777: dgos pa yod do gnyis pa nang sems rig la
NK035(ci)001:1778: ngo sprad pa la gnyis te bya byed sems la
NK035(ci)001:1779: ngo sprad pas snang ba'i 'du ba bcad par bstan
NK035(ci)001:1780: pa dang mi 'gyur ba'i rig pa la ngo sprad
NK035(ci)001:1781: pas 'dug tshul shes par bstan pa'o sems la ngo
NK035(ci)001:1782: sprad pa ni nyer gcig gtan la phab pas 'dir
NK035(ci)001:1783: ma spros so rig pa la gnyis te rig pa
NK035(ci)001:1784: rang gi ngo bo la sprad pa dang rtags la
NK035(ci)001:1785: sprad pa'o rtags ni thig le'i rtags su rang gi
NK035(ci)001:1786: mig gi phugs su rang gi mtheb mdzub kyis ded
NK035(ci)001:1787: pas thig le mthe ba gang ba zhig 'char te
NK035(ci)001:1788: dbang gi brdar dmar po shas che ba'i 'od du
NK035(ci)001:1789: shar ba de lus la thig ler gnas pa'i rtags
NK035(ci)001:1790: mtshan mo sprid pa drag po byung ba'i tshe mig
NK035(ci)001:1791: nas me stag dmar po 'phro ba'i tshul 'od du
NK035(ci)001:1792: 'char te shes rab kyi rtags dbyings kyi rtags a
NK035(ci)001:1793: tham ye shes kyi rlung gi rang sgra ni rna
NK035(ci)001:1794: ba'i mdun ngos mtheb mos mnan pas sgra 'ong ba
NK035(ci)001:1795: de yin ye shes kyi rtags ni skyes bu gcig
NK035(ci)001:1796: snga dro shar du 'dug bar du btsod chu bzhag
NK035(ci)001:1797: ste de yi nang du bltas pas chu'i nang du
NK035(ci)001:1798: sngon dmar du song ba de yin no kha'i rlangs
NK035(ci)001:1799: pa nyi zer la sngon dmar du yod pa de
NK035(ci)001:1800: ye shes kyi rlung yin pa'i rtags ba spu rnams
NK035(ci)001:1801: nyi zer la bstan na 'od 'byung ba ni sku'i
NK035(ci)001:1802: rtags rig pa'i rtags ni btsod chu'i nang du kha
NK035(ci)001:1803: rlangs 'od du 'byung ba de yin no rig pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1804: ngo bo la gsum ste rig pa'i sku la ngo
NK035(ci)001:1805: sprad pa dang rig pa rang gi 'dug tshul la
NK035(ci)001:1806: ngo sprad pa dang rig pa'i goms tshad la ngo
NK035(ci)001:1807: sprad pa'o sku ni gsum ste sprul sku ngo sprod
NK035(ci)001:1808: kyi man ngag gis snang ba 'di gtan la dbab
NK035(ci)001:1809: par bstan pas 'byung ba'i gnod pa dang bral bar
NK035(ci)001:1810: bstan pa dang longs sku ngo sprod kyi man ngag
NK035(ci)001:1811: gis bar do'i snang ba gtan la phab pa ste
NK035(ci)001:1812: skye gnyis mtsham su mngon par rdzogs par bud+d+ha bar
NK035(ci)001:1813: byed do chos sku ngo sprod kyi gdams ngag gis
NK035(ci)001:1814: gzhi gnas chen po gtan la dbab pa ste 'khor
NK035(ci)001:1815: 'das bsreg te mya ngan las 'da' bar byed pa'o
NK035(ci)001:1816: rig pa rang gi 'dug tshul ni rig pa ngon
NK035(ci)001:1817: sum gyi man ngag ces bya ba ste dpe dang
NK035(ci)001:1818: rtags rnams bral bar rab tu gsang ba'i don du'o
NK035(ci)001:1819: ri pa goms tshad ni 'khor 'das ru shan phyed
NK035(ci)001:1820: pa la sogs pa'o de ltar dpe du mas gtan
NK035(ci)001:1821: la phab pa ni 'di nyid la dbang po 'bring
NK035(ci)001:1822: po rnams yid ches pa'i dgos pa dang bar do
NK035(ci)001:1823: ngo shes pa'i dgos pa yod do mngon sum du
NK035(ci)001:1824: gtan la dbab pa rnams ni kun gyi spyod yul
NK035(ci)001:1825: ma yin pas yang mdzod du a tham de'i phyir
NK035(ci)001:1826: na ngo sprad pa dang rtogs pa thob pa dus
NK035(ci)001:1827: mnyam rtogs pa thob pa dang chos grub mtha' gzhan
NK035(ci)001:1828: la bor de la brtags pa gces ba dus mnyam
NK035(ci)001:1829: chos bor ba dang dbugs chad pa dus mnyam dbugs
NK035(ci)001:1830: chad pa dang sangs rgyas pa dus mnyam par bstan
NK035(ci)001:1831: no lta ba rang byung gi ye shes dpangs mtho
NK035(ci)001:1832: yang dpe du mas ma bstan na dbang po 'bring
NK035(ci)001:1833: po rnams b+hud mi d+ha'o a ti yo ga rtsol
NK035(ci)001:1834: sgrub dang bral yang gsang sngags kyi dbang dang byin
NK035(ci)001:1835: rlabs ma byas na dbang po tha ma rnams skye
NK035(ci)001:1836: ba gcig gis thogs par mi 'gyur te skye ba
NK035(ci)001:1837: brgyud par 'gyur ro lta ba stong pa nyid rgya
NK035(ci)001:1838: che yang rig pa tshad la ma phab na spyi
NK035(ci)001:1839: 'byams te dbang po rab kyis 'di nyid la ye
NK035(ci)001:1840: shes kyi rtsal mi rdzogs so de'i phyir na yang
NK035(ci)001:1841: mdzod kyi gdams pa bstan pa'o rig pa'i ye shes
NK035(ci)001:1842: dpe du ma'i sgo nas gtan la phab pa ngo
NK035(ci)001:1843: sprod rin po che 'khor lo zhes bya ba sprul
NK035(ci)001:1844: pa po dga' rab rdo rje'i mdzad pa rdzogs so
NK035(ci)001:1845: sa ma ya na ra kan rgya rgya rgya rgyud
NK035(ci)001:1846: med rnam par dag pa'i ston pa rdo rje 'chang
NK035(ci)001:1847: sel med dri ma dag par nges pa'i bka' de
NK035(ci)001:1848: don ma nor bsdus pa'i yi ge 'di sangs rgyas
NK035(ci)001:1849: mya ngan 'das pa'i rten du yi ger btab bdag
NK035(ci)001:1850: ni skye bo'i rigs med u rgyan yul du ni
NK035(ci)001:1851: dar ma sde yi lhums su zhugs pa'i tshul bstan
NK035(ci)001:1852: nas gsang sngags gsang ba'i yi ge 'di dag bkod
NK035(ci)001:1853: 'jig rten mun pa rnams ni 'di yis 'od du
NK035(ci)001:1854: 'bar rgyud dang man ngag rnams su rab phye nas
NK035(ci)001:1855: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen nyid kyi rgyud sbyang phyir man
NK035(ci)001:1856: ngag snying po rgyud kyi gsang don bkod bstan pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1857: rgyal po 'di ni gar gnas par mun pa rang
NK035(ci)001:1858: dag snang ba'i 'od dang ldan theg pa'i nang nas
NK035(ci)001:1859: khyad 'phags a ti gsang ba che de yi tshig
NK035(ci)001:1860: dang yi ge rgyud dang man ngag lung spyi yi
NK035(ci)001:1861: lus bzhin phyi yi yul tsam mtshon de ltar bkod
NK035(ci)001:1862: pa'i tshig tshogs grangs mang la gsang ba'i man ngag
NK035(ci)001:1863: snying tig 'di med na gzugs kyi phung po khong
NK035(ci)001:1864: gi snying med 'dra de ltar a ti rang don
NK035(ci)001:1865: gzhung rnams la mtshan par byed pa'i yi ge 'di
NK035(ci)001:1866: med na dbang po'i dwangs ma dpral ba'i mig med
NK035(ci)001:1867: 'dra a ti sde dang grangs bkod chos rnams la
NK035(ci)001:1868: bshad par bya ba'i rgyud chen 'di med na sgyur
NK035(ci)001:1869: bar byed pa kha yi lce med 'dra bstan pa
NK035(ci)001:1870: 'di las khyad par che ba'i thabs gzhan nas ston
NK035(ci)001:1871: re bdag ni na ra kan de yi phyir na
NK035(ci)001:1872: phyi rabs 'jug pa rnams 'di la goms par gyis
NK035(ci)001:1873: la mig ltar 'tshol 'jam dpal khyod kyis bstan pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1874: snying po 'di bstan pa'i don du skal dang ldan
NK035(ci)001:1875: la byin skal ba dag dang mi ldan byung srid
NK035(ci)001:1876: na bstan pa'i btsas su rang rgya thob la spos
NK035(ci)001:1877: bdag ni mya ngan 'da' ste gsang ba'i tshig gsum
NK035(ci)001:1878: po khyod kyis zung la snying gi dkyil du phur
NK035(ci)001:1879: 'di ni skal med rnams dang theg dman la rlung
NK035(ci)001:1880: phyogs tsam du brjod bar ma byed cig ci phyir
NK035(ci)001:1881: skrag cing brgyal nas gsang sngags nyid spong bas 'di
NK035(ci)001:1882: nyid bskal ba 'jig kyang snying la rgyas gdab bya
NK035(ci)001:1883: snying po byang chub bar du kha ru dbyung mi
NK035(ci)001:1884: bya zhes pa sprul pa po dga' rab rdo rjes
NK035(ci)001:1885: gsungs pa rdzogs so las can de dang 'phrad par
NK035(ci)001:1886: shog rgya rgya rgya ma rlas+aacatra22gwatha&a&a&a rgya gar skad du
NK035(ci)001:1887: pe ti ta ki la s+ya mi sha n+aa ma
NK035(ci)001:1888: bod skad du 'chi ba brtag pa zhes bya ba
NK035(ci)001:1889: bcom ldan 'das thugs rje chen po la phyag 'tshal
NK035(ci)001:1890: lo gnyis med ston pas 'gro la phan gdags phyir
NK035(ci)001:1891: mchog gsang rgyud las mdor bsdus rnam bshad pa de
NK035(ci)001:1892: yi don rnams rim pa ji lta bar rnam par
NK035(ci)001:1893: phye nas bdag gis bstan par bya sems can lus
NK035(ci)001:1894: rnams sdug bsngal bzhis bcings pas thugs rje che mchog
NK035(ci)001:1895: rdo rje 'chang chen gyis 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal nyid
NK035(ci)001:1896: kyi dus tshod dang rgyud du bkod pa'i tshig don
NK035(ci)001:1897: rgya che yang 'chi ba dang ni gnyis yin te
NK035(ci)001:1898: gdon dang nad la sogs pa dus ma yin par
NK035(ci)001:1899: 'chi ba dang 'byung ba zad de 'chi ba'o ji
NK035(ci)001:1900: ltar gyur kyang rtag pa 'adi'o gang gi 'chi ba
NK035(ci)001:1901: brtag pa'i skyes bu des bla ma dkon mchog la
NK035(ci)001:1902: tshogs gsog pa sngon du 'gro bas mkha' 'gro dang
NK035(ci)001:1903: chos skyong mchod la 'chi bar nges pa'i dus brtag
NK035(ci)001:1904: pa la gsum ste phyi phung po la brtag pa
NK035(ci)001:1905: dang nang rlung la brtag pa dang gsang ba rig
NK035(ci)001:1906: pa la brtag pa'o dang po la gnyis te gzhan
NK035(ci)001:1907: gyi phung po la brtag pa dang rang gi phung
NK035(ci)001:1908: po la brtag pa'o dang po la gnyis te dbyibs
NK035(ci)001:1909: dang kha dog la brtag pa dang rtsa dang rlung
NK035(ci)001:1910: la brtag pa'o dang po la gnyis te tshe yi
NK035(ci)001:1911: yan lag la brtag pa dang dbang po la brtag
NK035(ci)001:1912: pa'o yan lag ni sen mo'i bkrag shor na zla
NK035(ci)001:1913: ba dgu'i nyin phyed na nad kyis btab na 'chi
NK035(ci)001:1914: ba'o mig gi mtha' spris dkar po yal na zla
NK035(ci)001:1915: ba lnga na 'achi'o ltag pa'i bdud sgo nas skra
NK035(ci)001:1916: mtshom gcig gyen la langs na zhag nyi shu rtsa
NK035(ci)001:1917: gcig nas 'achi'o rkang pa'i long bu phyir log tu
NK035(ci)001:1918: 'gyur na zla ba gcig gi 'byung ba zug pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1919: dus su 'achi'o skyes bu nad kyis btab pa la
NK035(ci)001:1920: brtag pa ni so rnams kyi rtsa bar rdul dang
NK035(ci)001:1921: dreg pa chags na 'byung ba'i bdud 'dus pa zhes
NK035(ci)001:1922: bya ste zhag dgu na 'achi'o sna zhom na rlung
NK035(ci)001:1923: gi sgo 'gag pa zhes bya ste zhag lnga na
NK035(ci)001:1924: 'achi'o rtag tu yan lag brkyangs na 'byung ba'i ri
NK035(ci)001:1925: snyeg pa zhes bya ste zhag bdun na'o 'byed 'dzum
NK035(ci)001:1926: med par mig 'bru tshugs su blta na rlung yul
NK035(ci)001:1927: la shor ba zhes bya ste zhag gsum na'o mig
NK035(ci)001:1928: gi tshigs 'khrul zhig yud glog glog tsam gyen la
NK035(ci)001:1929: blta na chu'i rba log pa zhes bya ste zhag
NK035(ci)001:1930: bco lnga na'o 'gram pa'i sha shor gshor bu byung
NK035(ci)001:1931: na sa'i sgang ral ba zhes bya ste zhag bcu
NK035(ci)001:1932: dgu'i 'byung ba zug pa'i dus na 'achi'o dbugs yang
NK035(ci)001:1933: yang rgod na rlung gi grangs 'des pa zhes bya
NK035(ci)001:1934: ste zhag drug na'o sna g.yas g.yon du yo na
NK035(ci)001:1935: sna'i man ji ka chad pa zhes bya ste zhag
NK035(ci)001:1936: bdun na'o mig gi mchi ma mi thub par 'dzag
NK035(ci)001:1937: na bar chad pa zhes bya ste zhag lnga na'o
NK035(ci)001:1938: 'gram pa g.yon gshong bur song na bar sha chad
NK035(ci)001:1939: pa zhes bya ste zhag gcig na'o so 'thams na
NK035(ci)001:1940: 'byung ba'i lam chad pa zhes bya ste zhag gsum
NK035(ci)001:1941: gyi nyi ma phyed na'o lce la sngar med pa'i
NK035(ci)001:1942: thig le nag po byung na zhag gnyis kyi 'byung
NK035(ci)001:1943: ba zug pa'i dus na'o rna ba leb mor 'byar
NK035(ci)001:1944: na rna ba'i gnas 'then chad pa zhes bya ste
NK035(ci)001:1945: nam phyed na'o brang gi lhan sna zhom na chu'i
NK035(ci)001:1946: rka chad pa zhes bya ste zla ba phyed kyi
NK035(ci)001:1947: byer ba'i dus na'o rtsa gnyis log med na me'i
NK035(ci)001:1948: sa bon stong pa zhes bya ste zla ba phyed
NK035(ci)001:1949: kyi me'i dus na'o de dag ni gzhan la ste
NK035(ci)001:1950: nam phyed na'o rnal 'byor pa rang gi don du
NK035(ci)001:1951: bu'o // brtag pa ni / sngon du bla ma la sogs la tshogs bsags pa la bya'o //
NK035(ci)001:1952: de yang nam mkha'i khams su tshe'i gzugs brnyan yal lam ma yal brtag pa /
NK035(ci)001:1953: bar snang khams su gnam sa gnyis kyi 'brel thag
NK035(ci)001:1954: chad dam ma chad brtag pa ri rab kyi logs
NK035(ci)001:1955: la seng ge dkar mo'i mi babs sam ma babs
NK035(ci)001:1956: brtag pa ri thang mtshams su ljon shing gi sked
NK035(ci)001:1957: pa chag gam ma chag brtag pa rgya mtsho'i gting
NK035(ci)001:1958: du chu'i spris ma yal lam ma yal brtag pa
NK035(ci)001:1959: sa'i grong khyer du dge sbyong gi dud pa chad
NK035(ci)001:1960: dam ma chad brtag pa ri rab kyi rtse la
NK035(ci)001:1961: mi 'gyur ba'i nyi ma nub bam ma nub brtag
NK035(ci)001:1962: pa ri rab kyi khong gseng na mkha' 'gro ma'i
NK035(ci)001:1963: rang sgra chad dam ma chad brtag pa dpag bsam
NK035(ci)001:1964: gyi shing la 'chi bdag gi bdud langs sam ma
NK035(ci)001:1965: langs brtags pa'o dang po ni nam dwangs pa'i tshe
NK035(ci)001:1966: snga dro'am phyi dro la rang gi grib ma'i snying
NK035(ci)001:1967: khar rdo'am shing btsugs la mig gtad de langs la
NK035(ci)001:1968: dbyug pa'am phreng bzung nas yan lag brkyangs pa'i grib
NK035(ci)001:1969: ma la bltas nas nam mkhar bltas pas gzugs brnyan
NK035(ci)001:1970: 'char te yan lag tshang zhing gos gyon pa'i kha
NK035(ci)001:1971: dog shar na skyon med do bar chad la gsum
NK035(ci)001:1972: ste chad lhag las 'chi ba'i dus bzung ba ka
NK035(ci)001:1973: dog las gdon ngos bzung ba dbyibs la bslu bas
NK035(ci)001:1974: bzlog gam mi log ngos bzung ba'o dang po ni
NK035(ci)001:1975: lag gi phyag mtshan med na brten pa'i lha dang
NK035(ci)001:1976: bral bas lo bdun na 'achi'o lag pa g.yas med
NK035(ci)001:1977: na lo lnga na'o g.yon med na gsum na'o rkang
NK035(ci)001:1978: pa g.yas pa'i pus mo man chad med na lo
NK035(ci)001:1979: gnyis na'o thams cad med na zla ba brgyad na'o
NK035(ci)001:1980: rkang pa g.yon med na lo gcig na'o mgo yi
NK035(ci)001:1981: g.yas phyed med na zla ba dgu na'o g.yon med
NK035(ci)001:1982: na zla ba bdun na'o rked yan chad med na
NK035(ci)001:1983: zla ba lnga na'o rked dang bcas pa med na
NK035(ci)001:1984: zla ba gsum na'o ro stod med na zla ba
NK035(ci)001:1985: gnyis na'o smad med na zla ba gcig na'o lus
NK035(ci)001:1986: phyed tshal gyi g.yas med na zhag nyi shu rtsa
NK035(ci)001:1987: dgu na'o g.yon med na zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig
NK035(ci)001:1988: na'o dbyibs la gru bzhir byung na bslu bas bzlog
NK035(ci)001:1989: go zlum po dang nar mo dang zla gam yang
NK035(ci)001:1990: de bzhin no ro bstums pa lta bu dang gru
NK035(ci)001:1991: gsum ni thugs rje chen pos kyang mi bzlog go
NK035(ci)001:1992: kha dog ni dkar po las dbus nas yal na
NK035(ci)001:1993: klu dang rgyal pos zin pa'o nag po g.yas nas
NK035(ci)001:1994: yal na bdud dang ma mo'i dmar po g.yon nas
NK035(ci)001:1995: yal na klu btsan dang rgyal 'gong ngo sngon po
NK035(ci)001:1996: rkang pa nas je thung yal na klu dang mtsho
NK035(ci)001:1997: sman no nag ban bun du 'dug na ma mo
NK035(ci)001:1998: dang gshin rjes zin pa'o ser breng breng ni sa
NK035(ci)001:1999: bdag go khra khyug khyug ni shi 'adre'o gnam sa
NK035(ci)001:2000: gnyis kyi 'brel thag la brtag pa ni nyin phyed
NK035(ci)001:2001: dus su kha lhor bltas la gru mo pus mo'i
NK035(ci)001:2002: steng du bzhag nas lag ngar gyen la bsgrengs pas
NK035(ci)001:2003: khu tshur smin phrag tu bcangs pa la mig zur
NK035(ci)001:2004: mnyam par bltas pas lag ngar shin tu phra mor
NK035(ci)001:2005: 'ong ngo de nyid chad na zhag bcu dgu na
NK035(ci)001:2006: 'achi'o ri rab kyi seng ge zhon pa'i mi la
NK035(ci)001:2007: brdag pa ni nyi shar gyi shar phyogs su chu'i
NK035(ci)001:2008: rdzing lteng ka yod pa'i nub ngos kyi gyang ngam
NK035(ci)001:2009: rtsig ngos la rang gi grib ma nyis brtsegs su
NK035(ci)001:2010: 'ong ba'i steng ma med na chu'i mi stor ba
NK035(ci)001:2011: zhes bya ste zhag bcu drug gi nyin phyed na
NK035(ci)001:2012: 'achi'o ri thang mtshams su ljon shing gi rked pa
NK035(ci)001:2013: la brtag pa ni rtsa rnams la brtag pa ste
NK035(ci)001:2014: 'dir ma bris so rgya mtsho'i gting du chu'i spris
NK035(ci)001:2015: ma brtag pa ni mtshan mo chang mang po ma
NK035(ci)001:2016: 'thungs 'khrig pa ma spyad gtam mang po ma smras
NK035(ci)001:2017: pa'i nang par nyi ma rtse shar la shar du
NK035(ci)001:2018: bltas te 'khar phor la sogs pa snod dkar nag
NK035(ci)001:2019: ran par rang gi chu la brtag pa ste rlangs
NK035(ci)001:2020: pa sngon dmar du byung na zla ba phyed na
NK035(ci)001:2021: 'achi'o nag po hral hrol du song na zhag bcu
NK035(ci)001:2022: gcig na'o dmar po thig le can ni zhag dgu
NK035(ci)001:2023: na'o de ma yin pa ni tshe'i dus mi byed
NK035(ci)001:2024: do kha dog las gdon brtag pa ni sngar dang
NK035(ci)001:2025: 'dra'o sa'i grong khyer du du ba la brtag pa
NK035(ci)001:2026: ni nyi ma rtse shar na dri chen gyi rlangs
NK035(ci)001:2027: pa med na zhag dgu na'o ri rab kyi rtse
NK035(ci)001:2028: nas nyi ma brtag pa ni mig gi 'od med
NK035(ci)001:2029: na zhag gsum na'o ri rab kyi khong gseng gi
NK035(ci)001:2030: sgra la brtag pa ni seng ge nyal thabs las
NK035(ci)001:2031: rna ba sa la sbyar bas sgra 'byung ba sems
NK035(ci)001:2032: can 'gul ba skad shag shag grags na skyon med
NK035(ci)001:2033: rlung gi sgra byung na zhag bdun nam bcu gcig
NK035(ci)001:2034: na'o skad med na zhag bcu gcig na'o dpag bsam
NK035(ci)001:2035: gyi shing la brtag pa ni ltag pa'i bdud sgo
NK035(ci)001:2036: na skra tshom gcig gyen la langs na zhag bdun
NK035(ci)001:2037: na'o 'di dag phal gyi dbang du byas pa ste
NK035(ci)001:2038: rgas pa lus zungs zad pa rnams la nges pa
NK035(ci)001:2039: med do rnal 'byor pas mo dang dpyad pas mo
NK035(ci)001:2040: dang dpyad la sogs pa'i rten 'brel thun mong ba
NK035(ci)001:2041: rnams kyi spros pa dang bral bar bya ba'i phyir
NK035(ci)001:2042: ro 'chi ba brtag pa'i gal mdo zhes bya ba
NK035(ci)001:2043: slob dpon chen po 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis mdzad
NK035(ci)001:2044: pa rdzogs so sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa nges
NK035(ci)001:2045: pa'i bka' sgra tshig rtags su bkod pa ma yin
NK035(ci)001:2046: par don dam snying po nges pa'i bka' gsang 'di
NK035(ci)001:2047: 'bras bu yang dag nges pa'i snying pa'o bdag gi
NK035(ci)001:2048: bag chags nyid kyi lus rnams ni ri rab nyid
NK035(ci)001:2049: kyi rdul gyi grangs snyed gcig nas gcig tu blangs
NK035(ci)001:2050: lus kyi tha ma dwangs snyigs 'byed pa ni rgya
NK035(ci)001:2051: gar nub phyogs rim gnyis grong khyer du bram ze'i
NK035(ci)001:2052: rigs mchog legs ldan ston pa dang snang ba'i sgron
NK035(ci)001:2053: ma gnyis kyi bur skyes te shes rab dang ldan
NK035(ci)001:2054: yi ge'i rigs rnams dang sgra tshig kun mkhas 'jam
NK035(ci)001:2055: dpal rnon pos bzung mkhas pa'i blo ldan snying thig
NK035(ci)001:2056: don rnyed nas gsang lung nyid du brtul zhugs spyod
NK035(ci)001:2057: pa mdzad 'jam dpal lung bstan sprul pa nyid dang
NK035(ci)001:2058: mjal yun gyi sgrib pa ma sbyangs gnas su dag
NK035(ci)001:2059: sangs rgyas sprul pas dam pa'i don dag gi bka'
NK035(ci)001:2060: gsang snying po thugs kyi dkyil nas phyung bdud rtsi'i
NK035(ci)001:2061: chu rgyun bdag gi snying la babs ma rig rang
NK035(ci)001:2062: dag ye shes 'od kyis sbyangs dper na nyi shar
NK035(ci)001:2063: mun pa sangs pa bzhin 'bum tsho'i grangs las rgyas
NK035(ci)001:2064: bsdus phye nas bstan bdag ni sngon nas sbyangs pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2065: las sad de ji ltar gnas bzhin go ba'i sems
NK035(ci)001:2066: byung nas bstan pa dam pa'i bdag por bdag nyid
NK035(ci)001:2067: gyur bdag dang mjal nas bdun cu rtsa lnga na
NK035(ci)001:2068: sprul pa po ni mi snang dbyings su gshegs tshig
NK035(ci)001:2069: gsum gtan gyis 'khor ba'i zhen thag bcad de nas
NK035(ci)001:2070: bdag gi blo la dgongs shar ba bstan pa dam
NK035(ci)001:2071: pa 'di rnyed rab drin che stong gsum gang ba'i
NK035(ci)001:2072: rin chen rnyed gyur kyang tshe gcig tsam ste chu
NK035(ci)001:2073: bo'i rgyun 'bab 'dra snga ma'i spyod yul min par
NK035(ci)001:2074: phyi ma'i rgyud dang phrad bstan pa nyid ni yun
NK035(ci)001:2075: gyi rdzas dang nor dam pa nyid kyi drin ni
NK035(ci)001:2076: gang gis 'khor thabs med bdag gi lus dang ngag
NK035(ci)001:2077: dang yan lag thams cad ni lan stong bar du
NK035(ci)001:2078: nyid la mchog phul yang dam pa'i bka' drin rdul
NK035(ci)001:2079: cha tsam mi 'khor des na dam pa dri med
NK035(ci)001:2080: mgon la lus sogs mchod de ltar dam pa'i 'og
NK035(ci)001:2081: tu bdag la bsam shar ba skal ldan snying gi
NK035(ci)001:2082: rigs mchog gcig med pas su la'ang ma bstan 'phangs
NK035(ci)001:2083: pa'i yid bzhin nor mchog 'di sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK035(ci)001:2084: bstan pa'i btsas su ni rgya yis btab ste sba
NK035(ci)001:2085: bar blor shar nas rdo rje gdan gyi 'og tu
NK035(ci)001:2086: sbas nas bzhag phyi rabs skal ba can la smon
NK035(ci)001:2087: lam btab de ltar sbas nas bdag ni gang dgar
NK035(ci)001:2088: spyod 'byung ba'i dwangs yal tshe yi tha ma la
NK035(ci)001:2089: rgya nag rigs mchog sing ha nyid dang ni dur
NK035(ci)001:2090: khrod chen po bsil ba tshal du phrad sngon gyi
NK035(ci)001:2091: skal ldan snying gi bu gcig po bstan pa'i yang
NK035(ci)001:2092: snying bu yi bu la gtad 'di nyid snying la
NK035(ci)001:2093: brnogs te rgyas thob la snying po byang chub bar
NK035(ci)001:2094: du khar mi dbyung gal te bstan zhing sbyin pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2095: dus byung na snying dang 'dra ba gcig las mang
NK035(ci)001:2096: ba na ma h+aa k+aa la legs ldan nag po
NK035(ci)001:2097: yis tshe la bar chad gyis la snying khrag thar
NK035(ci)001:2098: la skyugs de yi phyir na 'di nyid snying la
NK035(ci)001:2099: zungs nga ni 'di nas 'byung ba rang dengs 'og
NK035(ci)001:2100: sum brgya nyi shu lnga 'das lo yi 'og rgya
NK035(ci)001:2101: gar nub phyogs gser gyi me tog gling bardzusa nas
NK035(ci)001:2102: skye zhing sprul pa de nyid kyis pad+ma 'byung gnas
NK035(ci)001:2103: u rgyan rgyal po'i rigs dad brtson ldan pa de
NK035(ci)001:2104: dang phrad nas ni gsang sngags sgrub sde'i don rnams
NK035(ci)001:2105: nges shes 'gyur de nas yang dag snying po'i bstan
NK035(ci)001:2106: pa 'di rnal 'byor sgrub la brtson pa'i +aar+ya de
NK035(ci)001:2107: wa la de nyid snang bar gyur nas de yang
NK035(ci)001:2108: rang dengs su dur khrod 'jags ma'i gling du de
NK035(ci)001:2109: nyid grol de ltar bdag gis 'di nyid nyams blangs
NK035(ci)001:2110: pas snang ba thams cad zad de de nyid bsgyur
NK035(ci)001:2111: mig gi spyod yul 'gyur te 'byung ba rang zad
NK035(ci)001:2112: 'adi'o sgra dang dri ro nyid dang sgo lnga'i kha
NK035(ci)001:2113: dog dengs mngon shes ldan zhing dbyung ba'i dgra rnams
NK035(ci)001:2114: zad lus la sangs rgyas rnams kyi sku yi yon
NK035(ci)001:2115: tan shar snang ba rnams ni zad pa'i sar skyes
NK035(ci)001:2116: pas dran tshor thams cad mi rtog ye shes so
NK035(ci)001:2117: rtogs pas sangs rgyas dang ni shes rab mnyam de
NK035(ci)001:2118: nyid dpe yi lung la ji ltar snang ba bzhin
NK035(ci)001:2119: bdag gi blo la de yi spyod yul du snang
NK035(ci)001:2120: ba rnams ni zab cing rgya che'o de yi don
NK035(ci)001:2121: rnam dril ba sing ha la gtad kyis 'byung ba'i
NK035(ci)001:2122: dgra dang bral bar gyis snying la phur la yid
NK035(ci)001:2123: la rnam par dpyod ces slob dpon chen po 'jam
NK035(ci)001:2124: dpal bshes gnyen gyis gsungs so gtad pa'i rgya dang
NK035(ci)001:2130: &&& rgya gar skad du tro ta la mu g+ha
NK035(ci)001:2131: b+he la bod skad du 'chi ba bslu ba bcom
NK035(ci)001:2132: ldan 'das gzhon nu khro gnyer can la phyag 'tshal
NK035(ci)001:2133: lo 'gro ba sdug bsngal rnams las grol bar bya
NK035(ci)001:2134: ba'i phyir 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal shin tu mi bzad
NK035(ci)001:2135: drag po rnams thugs rje chen pos de dag ma
NK035(ci)001:2136: lus gzung bya'i phyir 'chi ba las bzlog dus las
NK035(ci)001:2137: bshos 'debs rnam par bshad par bya de la rigs
NK035(ci)001:2138: kyi bu kha cig la gong gi 'chi ba'i rtags
NK035(ci)001:2139: byung ba de dag las lor nur ba dang zla
NK035(ci)001:2140: bar nur bas bzlog pa'i man ngag la spyir dril
NK035(ci)001:2141: nas bzlog pa dang bye brag tu bzlog pa'o dang
NK035(ci)001:2142: po ni bar chad kyi gdon 'byung po rnams kyis
NK035(ci)001:2143: tshe 'du byed pa yin te lus 'byung ba lnga'i
NK035(ci)001:2144: rten yan lag lnga dbang po lnga don snying lnga
NK035(ci)001:2145: snod lnga rtsa chen po lnga'i rang bzhin du gnas
NK035(ci)001:2146: par rkyen lo zla nyin mtshan gyi 'pho bas gyis
NK035(ci)001:2147: bslangs te 'chi ba dang 'byung ba lo gcig la
NK035(ci)001:2148: zla ba bcu gnyis kyi dus su 'byung ba res
NK035(ci)001:2149: zla ba gnyis dbang ngo gnyis spyi khyab tu gnas
NK035(ci)001:2150: zla ba gcig la re res zhag lnga lnga dbang
NK035(ci)001:2151: lnga spyi khyab tu gnas nang 'khrugs pas 'chi ba
NK035(ci)001:2152: dang bar chad gdon gyis 'chi ba'o de'i rtags su
NK035(ci)001:2153: 'chi ltas 'byung ba rnams rtogs pa'o de yang byung
NK035(ci)001:2154: ma thag cho ga dang rim gro dang lta spyod
NK035(ci)001:2155: la sogs pas bzlog go 'byung ba dang gdon gyis
NK035(ci)001:2156: gnad la sleb nas mi bzlog go dper na mkhar
NK035(ci)001:2157: gyi 'og khang du me sod sla zhing yang thog
NK035(ci)001:2158: tu shor na mi sod pa dang 'dra'o 'chi ltas
NK035(ci)001:2159: byung nas sngon du bla ma dkon mchog mchod de
NK035(ci)001:2160: tshogs bsags pa'i las ci 'grub bya'o de nas 'byung
NK035(ci)001:2161: ba 'khrugs pa la 'khor lo dang 'byung ba'i yi
NK035(ci)001:2162: ges bzlog pa ni rgya shog gam ta la'i lo
NK035(ci)001:2163: ma la yi ge bri'o de'ang rlung gi 'khor lo
NK035(ci)001:2164: rtsibs bzhi pa dang lnga'i lte ba dang rtsibs la
NK035(ci)001:2165: yam mu khyud la +aa li'o de bzhin du me
NK035(ci)001:2166: la ram sa la lam chu la kham nam mkha'
NK035(ci)001:2167: la e mu khyud la +aa li kha dog 'byung
NK035(ci)001:2168: ba dang mthun par byas la 'byung ba so so'i
NK035(ci)001:2169: lhar bskyed de de la mchod pa lnga 'bum zhing
NK035(ci)001:2170: sdig pa bshags la rang gi 'dod pa'i don la
NK035(ci)001:2171: gsol ba gdab cing so so'i yi ge lo grangs
NK035(ci)001:2172: brjod nas lha la bstim kham phor kha sbyar du
NK035(ci)001:2173: bcug pa tshon skud lngas rgya gram du bcing ba
NK035(ci)001:2174: dang shing sna dang chu sna dang me sna dang
NK035(ci)001:2175: sa sna dang sems can rigs mi mthun pa'i kha'i
NK035(ci)001:2176: rlangs pa bsgres pa'i ngar zan dang bcas pa la
NK035(ci)001:2177: mi gzugs khru gang pa byas te dbang po lnga
NK035(ci)001:2178: la yi ge lnga bris la gzhug go gdon bslu
NK035(ci)001:2179: ba'i rdzas ni khams sa'am ngar zan la byas pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2180: ngar glud lo grangs tsam la tshon rtsis 'byung ba
NK035(ci)001:2181: lnga'i mdog tu bsgyur ba sngo nag bdud dang dmar
NK035(ci)001:2182: po btsan dang dkar bo rgyal po dang ser po
NK035(ci)001:2183: gnyan dang ljang gu klu dang khra bo shi 'dre
NK035(ci)001:2184: dag byas la rang gi dri ma dang gos dum
NK035(ci)001:2185: dang mchil ma dang skra sen dang dri chu bsre
NK035(ci)001:2186: zhing bal tshon dang dar sna dang ltas ngan gyi
NK035(ci)001:2187: bya sgro 'ug pa srin bya sogs sna tshogs glud
NK035(ci)001:2188: la btsug pa'i mdun du gtor ma kha dog dang
NK035(ci)001:2189: mthun pa re re ngar zan gyi chang bu lo
NK035(ci)001:2190: grangs re bzhag nas de thams cad sngags drug gis
NK035(ci)001:2191: byin gyis brlabs la tshig tu khyer cig khyer cig
NK035(ci)001:2192: stobs ldan rnams sred dang chags dang zhen pa dang
NK035(ci)001:2193: dran dang gzung dang bsam dang reg glod dang zhi
NK035(ci)001:2194: dang grol bar mdzod ces brjod nas glud 'khor lo
NK035(ci)001:2195: dang bcas pa chu chen po'i gzhung la bskyal na
NK035(ci)001:2196: lo gsum gyi bar du 'chi ba las bzlog par
NK035(ci)001:2197: 'gyur ro 'chi ltas ma byung gi gong du lo
NK035(ci)001:2198: gsum gsum na re re byas na mchog tu legs
NK035(ci)001:2201: &&& bde ba chen po skyob pa'i lha thugs rje
NK035(ci)001:2202: che la phyag 'tshal lo bye brag tu bzlog pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2203: thabs la rang gi bla ma yod na rab med
NK035(ci)001:2204: na'ang grogs yid dang mthun pa zhig gis 'byung ba
NK035(ci)001:2205: lnga'i sa bon gyis dbang po lnga la dbang bskur
NK035(ci)001:2206: bar byas la de nas sen mo'i bkrag med na
NK035(ci)001:2207: dge slong bdun la chos ston bya zhing yon dbul
NK035(ci)001:2208: sdom ldan yin na bskyar med na'ang blang gos ser
NK035(ci)001:2209: po gyon pas bzlog go mig gi spris yal na
NK035(ci)001:2210: tsha tsha dkar po lo grangs btab la bskor ba
NK035(ci)001:2211: bdun byas nas chu chen por dor zhing gom pa
NK035(ci)001:2212: lo grangs ma song bar phyir mig mi blta bar
NK035(ci)001:2213: 'ong ngo ltag pa'i skra gyen la log pas 'bru
NK035(ci)001:2214: nag po la zan byas te ngar glud khru gang
NK035(ci)001:2215: bcos pa'i snying khar lung btang gi rdog po lo
NK035(ci)001:2216: grangs dang rang gi ming bris pa bcug nas nag
NK035(ci)001:2217: por byas pa'i skra dang gos rang gi gos ras
NK035(ci)001:2218: kyis byas la rang gi gnas khang nas gom pa
NK035(ci)001:2219: brgya nyi shu rtsa gcig gis sar dong nag po
NK035(ci)001:2220: gru gsum brus te ram lo grangs brjod nas glud
NK035(ci)001:2221: de bskyur la bdud nag po khyod 'di khyed cig
NK035(ci)001:2222: khal che'o khal che'o zhes lan gsum brjod nas drii
NK035(ci)001:2223: chen btang la sas byi bas nas phyi mig mi
NK035(ci)001:2224: blta bar 'bros so rkang pa'i long mo'i rtags la
NK035(ci)001:2225: nyi ma grib chung phebs tsam na nub tu bltas
NK035(ci)001:2226: te gcer bur 'dug pa'i 'phongs su khyi mjug btsugs
NK035(ci)001:2227: mdun du dri chen btang la kham re za zhing
NK035(ci)001:2228: khyi skad re 'don pa lan gsum bya'o so'i rtsa
NK035(ci)001:2229: bar dreg pa byung na ra lpags gyon nas shar
NK035(ci)001:2230: du bltas te ra'i skad lan gsum 'don no sna
NK035(ci)001:2231: zhom pas sna'i rtse mor a bsams la a nyi
NK035(ci)001:2232: shu rtsa gcig brjod cing chu sna dgu'i khrus bya'o
NK035(ci)001:2233: yan lag brkyangs pas yan lag la 'byung ba lnga'i
NK035(ci)001:2234: 'khor lo sngar bzhin rgya skegs kyis bris nas gzugs
NK035(ci)001:2235: chus sngar bzhin bakru'o mig 'bru tshugs su blta na
NK035(ci)001:2236: dge slong la chos ston bya byis pa lo grangs
NK035(ci)001:2237: bsags la ton mo bya gos dmar po gyon no
NK035(ci)001:2238: 'gram pa gshong bur song na s+aats+tsha ser po lo
NK035(ci)001:2239: grangs gdab chu gtor dang sbyin sreg dang dar ljang
NK035(ci)001:2240: khu'i ba dan lo grangs bya zhing e lo grangs
NK035(ci)001:2241: bzlas so dbugs rgod na bu ram gyi lde gu
NK035(ci)001:2242: la rlung gi snying po bzlas nas za'o sna yo
NK035(ci)001:2243: na sna rtser h'u dkar po bsam mo mchi ma
NK035(ci)001:2244: 'dzag na mig tu b+h+r+aum bsam la bzlas so 'gram
NK035(ci)001:2245: pa gshong gi song na k+sham bzlas so so 'thams
NK035(ci)001:2246: na shagra shahwam &a&a&abazlasa so lce la thig le nag
NK035(ci)001:2247: po byung na h'u bsam mo rna ba 'byar na
NK035(ci)001:2248: yum bsam mo brang gi lhen sna zhom na yamm+mu
NK035(ci)001:2249: &&&basama mo rtsa gnyis log med na h+mum&a&a&abasama mo yi
NK035(ci)001:2250: ge de dag ngag tu'ang bzlas shing mtshal dang dri
NK035(ci)001:2251: bzang pos bri ba yang bya'o tshe gzugs kyi phyag
NK035(ci)001:2252: mtshan med na rang gi bla ma la tshogs brgya
NK035(ci)001:2253: rtsa bya'o lag pa g.yas med na 'bru sna bdun
NK035(ci)001:2254: gyi phye la glud khru gang pa seng ge'i mgo
NK035(ci)001:2255: can kha gdengs pa byas te byang bu lo grangs
NK035(ci)001:2256: btsugs nas byang phyogs kyi lam srang du bskyal lo
NK035(ci)001:2257: g.yon med na sre mo'i rlid bur stag nag phag
NK035(ci)001:2258: nag khyi nag gsum gyi mche ba dang dri chus
NK035(ci)001:2259: sbrus pa'i ngar glud blugs la chu la dor ro
NK035(ci)001:2260: rkang pa g.yas pa'i pus mo man chad med na
NK035(ci)001:2261: nyi ma nub tu sa sros dus seng ldeng ngam
NK035(ci)001:2262: rgya shug gi me lo grangs btang ngo g.yon med
NK035(ci)001:2263: na sa dkar po'i glud khru gang gi snying khang
NK035(ci)001:2264: stag pa'i byang bu la lo grangs kyi nyag bris
NK035(ci)001:2265: la btsug nas lha khang 'dre can du tho rengs
NK035(ci)001:2266: bskyal lo mgo'i g.yas med na phung shul gyi sa
NK035(ci)001:2267: sna dgu dang shing nag po'i 'bras bu sbyar te
NK035(ci)001:2268: ga'u nag po ka sbyar byas pa'i nang du rang
NK035(ci)001:2269: gi skra dang gos dum bcug pa'i ga'u'i rgyab tu
NK035(ci)001:2270: lo'i rgyal po rtags 'di khyer sogs lo bcu gnyis
NK035(ci)001:2271: kyi ming glang ma'i byang bu la bris pa btsug
NK035(ci)001:2272: ste tsher ma sna tshogs kyang btsugs nas nam phyed
NK035(ci)001:2273: dus dur khrod du bskyal lo g.yon med na 'bru
NK035(ci)001:2274: sna nyi shu rtsa lnga'i ngar glud kyi snying khar
NK035(ci)001:2275: mi rta khyi gsum gyi rus pa gos dum gyis
NK035(ci)001:2276: drel ba bcug la tshes bcu gcig gi nam sros
NK035(ci)001:2277: dus gom pa brgyad cu'i phyir dong brus par bcug
NK035(ci)001:2278: nas rang gi ming nas bos te ngu ba'i tshul
NK035(ci)001:2279: lan gsum byas la sba'o sked man chad med na
NK035(ci)001:2280: shar lhor tshes ma'i hom lo grangs byas te rim
NK035(ci)001:2281: gyis bsreg cing ram lo grangs brjod do sked dang
NK035(ci)001:2282: bcas pa med na lus ro sol gyis byugs te
NK035(ci)001:2283: skra spyi bor bcings la shog bu sor bzhi la
NK035(ci)001:2284: rang gi lo'i ming dang gnam lo'i ming bris pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2285: phyogs bzhir ram yam lam kham bris pa rang gi
NK035(ci)001:2286: sna la btags te gu gul gyis bdug cing tshes
NK035(ci)001:2287: dgu'i nam phyed dus phyogs bzhir rgyug cing kha la
NK035(ci)001:2288: khyod khyed ces 'brel med pa mang po brjod nas
NK035(ci)001:2289: shog bu de dur khrod du sba'o stod khog med
NK035(ci)001:2290: na me btang nas lo bcu gnyis kyi ming byang
NK035(ci)001:2291: bsreg go smad med na dur khrod du phyin nas
NK035(ci)001:2292: rus pa sna tshogs kyi dud pa btang ngo lus
NK035(ci)001:2293: spyi'i g.yas med na gtsug tor 'don pa tsh+wa tsh+wa
NK035(ci)001:2294: lo grangs bya'o g.yon med na gos dmar po gyon
NK035(ci)001:2295: zhing gzugs grangs med 'don no gnam sa'i 'brel thag
NK035(ci)001:2296: chad na dge ba grub tshad dang gsung rab mang
NK035(ci)001:2297: po klog go seng ge'i mi babs na dkyil 'khor
NK035(ci)001:2298: gyi cho ga lo grangs zhu'o ri thang mtshams su
NK035(ci)001:2299: lhon shing chag na don snod so so'i sman sbyor
NK035(ci)001:2300: bya'o chu'i rlangs pa sngo dmar byung na lo bcu
NK035(ci)001:2301: gnyis kyi gzugs khams la byas te kha dog lngar
NK035(ci)001:2302: bsgyur s+aats+tsha re ngar glud re stag pa'i hom re
NK035(ci)001:2303: byas te nyi ma dmar thag chod dus byang shar
NK035(ci)001:2304: gyi dur khrod du bskyal lo nag po hral hrol
NK035(ci)001:2305: la 'bru sna lcags zangs kyi phye dang bcas pa
NK035(ci)001:2306: phyogs bzhir gtor ro dmar po thig le can la
NK035(ci)001:2307: rang gi dri ma 'dres pa'i ngar glud lo grangs
NK035(ci)001:2308: la gzi mo byi thur re dang dar dmar po'i
NK035(ci)001:2309: ba dan re btsug ste rus pa sna tshogs dang
NK035(ci)001:2310: lhan cig shar gyi lam po cher bskyal lo dri
NK035(ci)001:2311: chen gyi rlangs med na rta thod la 'byung ba'i
NK035(ci)001:2312: sa bon bris te nyi ma mdung gang dus nub
NK035(ci)001:2313: tu bltas te rta skad grangs med gdon no rna
NK035(ci)001:2314: ba'i rlung sgra la zas sna tshogs tshad kyi gtor
NK035(ci)001:2315: ma lo bcu gnyis kyi ming dang bcas pa nub
NK035(ci)001:2316: phyogs kyi sdong po'i drung du bskyal lo skad med
NK035(ci)001:2317: na snying nang du yam bsam la mig gyen du
NK035(ci)001:2318: bsgrad de 'dug pa'i spyi bor gcig gis gzungs chus
NK035(ci)001:2319: bakru'o shing lo langs na tshogs dang dge sbyor la
NK035(ci)001:2320: 'bad do cho ga de dag byas la brtags pas
NK035(ci)001:2321: lan bdun nas lo grangs tsam gyis 'chi ba zlog
NK035(ci)001:2322: nges so 'chi ba bslu ba'i man ngag slob dpon
NK035(ci)001:2323: chen po sh+r+ai sing has mdzad pa rdzogs so rgya
NK035(ci)001:2324: rgya rgya las can gcig dang 'phrad par shog sangs
NK035(ci)001:2325: rgyas dgongs pa mthar thug nges pa'i lung zab cing
NK035(ci)001:2326: rgya che bkod pa chen po'i don rnams las nges
NK035(ci)001:2327: pa'i bka' gsang yongs bsdus snying po'i don 'di ni
NK035(ci)001:2328: dam pa 'jig rten g.yul ngo thams cad bzlog mdzad
NK035(ci)001:2329: pa'i 'jam dpal nyid gyi sprul pa dri med kun
NK035(ci)001:2330: gyi mgon nges pa'i snying po gcig tu dril nas
NK035(ci)001:2331: ni gti mug 'thug pos bcings pa ye shes 'od
NK035(ci)001:2332: du ni rnam par bkrol te rang snang nyid ston
NK035(ci)001:2333: bla ma mgon dri med 'jam dpal sprul pa khyod
NK035(ci)001:2334: la bdag ni 'dud bdag gis gnas skabs bag chags
NK035(ci)001:2335: bsags pa'i lus 'di ni sho sha rab tu bkod
NK035(ci)001:2336: pa'i gling zhes yul du ni rgya nag rigs la
NK035(ci)001:2337: khyim bdag dge ba ldan pa'i yid snang ba gsal
NK035(ci)001:2338: bar byed pa'i lhums su ni grong khyer sho 'khyams
NK035(ci)001:2339: nag po zhes byar bdag ni skyes de nas lo
NK035(ci)001:2340: ni bco lnga dag na byang chub shing drung du
NK035(ci)001:2341: slob dpon mkhas pa ha sti b+ha la las bdag
NK035(ci)001:2342: gis yi ge rtsis dang sgra dang bstan bcos nyan
NK035(ci)001:2343: lo gsum gyis ni mkhas pa'i snyan pa thob de
NK035(ci)001:2344: nas nub phyogs gser gling dag tu 'gro snyam nas
NK035(ci)001:2345: rnga mong stobs ldan dag la zhon nas nub phyogs
NK035(ci)001:2346: phyin bar gyi thang khob snyug tshal 'dam bu'i khrod
NK035(ci)001:2347: du ni sgra chen 'jigs pa'i nga ro nam mkha'
NK035(ci)001:2348: dag nas grags bdag ni dad pa'i shugs kyis nam
NK035(ci)001:2349: mkha' cer bltas bas 'od dpung yid ldan dkyil na
NK035(ci)001:2350: thugs rje chen po nyid 'dzum pa'i zhal dang bde
NK035(ci)001:2351: ba'i phyag rgya mdzad nas ni lung bstan 'bras bu
NK035(ci)001:2352: 'dod na so sa gling du song zhes thos bdag
NK035(ci)001:2353: yid rab tu dga' ba las bdag gi bsam pa
NK035(ci)001:2354: phyir la 'di ltar skyes bdag ni da rung na
NK035(ci)001:2355: gzhon lo brgyad bar du yang 'bras bu nges pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2356: gsang sngags go bya'i phyir gsang sngags mtha' dag la
NK035(ci)001:2357: ni goms par bya snyam nas slar log rgya na
NK035(ci)001:2358: ga shar gyi ri bo rtse lnga la gdol pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2359: slob dpon b+he la kirti las gsang ba'i sngags su
NK035(ci)001:2360: grags pa'i rgyud sde dang lung dang man ngag sgrub
NK035(ci)001:2361: pa'i thabs rnams nyan lo bdun gyis ni bdag gis
NK035(ci)001:2362: ma lus shes snga dro'i gro thon ri bo'i shar
NK035(ci)001:2363: du phyin khrus rdzings dal 'jam nang na khrus byed
NK035(ci)001:2364: 'dug pa las bdag ni yid 'gyur skad cig tsam
NK035(ci)001:2365: du dran pa nyams de nas dran pa nyid ni
NK035(ci)001:2366: sangs nas yar langs pas nam mkhar 'od dbung dkyil
NK035(ci)001:2367: na thugs rje chen po nyid snang bar gyur te
NK035(ci)001:2368: bdag la lung yang bstan de nas bdag gis bsam
NK035(ci)001:2369: pa yang btang ba 'di nas rgya gar yul du
NK035(ci)001:2370: bsgrod cing 'gro ba la 'jigs pa'i gcan gzan khyung
NK035(ci)001:2371: dang rigs med mon gdug pa rnams kyis lam ni
NK035(ci)001:2372: gtser snyam nas lo gsum bar du rdzu 'phrul sna
NK035(ci)001:2373: 'gal bsgrubs de nas rdzu 'phrul stobs kyis sa la
NK035(ci)001:2374: khru gang du reg pa med par rlung gis bskyod
NK035(ci)001:2375: du phyin nyin zhag dgu na dur khrod so so'i
NK035(ci)001:2376: gling 'jam dpal sprul pa nyid dang bdag mjal nas
NK035(ci)001:2377: yun gyi sgrib pa ma sbyangs gnas su dag nyi
NK035(ci)001:2378: shu rtsa lnga'i bar du 'bras bu'i yang zhun rnams
NK035(ci)001:2379: nyams su blangs shing yang snying zhu dag byas gsang
NK035(ci)001:2380: ba'i rgyud dang man ngag yi ge rnams dam pa
NK035(ci)001:2381: nyid kyis lung bstan rdo rje gdan nas phyung khyer
NK035(ci)001:2382: nas slar log rgya nag dag tu phyin byang chub
NK035(ci)001:2383: shing drung sangs rgyas 'byung ba'i gnas yang steng dag
NK035(ci)001:2384: gi brang khang sprel ma ru gsang ba'i rgyud dang
NK035(ci)001:2385: man ngag lung dang ni dam pas lung bstan bdag
NK035(ci)001:2386: gis sde bzhir phyes sde gsum spros bcas don du
NK035(ci)001:2387: sdebs nas ni lha khang bya 'dab 'og gi ka
NK035(ci)001:2388: ba bzhi sgril nang zangs kyi sgrom bur de dag
NK035(ci)001:2389: stsal nas ni phyi rabs don du rgya yis btab
NK035(ci)001:2390: ste sbas yang gab sbas pa'i snying tig sgron ma
NK035(ci)001:2391: 'di bdag gi snying dang gzugs kyi phung po bzhin
NK035(ci)001:2392: 'bral ba'i skabs med lus la rtag tu bcangs de
NK035(ci)001:2393: nas nam zhig shing nags 'thug po ru bdag gis
NK035(ci)001:2394: gsang ba'i nyams bskyangs lus kyi spyod pa brtsams de
NK035(ci)001:2395: nas nam phyed dus kyi thun gcig rmi lam na
NK035(ci)001:2396: bdag gi ma ru byas pa'i bud med rgyan ldan
NK035(ci)001:2397: zhig bu gcig longs dang gsang ba yang bsdu snying
NK035(ci)001:2398: po rnams bkra shis khri sgo'i ka ba'i 'og tu
NK035(ci)001:2399: sbos rang rgyas thob la bstan pa'i btsas su zhog
NK035(ci)001:2400: de skad zer bas ka ba'i dkyil du ni rang
NK035(ci)001:2401: rgyas btab nas 'di ni de ru sbas smug nag
NK035(ci)001:2402: 'jigs pa'i gzugs can sngags kyis srungs e ka tsa
NK035(ci)001:2403: ti khros ma rag gdong ma bstan pa'i snying po
NK035(ci)001:2404: 'di gtad bka' 'di srungs lung dang mi ldan ban
NK035(ci)001:2405: 'dras 'di khyer na khyod ni smug nag srog la
NK035(ci)001:2406: rngam pa'i 'khor rab tu mi bsrun sha dang khrag
NK035(ci)001:2407: 'dod rnams de yi sha dang khrag la longs spyod
NK035(ci)001:2408: gyis skal ldan snying gi bu dang 'phrad pa'i tshe
NK035(ci)001:2409: 'di rnams byin la khyod kyis stong grogs gyis rtsis
NK035(ci)001:2410: dang gto dang khram la dpyad rnams ni ri bo
NK035(ci)001:2411: rtse lnga'i shar gyi dkyil ngos sbos mchog tu zab
NK035(ci)001:2412: pa'i yang zab snying po'i chos dkon pa'i rin chen
NK035(ci)001:2413: mig gi 'bras bu 'di nam zhig 'byung ba'i dus
NK035(ci)001:2414: ni byung ba na dad brtson shes rab ldan pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2415: spyod yul las gzhan la bshad cing bstan pa'i gnas
NK035(ci)001:2416: med pas rang gi sems la rgya yis thob la
NK035(ci)001:2417: brnogs 'chi ba nyid las bzlog pa'i man ngag 'di
NK035(ci)001:2418: bdag gis nyams blangs 'chi dus lan gsum bzlog de
NK035(ci)001:2419: yi phyir na nyams su len pa'i grogs gzhan la
NK035(ci)001:2420: mi ltos phyir na 'di dag bris a ti'i rang
NK035(ci)001:2421: nga spros pa kun bral yang sems can blo yi
NK035(ci)001:2422: dri ma ma zad bar 'di dag rnams kyang kun
NK035(ci)001:2423: rdzob bden pa'o don dam nyid la skye shi'i sdug
NK035(ci)001:2424: bsngal bral zhes sh+r+ai sing has gsungs so rgya gar
NK035(ci)001:2425: gyi mkhan po bi ma la mi tras sgra rang
NK035(ci)001:2426: 'gyur du bsgyur ba'o rgya rgya rgya tha /
NK035(ci)001:2432: &&& rgya gar skad du gri tri pa sam hi
NK035(ci)001:2433: n+aa ma bod skad du lta ba'i snying po zhes
NK035(ci)001:2434: bya ba stong pa chen po ye nas thabs kyis
NK035(ci)001:2435: grub pa nyid la phyag 'tshal lo sangs rgyas kun
NK035(ci)001:2436: gyi bde ba chen po de mngon sum nyid du
NK035(ci)001:2437: gtan la phab na ni snang ba cer mthong goms
NK035(ci)001:2438: pa'i tshad rnams la nyams blangs phyogs shing don la
NK035(ci)001:2439: mi mos na 'di ltar yid kyi phyogs la gtad
NK035(ci)001:2440: par gyis dngos po'i 'dug tshul dran pa rang dag
NK035(ci)001:2441: pas yod med mtha' bral sgra tshig ming yang med
NK035(ci)001:2442: bya dang byed dang bcos pa'i mtha' mi srid de
NK035(ci)001:2443: yi don rnams phyogs gcig nyid du yang bla ma'i
NK035(ci)001:2444: lung la brten nas bstan par bya kye ma kye
NK035(ci)001:2445: ma rjes su 'dzin pa'i mkha' 'gro ma khyod nyon
NK035(ci)001:2446: cig gsang ba yang nas yang du bsdus pa'i man
NK035(ci)001:2447: ngag gi snying po 'di med par phyi dang nang
NK035(ci)001:2448: dang gsang ba gsum la gding 'cha' ba'i skyes bu
NK035(ci)001:2449: ni rnam shes kyi snying med pa'i ro la don
NK035(ci)001:2450: du 'dzin pa'i skyes bu dang 'dra'o de'i phyir na
NK035(ci)001:2451: ngo mtshar gyi gad mo bcu gnyis rgyud rnams kyi
NK035(ci)001:2452: khong don du mdzad pa bdag gis bstan gyis ma
NK035(ci)001:2453: yengs par nyon cig lta ba rang byung ye shes
NK035(ci)001:2454: la ltos dang dge sdig dang lta sgom las 'das
NK035(ci)001:2455: pa ngo mtshar gzhi ma bskyod bar lus ngag gi
NK035(ci)001:2456: bya ba ci byas kyang phan gnod dang bral ba
NK035(ci)001:2457: ha ha chos kyi sku stong ba kun khyab kyi
NK035(ci)001:2458: ye shes la ltos dang skye ba med pa ye
NK035(ci)001:2459: nas lhan cig tu gnas pa ngo mtshar skyes bus
NK035(ci)001:2460: mtshon thogs nas 'gro ba rnams dus gcig la bsgral
NK035(ci)001:2461: yang gang zag gi rgyud la phan gnod dang bral
NK035(ci)001:2462: ba ha ha shes pa stong pa kun snang gi
NK035(ci)001:2463: ye shes la ltos dang gang snang thams cad rang
NK035(ci)001:2464: gi grogs su shar ba ngo mtshar cir snang rang
NK035(ci)001:2465: gi gzhi las g.yos ba med pa ha ha rig
NK035(ci)001:2466: pa stong pa kun grol gyi snang ba la ltos
NK035(ci)001:2467: dang rang gi gnyen por rang che ba la ngo
NK035(ci)001:2468: mtshar nyon mongs pa rnams rang gis rang grol ba
NK035(ci)001:2469: ha ha rig pa ye nas stong ba kun dag
NK035(ci)001:2470: gi ngo bo la ltos dang 'bad rtsol me pa
NK035(ci)001:2471: 'bras bu rnyed pa ngo mtshar gcig zin pas 'khor
NK035(ci)001:2472: 'das thams cad gnyis med du dag pa ha ha
NK035(ci)001:2473: ngo bo stong pa chen po kun bzhag gi tshad
NK035(ci)001:2474: la ltos dang 'gro drug sku gsum du snang ba
NK035(ci)001:2475: ngo mtshar 'gro ba rnams kyis sgom pa rdul tsam
NK035(ci)001:2476: ma byas par dus gcig la sangs rgya ba ha
NK035(ci)001:2477: ha sku gsum stong pa chen po ye rdzogs kyi
NK035(ci)001:2478: 'bras bu la ltos dang dus gsum 'bral ba med
NK035(ci)001:2479: pa ngo mtshar pho rol tu phyin pa drug ma
NK035(ci)001:2480: spyad par tshogs rnams dus gcig la rdzogs pa ha
NK035(ci)001:2481: ha rig pa cer bzhag chen po kun mnyam gyi
NK035(ci)001:2482: ye shes la ltos dang bya byed thams cad rgyan
NK035(ci)001:2483: du shar ba ngo mtshar spong len thams cad lta
NK035(ci)001:2484: bas grol ba ha ha stong pa'i stong pa ye
NK035(ci)001:2485: stong chen po la ltos dang sangs rgyas thams cad
NK035(ci)001:2486: g.yang sar 'dug pa ngo mtshar bya byed sgom pas
NK035(ci)001:2487: ltung bar 'gyur ba ha ha mi stong pa'i stong
NK035(ci)001:2488: pa dngos can la ltos dang med pa la bdag
NK035(ci)001:2489: tu 'dzin pa'i theg pa ngo mtshar skyes pas skyes
NK035(ci)001:2490: med thob pa ha ha lta ba'i gzhi 'dzin pa
NK035(ci)001:2491: stong pa'i yul dngos po lam du byed pa ngo
NK035(ci)001:2492: mtshar gyi gad mo bcu gnyis ba rdzogs so rgya
NK035(ci)001:2493: rgya rgya e ma nyon cig bla na med pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2494: gsang chen nges pa 'di ma mthong bar phyi nang
NK035(ci)001:2495: gsang ba gsum la gding 'cha' ba'i skyes bu ni
NK035(ci)001:2496: blta bar 'dod kyang dbral ba'i mig med pa dang
NK035(ci)001:2497: 'dra'o de'i phyir na gzhi'i ngom tshig dgu la goms
