NK035(ci)001:2498: pa gces so mi 'gyur ba gzhi la dran pa
NK035(ci)001:2499: rang dag dran med kyi skye ba bkag pas blo
NK035(ci)001:2500: 'das skye rgyun med pa ngom pa'i tshig tu byung
NK035(ci)001:2501: ba'o chos sku rang snang gzhan byung gi snang ba
NK035(ci)001:2502: rang dag pa ni sgra dang dri ro mya ngan
NK035(ci)001:2503: las 'da' bar byed pas lung kun gyi bdag nyid
NK035(ci)001:2504: du byung ba ni ngom pa'i tshig tu byung ba'o
NK035(ci)001:2505: nyon mongs rang rgyas btab pa'i gzhi chos kun gyi
NK035(ci)001:2506: bdag nyid du byung bas 'khrul pa rang sar dag
NK035(ci)001:2507: pa ngom pa'i tshig tu byung ba'o 'dzin pa yul
NK035(ci)001:2508: thams cad gcig tu mthong ba snang ba rang rgyas
NK035(ci)001:2509: btab pa ni ngom pa'i tshig tu byung ba'o de
NK035(ci)001:2510: nyid 'gyed pa med par snang ba kun gyi bdag
NK035(ci)001:2511: por ye nas 'dug pas sgo lnga rang sar dag
NK035(ci)001:2512: pa ngom pa'i tshig tu byung ba'o 'byed pa med
NK035(ci)001:2513: pa'i shes rab kyis bsdus yig la mkhas pa ni
NK035(ci)001:2514: spros med du la bzla bas ngom pa'i tshig tu
NK035(ci)001:2515: byung ba'o chos rnams cog bzhag gi lta ba dgongs
NK035(ci)001:2516: pa dang 'brel ba ni lta ba ngom pa'i tshig
NK035(ci)001:2517: tu byung ba'o sgro 'dogs thams cad dus gcig la
NK035(ci)001:2518: chod pa'i tshig gis rnal 'byor pa grol sar bskyal
NK035(ci)001:2519: ba ni theg pa thams cad ngom pa'i tshig tu
NK035(ci)001:2520: byung ba'o rang snang sgron ma gnyen po la ma
NK035(ci)001:2521: ltos pa rang snang ba ni rtags thams cad kyi
NK035(ci)001:2522: ngom pa'i tshig tu byung ba'o gzhi snang 'khrul pa
NK035(ci)001:2523: dag pas chos rnams spar gyis zin lam du gol
NK035(ci)001:2524: sa chod bas re dogs tshigs mtha' chod bla ma'i
NK035(ci)001:2525: gsung bzhin bsgrubs pas dngos grub myur du thob shes
NK035(ci)001:2526: rab rnon por skyes pas chos can dum bur bshig
NK035(ci)001:2527: ngom pa'i tshig dgus gzhi'i bcud phyung ba rdzogs so
NK035(ci)001:2528: rgya rgya rgya kye ma rigs kyi bu gsang ba
NK035(ci)001:2529: yang zhun nges pa'i lta ba rang byung gi rgyal
NK035(ci)001:2530: po ma mthong bar phyi nang gsang ba'i lta ba
NK035(ci)001:2531: mun rdo lta bu la yid 'cha' ba'i gang zag
NK035(ci)001:2532: ni 'ben med par skyes bus mda' 'phen pa dang
NK035(ci)001:2533: 'dra ste gang du babs ngo mi shes so de'i
NK035(ci)001:2534: phyir khyad par du 'phags pa'i tshig bcu gcig la
NK035(ci)001:2535: mkhas par bya'o srog ma bcad na dge ba mi
NK035(ci)001:2536: 'phel bas spyod pa thams cad las khyad par du
NK035(ci)001:2537: 'phags te ya mtshan sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa ma
NK035(ci)001:2538: nub na zhing khams mi 'phel bas yul thams cad
NK035(ci)001:2539: las khyad par du 'phags te ya mtshan dmyal ba
NK035(ci)001:2540: rnams la mchod pa ma phul na dngos grub mi
NK035(ci)001:2541: 'byung bas nyams len thams cad las khyad par du
NK035(ci)001:2542: 'phags te ya mtshan sdug bsngal thams cad dang du
NK035(ci)001:2543: ma blangs na bde ba nyid gtan la phebs mi
NK035(ci)001:2544: srid pas sgom pa thams cad las khyad par du
NK035(ci)001:2545: 'phags te ya mtshan ma skyes pa thams cad skyes
NK035(ci)001:2546: par ma byas na skye med rnyed mi srid pas
NK035(ci)001:2547: 'bras bu thams cad las khyad par du 'phags te
NK035(ci)001:2548: ya mtshan 'byung ba ma 'phel na nyams mi skyong
NK035(ci)001:2549: bas dgongs pa thams cad las khyad par du 'phags
NK035(ci)001:2550: te ya mtshan sems can ma 'phel na 'khor ba
NK035(ci)001:2551: nyid dong mi sprugs pas gzhi thams cad las khyad
NK035(ci)001:2552: par du 'phags te ya mtshan snying rje'i rgyun thag
NK035(ci)001:2553: ma bcad na thugs rje mi 'byung bas mdzad pa
NK035(ci)001:2554: thams khyad par du 'phags te ya mtshan ma rig
NK035(ci)001:2555: pa ma bsgoms na 'khrul pa mi 'dag pas rtsa
NK035(ci)001:2556: ba thams cad las khyad par du 'phags te ya
NK035(ci)001:2557: mtshan ma btsal rang las rnyed pa'i nor bu rin
NK035(ci)001:2558: chen de ma bsgoms gzhi la bzhag pa'i man ngag
NK035(ci)001:2559: rin po che ma bsgrubs cig car 'byung ba'i rang
NK035(ci)001:2560: rig 'od po che ma song gnas su phyin pas
NK035(ci)001:2561: snying po ye dag nyid rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen
NK035(ci)001:2562: po'i don la the tshom mi za bar bstan pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2563: phyiir gzhi thams cad kyi bcud phyung nas lung kun
NK035(ci)001:2564: gyi rgyan du bkod pa khyad par 'phags pa'i tshig
NK035(ci)001:2565: dgus gtan la phab pa rdzogs so rgya rgya rgya
NK035(ci)001:2566: e ma ho gsang ba yang gsang snying tig gi
NK035(ci)001:2567: don ma mthong bar phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi
NK035(ci)001:2568: ngo spros la yid ches par byed pa'i gang zag
NK035(ci)001:2569: ni rgyu kha ba'i sa bon las 'bras bu mngar
NK035(ci)001:2570: ba 'dod pa dang 'dra'o de'i phyir na rang byung
NK035(ci)001:2571: gi che ba bcu drug pa 'di goms par bya'o
NK035(ci)001:2572: dngos po gshis la tshig dang brjod bya ma grub
NK035(ci)001:2573: pa'i phyir sangs rgyas rnams kyi slob dpon du dmyal
NK035(ci)001:2574: ba rang byung ba'o rig pa nyid la srog med
NK035(ci)001:2575: pa'i phyir srog bcad pas dge ba 'phel ba rang
NK035(ci)001:2576: byung ba'o 'dug tshul la bzang ngan med pa'i phyir
NK035(ci)001:2577: sangs rgyas bas sems can snga bar rang byung ba'o
NK035(ci)001:2578: rig pa rtsol sgrub dang bral ba'i phyir mi rtog
NK035(ci)001:2579: pa bsgom pa'i sgom chen bas shan pa sngon du
NK035(ci)001:2580: sangs rgya bar rang byung ba'o lam nye ring med
NK035(ci)001:2581: pa'i phyir sa bcu'i sems dpa' bas mtshams med pa
NK035(ci)001:2582: lnga byas pa'i gang zag rdzu 'phrul che bar rang
NK035(ci)001:2583: byung ba'o lta ba la mtho dman med pa'i phyir
NK035(ci)001:2584: nyan thos dgra bcom pa bas mu stegs rtag chad
NK035(ci)001:2585: sngon du sangs rgya bar rang byung ba'o sgom pa
NK035(ci)001:2586: la bar mtshams med pa'i phyir bsam gtan rang lugs
NK035(ci)001:2587: su gnas pa'i rang sangs rgyas bas grub mtha'i tshig
NK035(ci)001:2588: med pa'i skye bos 'bras bu sngon du thob par
NK035(ci)001:2589: rang byung ba'o spyod pa la zin pa med pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2590: phyir brtul zhugs chen po dur khrod du rgyu ba
NK035(ci)001:2591: las byis pa gshed ma bye ba snang ba la
NK035(ci)001:2592: dbang du bsgyur bar rang byung ba'o 'bras bu la
NK035(ci)001:2593: sems med pa'i phyir sngon byung gi kun tu bzang
NK035(ci)001:2594: po dang shan pa rnams khyad med du rang byung
NK035(ci)001:2595: ba'o shes pas bsdus pa thams cad gzhi gcig pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2596: phyir sems can gyi thugs rjes sangs rgyas la skyob
NK035(ci)001:2597: par rang byung ba'o gzhi bslab bya dang bral ba'i
NK035(ci)001:2598: phyir rang gi man ngag ston pa'i bla ma bas
NK035(ci)001:2599: sde snod la las dang po pa 'byongs par rang
NK035(ci)001:2600: byung ba'i rig pa la gol sgrib med pa'i phyir
NK035(ci)001:2601: sems can 'bum gyi srog bton pa'i dge slong dang
NK035(ci)001:2602: sems can 'bum gyi srog bcad pa'i rgyal po gnyis
NK035(ci)001:2603: 'tshang rgya ba la khyad par med par rang byung
NK035(ci)001:2604: ngo dngos po la tshig med pa'i phyir sde snod
NK035(ci)001:2605: shes pa'i pan+di ta bas ba glang rdzi chos mkhas
NK035(ci)001:2606: par rang byung ngo ngo bo la sdug bsngal med
NK035(ci)001:2607: pas dmyal ba'i grol sa sangs rgyas yin par rang
NK035(ci)001:2608: byung ngo stong pa la go mtshams med pa'i phyir
NK035(ci)001:2609: stong pa nyid la 'byongs pa'i skyes bu bas mu
NK035(ci)001:2610: stegs bas mthong bar rang byung ngo snang ba bsgom
NK035(ci)001:2611: mi dgos pa'i phyir chos kyi dbyings las 'byung bar
NK035(ci)001:2612: rang byung ngo ma bltas cig car mthong ba'i sgron
NK035(ci)001:2613: me 'od po che ma brten rang la bzhag pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2614: yon tan gter po che ma bsnyags rang la gnas
NK035(ci)001:2615: pa'i bde ba skyid po che chos rnams ye nas
NK035(ci)001:2616: dag pas rang la rang drin che 'dug tshul rang
NK035(ci)001:2617: snang du bkod pa'i man ngag dran pa rang yal
NK035(ci)001:2618: gyi thabs gzhi'i don gtan la phab pa che ba
NK035(ci)001:2619: bcu drug pa rdzogs so rgya rgya rgya e ma
NK035(ci)001:2620: ho rigs kyi bu yang gab sbas pa'i snying tig
NK035(ci)001:2621: 'di yi tshad ma zin par phyi nang gsang ba'i
NK035(ci)001:2622: bar do gzhi la phugs gtod pa ni nam mkha'i
NK035(ci)001:2623: sprin la 'dzol 'dzug pa'i sems can dang 'dra'o de'i
NK035(ci)001:2624: phyir na khyad med du bstan pa'i tshig don bdun
NK035(ci)001:2625: la bslab par bya'o rig pa skye shi dang bral
NK035(ci)001:2626: ba'i gnad kyis sems can bye ba'i srog bcad pa
NK035(ci)001:2627: dang pha rol tu phyin pa bcu la gnas pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2628: gang zag la khyad par rdul tsam yang med par
NK035(ci)001:2629: kun tu bzang po la bstan to chos nyid la
NK035(ci)001:2630: spros pa med pa'i gnad kyis stong pa nyid sgom
NK035(ci)001:2631: pa'i skyes bu dang skad cig kyang mi sgom pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2632: gang zag gnyis 'tshang rgya ba la khyad par rdul
NK035(ci)001:2633: tsam yang med par kun tu bzang pos bstan to
NK035(ci)001:2634: rig pa 'dus ma byas pa'i gnad kyis 'dus byas
NK035(ci)001:2635: kyi dge ba dpag tu med pa byas pa'i dad
NK035(ci)001:2636: pa can dang sdig can gnyis la tshogs rdzogs pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2637: sgo nas khyad par rdul tsam yang med par kun
NK035(ci)001:2638: tu bzang pos bstan to rig pa'i ye shes la
NK035(ci)001:2639: 'gro 'ong med pa'i gnad kyis chos nyid kyi rtags
NK035(ci)001:2640: du ma dang ldan pa'i skyes bu dang thos bsam
NK035(ci)001:2641: la ma sbyangs pa gnyis khyad par rdul tsam yang
NK035(ci)001:2642: med par kun tu bzang pos bstan to chos nyid
NK035(ci)001:2643: la skye 'gag med pa'i gnad kyis dmyal ba'i sdug
NK035(ci)001:2644: bsngal myong dgos pa'i sdig can dang bde ba'i 'bras
NK035(ci)001:2645: bu myong nges pa'i skyes bu gnyis la khyad par
NK035(ci)001:2646: rdul tsam yang med par kun tu bzang pos bstan
NK035(ci)001:2647: to rig pa la 'gyur ba med gnad kyis chos
NK035(ci)001:2648: kyi spros pa chod pa'i skyes bu dang bdag tu
NK035(ci)001:2649: lta ba gnyis khyad par rdul tsam yang med par
NK035(ci)001:2650: kun tu bzang pos bstan to chos sku rang la
NK035(ci)001:2651: yod pa'i gnad kyis phyir mchod bstod sna tshogs byas
NK035(ci)001:2652: pa'i skyes bu dang nyal ba gnyis la khyad par
NK035(ci)001:2653: rdul tsam yang med par kun tu bzang pos bstan
NK035(ci)001:2654: to rang bzhin nyag gcig mthong bas lta ba'i lta
NK035(ci)001:2655: bar gyur mnyam bzhag zung 'jug shes pas sgom pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2656: sgom par gyur rtsal chen yongs rdzogs shes pas spyod
NK035(ci)001:2657: pa'i spyod par gyur rang dag cer tshad zin pas
NK035(ci)001:2658: 'bras bu'i 'bras bur gyur 'di ltar rgyud la 'byongs
NK035(ci)001:2659: na kun tu bzang po'i lam gzhi'i ngom tshig lam
NK035(ci)001:2660: gyi khyad med 'bras bu'i rang mnyam du gtan la
NK035(ci)001:2661: phab pa khyad med bdun pa rdzogs so rgya rgya
NK035(ci)001:2662: rgya e ma ho 'dir ni yang gsang don bstan
NK035(ci)001:2663: pa tshogs dang mchod pa'i rim pa yi dge sbyor
NK035(ci)001:2664: rnams ni rgyud thag gcad thos dang bsam dang sgom
NK035(ci)001:2665: pa yis ngan song gsum gyi 'dun sa byed lta
NK035(ci)001:2666: dang sgom dang spyod pa yis sdug bsngal rnams kyi
NK035(ci)001:2667: phung po 'dzin lha dang gtor ma dkyil 'khor gyis
NK035(ci)001:2668: 'khor ba'i bag chags rten par byed sngags dang ting
NK035(ci)001:2669: 'dzin bstod gsol gyis 'jig rten dri ma sna tshogs
NK035(ci)001:2670: sdud theg pa'i ris dang grub mtha' yis rang gi
NK035(ci)001:2671: de nyid 'dam du 'ching dad dang shes rab brtson
NK035(ci)001:2672: 'grus kyis thar pa'i lam chen sgrib par byed dbang
NK035(ci)001:2673: dang dam tshig sdom pa yis bla ma'i byin rlabs
NK035(ci)001:2674: spong bar byed goms dang drod tshad rtags rnams kyis
NK035(ci)001:2675: sku gsum 'bras bu bslu bar byed bla ma sangs
NK035(ci)001:2676: rgyas yi dam gyis ngan song gsum du bying bar
NK035(ci)001:2677: byed sgrub dang sgrub pa chen po yis lha yi
NK035(ci)001:2678: sku rnams spong bar byed sbyin dang bzod dang brtson
NK035(ci)001:2679: 'grus kyis 'khor ba'i sgo nyid spel bar byed de
NK035(ci)001:2680: phyir ye shes ye shes las ye shes nyid ni
NK035(ci)001:2681: khyad par che srog bcad pas ni bde ba thob
NK035(ci)001:2682: ma byin len pa nges pa'i lam mi tshangs spyod
NK035(ci)001:2683: pas bde stong rtogs mdor na lus ngag 'dod yon
NK035(ci)001:2684: rnams ji ltar spyad kyang de rang nyid lta ba'i
NK035(ci)001:2685: snying po zhes bya ba slob dpon mkhas pa chen
NK035(ci)001:2686: po ye shes mdos rgyud kun gyi khong don du
NK035(ci)001:2687: mdzad pa rdzogs so rgya rgya rgya sangs rgyas rnams
NK035(ci)001:2688: kyi thugs kyi dgongs brgyud pa'i thugs rje mchog gi
NK035(ci)001:2689: sprul pa mi lus can 'jig rten las gtso dam
NK035(ci)001:2690: pa dri med mgon sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs
NK035(ci)001:2691: rmad po che dam pa nges pa'i skal ldan nyid
NK035(ci)001:2692: la ni bdag gis spyi bos zhabs la rab btud
NK035(ci)001:2693: nas mgon po bdag 'ching gcod la phyag 'tshal lo
NK035(ci)001:2694: bkang gsang nges pa'i lung rab snang ba 'di bka'
NK035(ci)001:2695: yi byin rlabs rim nas rim brgyud pa bdag gi
NK035(ci)001:2696: blo la nges pa'i 'bras bu 'di nges pa'i shes
NK035(ci)001:2697: pa rtogs te rtags 'di dag 'di la goms pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2698: stobs kyis shar ba yin dang po nyid nas yod
NK035(ci)001:2699: pa ma yin te bdag gi yul ni rgya gar
NK035(ci)001:2700: shar phyogs su rigs na gdol pa rab tu dman
NK035(ci)001:2701: pa'i rigs pha ni shan ting lag pa zhes bya
NK035(ci)001:2702: dang ma ni dge sems byams ma shes bya'i bur
NK035(ci)001:2703: bdag ni skye ba'i lus blangs nas da lta'i lus
NK035(ci)001:2704: la thug bar ro de dus phung po bag chags
NK035(ci)001:2705: la da lta'i rtags 'di ga la srid de phyir
NK035(ci)001:2706: 'di la rab goms nas rtags ni 'dod pa med
NK035(ci)001:2707: bzhin 'byung sngon gyi phung po dar ba'i dus sde
NK035(ci)001:2708: snod rnams la blo sbyangs nas theg pa rnams kyi
NK035(ci)001:2709: spros pa bcad de nas rdo rje gdan drung yod
NK035(ci)001:2710: phyag rgya yi ni rgya chen dang dus kyi 'gro
NK035(ci)001:2711: don khams bsangs pas nub phyogs 'dam bu'i tshal gnas
NK035(ci)001:2712: tshe nam mkha' mi mjed bar snang nas rdo rje
NK035(ci)001:2713: sems dpa' zhes bya'i sku mig gi yul du mngon
NK035(ci)001:2714: pa ru snang bar gyur te lung yang bstan rgya
NK035(ci)001:2715: nag rigs ni yin par grags de nas gnyis kyis
NK035(ci)001:2716: slar log nas so so'i grong khang nang du yong
NK035(ci)001:2717: bdag ni le los bcings te g.yengs de dus dam
NK035(ci)001:2718: pa'i lus ma blangs phyis ni bi ma la dang
NK035(ci)001:2719: phrad bdag kyang dad dang brtson 'grus sprug dam pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2720: byin rlabs snying la zhugs lam yang nam mkha' dag
NK035(ci)001:2721: las phyung byang chub 'byung ba'i shing drung du bla
NK035(ci)001:2722: ma la dmigs lus kyis brtol dam pa nyid ni
NK035(ci)001:2723: mi snang bar bdag ni shes pa yid kyang 'khrugs
NK035(ci)001:2724: de nas phyogs ni kun tu bltas gzhan ni gang
NK035(ci)001:2725: yang ma mthong bar bud med ldem bag chu ban
NK035(ci)001:2726: khur dung so 'khor ba smin ma g.yu dpral ba'i
NK035(ci)001:2727: gnyer ma gyen la langs shin tu mtshan ldan gcig
NK035(ci)001:2728: na re dam pa nges pa'i lung 'dod na bkra
NK035(ci)001:2729: shis khri sgor snang bar 'gyur zhes bstan bdag gis
NK035(ci)001:2730: der phyin pas thugs rje'i mnga' bdag nyid dang phrad
NK035(ci)001:2731: byin rlabs rim pa de ru zhus yun ring sgrib
NK035(ci)001:2732: pa ma sbyangs par rang bzhin gyis ni gnas su
NK035(ci)001:2733: dag sku gsum rang nges lung yang thob lo ni
NK035(ci)001:2734: bcu bdun bar dag tu dam pa'i mdzad spyod rten
NK035(ci)001:2735: 'brel bltas bla ma 'byung ba rang dengs su nam
NK035(ci)001:2736: mkha' 'od kyis bkang ste gshegs byin rlabs tshig gi
NK035(ci)001:2737: spros pa bcad bla mas lung nyid rab bstan pas
NK035(ci)001:2738: thig le mchog gi yi ge rnams khyer te b+ha
NK035(ci)001:2739: sing nags su phyin mdor na man ngag nges pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2740: don mkha' 'gro rnams kyi gdung ba bcad skal ldan
NK035(ci)001:2741: snying gi bu gcig po bi ma mi tra khyod
NK035(ci)001:2742: la gtad 'di la rab tu goms par mdzod gal
NK035(ci)001:2743: te 'di la ma goms na ma spyad bzhag pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2744: gter dang 'dra de bas 'di la goms pa gces
NK035(ci)001:2745: nam zhig skal lda na gnyis nas gsum bzhi las
NK035(ci)001:2746: mang na mkha' 'gros 'tshod snying dang 'dra ba'i rigs
NK035(ci)001:2747: la gtod rang gar btang na rang srog 'tshig de
NK035(ci)001:2748: bas snying la rab tu brnogs zhes ye shes mdos
NK035(ci)001:2749: gsungs so rgya rgya rgya las can de dang 'phrad
NK035(ci)001:2750: par shog rgya gar gyi mkhas pa chen po bi
NK035(ci)001:2751: ma la mi tras sgra rang 'gyur du bsgyur ba'o
NK035(ci)001:2752: smug nag khros ma'i rgyal mo e ka tsa ti
NK035(ci)001:2753: dang dpal mgon po nag po la gtad do srungs
NK035(ci)001:2754: shig rgya rgya rgya rgya gar skad du sa mun
NK035(ci)001:2755: tra sarba no pi ka ka ta pa ta na
NK035(ci)001:2756: ha n+aa ma bod skad du snang ba 'dus pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2757: bcud phur zhes bya ba bcom ldan 'das mngon par
NK035(ci)001:2758: byang chub pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo 'jig rten
NK035(ci)001:2759: khams na dkon pa'i rin chen 'di phyi rabs rnal
NK035(ci)001:2760: 'byor rnams kyi don nyid du bla ma'i lung dang
NK035(ci)001:2761: mthun par bdag gis bkod snang ba rnams kyis dngos
NK035(ci)001:2762: la gang bsgribs pa de yi mdo rnams gsal bar
NK035(ci)001:2763: bya ba'i phyir tshig nyung don 'dus gsal bar gtan
NK035(ci)001:2764: la dbab 'khrul pa'i snang ba nyid kyi gang bcings
NK035(ci)001:2765: pa de nyid grol ba'i thabs 'di mchog tu bzung
NK035(ci)001:2766: sems sogs nyon mongs rnams kyis gang bsgribs pa de
NK035(ci)001:2767: nyid sel bar 'dod pa'i skal ldan rnams yi ge
NK035(ci)001:2768: 'di la rtag tu goms par mdzod snang ba thams
NK035(ci)001:2769: cad snang ba'i bdag por byung ba ni rdo rje
NK035(ci)001:2770: sems dpa'i rdo rje sems dpa' yin zhes pa ni
NK035(ci)001:2771: 'gro drug 'khrul pa'i snang ba med na ni chos
NK035(ci)001:2772: can gyi gzhi med pas las dang po bas 'gro
NK035(ci)001:2773: drug 'khrul pa'i snang ba tsam 'byongs pa shin tu
NK035(ci)001:2774: gces so ye shes sgyu ma'i snang ba med na
NK035(ci)001:2775: sems can gyi lam chad pas las dang po bas
NK035(ci)001:2776: dpe rnams goms par bya ste ye shes sgyu ma'i
NK035(ci)001:2777: snang ba tsam shes pa gal che'o rig pa mngon
NK035(ci)001:2778: sum gyi snang ba med na skyes bu rnams kyis
NK035(ci)001:2779: 'bad rtsol ci byas kyang rang sangs mi rgya bas
NK035(ci)001:2780: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis rig pa mngon sum gyi
NK035(ci)001:2781: snang ba la goms pa gces so bde gshegs gdul
NK035(ci)001:2782: bya'i snang ba med na rten gyi gang zag rnams
NK035(ci)001:2783: sangs rgyas pa'i dus na sprul sku'i zhing mi shes
NK035(ci)001:2784: pas bde gshegs gdul bya'i snang ba la rtsa la
NK035(ci)001:2785: rdzogs pa rab tu gces so 'khrul pa rang dag
NK035(ci)001:2786: gi snang ba med na nyams su blangs kyang tshe
NK035(ci)001:2787: 'di ru rtags mi phyin pas skal ldan rnams kyi
NK035(ci)001:2788: 'khrul pa rang dag gi snang ba la tshad du
NK035(ci)001:2789: zin pa rab tu gces so chos nyid rang zad
NK035(ci)001:2790: kyi snang ba med na rtags dang rdzu 'phrul bsam
NK035(ci)001:2791: gyis mi khyab pa yod kyang 'bras bu la thug
NK035(ci)001:2792: pa med pas na chos nyid rang zad kyi snang
NK035(ci)001:2793: ba zad sar rab tu skyol ba gces so ngo
NK035(ci)001:2794: bo ka dag gi snang ba med na skyes bu
NK035(ci)001:2795: rnams kyis 'bras bu zad sar bskyal yang rig pa
NK035(ci)001:2796: 'bem gyi grol ba ngo mi shes pas 'byung ba
NK035(ci)001:2797: rang dag tu song ba'i skyes bu rnams kyis ngo
NK035(ci)001:2798: bo ka dag gi snang ba'i sa bzung ba rab
NK035(ci)001:2799: tu gces so rang bzhin lhun grub kyi snang ba
NK035(ci)001:2800: med na skyes bu de sangs rgyas kyang thugs rjes
NK035(ci)001:2801: sems can gyi don byed mi nus pas rang bzhin
NK035(ci)001:2802: lhun grub kyi snang ba la goms shing ngo shes
NK035(ci)001:2803: par rab tu gces so de ltar skyes bus snang
NK035(ci)001:2804: ba rnam pa brgyad kyi don shes nas snang ba
NK035(ci)001:2805: 'di dag rnam par dag pa'i rtags dang ldan pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2806: gang zag ces bya'o 'gro drug 'khrul pa'i snang ba'i
NK035(ci)001:2807: dus na skyes bu rnams kyis 'di ltar shes par
NK035(ci)001:2808: bya'o snang ba mched par shes pa rnams kyi sgo
NK035(ci)001:2809: lnga'i rlung zad de rang dag pa'o snang ba thob
NK035(ci)001:2810: pa'i don shes pa'i skal ldan rnams kyi kha dog
NK035(ci)001:2811: dang dbyibs su 'dzin pa'i rlung zad de 'khrul pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2812: de nyid du shes pa'o snang ba nye bar thob
NK035(ci)001:2813: pa'i rnal 'byor pas ni nye bar len pa'i phung
NK035(ci)001:2814: por 'dzin pa'i rlung zad de sku phyag rgya chen
NK035(ci)001:2815: por grol lo de'i phyir na mched dang thob pa
NK035(ci)001:2816: nyer thob pa 'di dag rlung la brten pa'o mched
NK035(ci)001:2817: pa rtogs phyir grangs rlung zad phyag rgya chen por
NK035(ci)001:2818: rang grol ba'o thob pa'i sa ni spru zer phra
NK035(ci)001:2819: rlung stobs nyer thob pas ni bdag 'dzin grol zhes
NK035(ci)001:2820: so ye shes sgyu mar snang ba'i dus ni sku'i
NK035(ci)001:2821: snang ba tshom bu la mkhas par bya ba dang
NK035(ci)001:2822: thig le'i snang ba la mkhas par bya ba dang
NK035(ci)001:2823: ye shes kyi snang ba zer thag la mkhas par
NK035(ci)001:2824: bya ba dang 'od kyi snang ba dum bu la
NK035(ci)001:2825: mkhas par bya ba ni rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis
NK035(ci)001:2826: lam mthong ba la mkhas par bya ba ste de'i
NK035(ci)001:2827: phyir na sku dang thig le ye shes 'od 'di
NK035(ci)001:2828: dag rnams la su goms pa ye shes dag pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2829: lam zin pa'o zhes te lnga lnga zung du 'brel
NK035(ci)001:2830: ba'i tshe rang ngo gnad la dril ba gces 'phro
NK035(ci)001:2831: dang 'du dang 'gyur ba'i tshe rang gi shes pa
NK035(ci)001:2832: brtan pa gces snying khar zer thag shar ba'i tshe
NK035(ci)001:2833: gong gi yid ches bzung ba gces snang ba dum
NK035(ci)001:2834: bur shar ba'i tshe mkhas pas snang ba mched pa
NK035(ci)001:2835: bzung zhes pa'o rig pa mngon sum gyi snang ba
NK035(ci)001:2836: ni lus ngag gi snang ba bzlog la sngon du
NK035(ci)001:2837: 'gro ba'i rim ba la mkhas par bya'o nyams gong
NK035(ci)001:2838: nas gong du 'phel ba la snang ba'i tshad la
NK035(ci)001:2839: mkhas par bya'o chos nyid rang zad kyi rig pa
NK035(ci)001:2840: ngo bo ka dag gi 'dug sa shes par bya'o
NK035(ci)001:2841: de'i phyir na sgo dang yul dang gnad dang gsum
NK035(ci)001:2842: 'di gsum lam du gang byed pa 'byung ba rnams
NK035(ci)001:2843: las rang sar grol zhes so bde gshegs gdul bya'i
NK035(ci)001:2844: snang ba ni gang gi zhing khams mkhas pas dbyings
NK035(ci)001:2845: rnams la tshad zin pa dang gang gis sku yi
NK035(ci)001:2846: snang ba la mkhas pas bdag med rtogs pa dang
NK035(ci)001:2847: mdzad pa'i snang ba la mkhas pa dang sems can
NK035(ci)001:2848: gyi don la thogs pa med pa'o de'i phyir na
NK035(ci)001:2849: khams gsum pa dang mdzad pa la gang gis 'di
NK035(ci)001:2850: gsum mngon spyod na sangs rgyas sku gsum mngon du
NK035(ci)001:2851: shes zhes pas so 'khrul pa rang dag gi snang
NK035(ci)001:2852: ba ni dag pa'i sa'i snang ba la mkhas pas
NK035(ci)001:2853: phung po mya ngan las 'das pa'i don rtogs pa
NK035(ci)001:2854: dang dag pa dus kyi snang ba la mkhas pas
NK035(ci)001:2855: yul rnams mya ngan las 'das pa'i don rtogs pa
NK035(ci)001:2856: dang dag pa'i tshad la mkhas pas ni 'bras bu
NK035(ci)001:2857: mya ngan las 'das pa'i don rtogs pa dang de'i
NK035(ci)001:2858: phyir na sa dang tshad dang dus shes na snang
NK035(ci)001:2859: ba rnams la cid dgar rol zhes pa'o chos nyid
NK035(ci)001:2860: rang zad kyi dgongs pa ni zad pa'i dus la
NK035(ci)001:2861: mkhas pas 'byung ba rnams rang sar dag pa dang
NK035(ci)001:2862: zad pa'i lugs la mkhas pas sku dang ye shes
NK035(ci)001:2863: stong dang mi stong la sogs pa rnams rang sar
NK035(ci)001:2864: dag pa'o de'i phyir na dus dang lugs dang tshad
NK035(ci)001:2865: rnams kyis bla ma'i man ngag mthar phyin pa'o zhes
NK035(ci)001:2866: pa'o ngo bo ka dag gi snang ba ni ngo
NK035(ci)001:2867: bo'i snang ba la mkhas pas sku'i de bzhin nyid
NK035(ci)001:2868: ka nas dag pa dang rang bzhin gyi snang ba
NK035(ci)001:2869: la mkhas pas 'od dang thig le'i de bzhin nyid
NK035(ci)001:2870: rnam par dag pa dang thugs rje'i snang ba la
NK035(ci)001:2871: mkhas pas gzis sna thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK035(ci)001:2872: su ka nas dag pa'o de'i phyir na ngo bo
NK035(ci)001:2873: rang bzhin thugs rje yis byas pa'i don rnams chud
NK035(ci)001:2874: mi gson zhes pa'o rang bzhin lhun grub kyi snang
NK035(ci)001:2875: ba la mkhas pa ni 'char lugs kyi snang ba
NK035(ci)001:2876: la mkhas pas mtha' gang la'ang mi gnas par mya
NK035(ci)001:2877: ngan las 'das pa'o de'i phyir na 'char lugs thim
NK035(ci)001:2878: lugs grol lugs dang rang gi gding du chud pa'o
NK035(ci)001:2879: 'khrul pa rnams ni rang dag pa'o zhes so de
NK035(ci)001:2880: ltar na snang ba rnam pa brgyad kyi don skyes
NK035(ci)001:2881: bus nyams su myong nas sangs rgyas dang mnyam par
NK035(ci)001:2882: sbyor ba zhes bya'o snang ba rin po che'i pra
NK035(ci)001:2883: khrid ces bya ba mkhas pa bi ma la mu
NK035(ci)001:2884: tras dur khrod chen po rab tu snang byed du
NK035(ci)001:2885: mkha' 'gro bde ba'i yid can gyi don du mdzad
NK035(ci)001:2886: pa'o rdzogs so rgya gar gyi mkhas pa chen po
NK035(ci)001:2887: bi ma la mi tras sgra rang 'gyur du bsgyur
NK035(ci)001:2888: ba'o gu ru na mo yo gi dam pa sangs
NK035(ci)001:2889: rgyas kun gyi zhal mthong bdud rtsi'i ro ldan pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2890: ro langs bde ba bcom ldan lha yi lha mchog
NK035(ci)001:2891: nyid sangs rgyas sprul pa 'gro ba'i gdung ba sel
NK035(ci)001:2892: mdzad pa dam pa bdud rtsi bde ba nyid la
NK035(ci)001:2893: phyag 'tshal bstod dam pa de nyid rjes 'dzin sprul
NK035(ci)001:2894: pa'i sku nyon mongs rang dag mkhyen pa'i thugs dang
NK035(ci)001:2895: ldan gsung gi 'od kyis 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal gcod
NK035(ci)001:2896: dam pa yid bzhin myu gu de la phyag 'tshal
NK035(ci)001:2897: bstod dam pa'i gdung 'dzin mkhas pa sde snod rnams
NK035(ci)001:2898: kyi bdag thugs rje chen po'i sprul pa 'dzam gling
NK035(ci)001:2899: kun gyi rgyan dri med gsung mnga' 'gro ba ngal
NK035(ci)001:2900: gso'i gnas dam pa shes rab myu gu de la
NK035(ci)001:2901: phyag 'tshal bstod de rjes 'dzin pa'i mkhas pa 'jig
NK035(ci)001:2902: rten gsum gyis mgon rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa
NK035(ci)001:2903: bdag blo'i 'ching gcod pa tshangs pa'i gsung mnga' mkha'
NK035(ci)001:2904: 'gro kun gyi yid rab 'phrog dam pa bde ba'i
NK035(ci)001:2905: myu gu mgon la phyag 'tshal bstod bdag gis bla
NK035(ci)001:2906: ma rnams la bstod phul bas phyi rabs rjes su
NK035(ci)001:2907: 'jug pa'i rnal 'byor rnams yid ches dad pa'i mchog
NK035(ci)001:2908: tu 'di zung zhig gsang ba'i man ngag bdag gi
NK035(ci)001:2909: khog snying 'di rgya yis dpe las bod kyi yi
NK035(ci)001:2910: ger bsgyur bstan zhing bshad pa'i rje blon gnyis po
NK035(ci)001:2911: yang dam tshig gzhung dang ldan zhing dad ldan yang
NK035(ci)001:2912: snying gi man ngag mchog 'di blos ma thengs bstan
NK035(ci)001:2913: pa'i btsas su sa yi gter du sbas 'di nyid
NK035(ci)001:2914: nam zhig 'byung ba'i dus byung na skal ldan snying
NK035(ci)001:2915: gi bu dang 'phrad par shog mchims phu'i brag btsan
NK035(ci)001:2916: rdo rje drag po rtsal bka' 'di srungs la bstan
NK035(ci)001:2917: pa'i bdag po gyis chos skyong mgon po legs ldan
NK035(ci)001:2918: nag po khyod bka' 'di gtad do khyod kyis thub
NK035(ci)001:2919: par srungs smug nag khros ma'i rgyal mo sngags kyi
NK035(ci)001:2920: bdag bka' 'di bcol lo khyod kyis dam du zung
NK035(ci)001:2921: gal te dus min smon lam mtha' zad nas ban
NK035(ci)001:2922: 'dra dam nyams bdag gis 'di khyer na tshe la
NK035(ci)001:2923: bar chod srog la sbar gyi thob snying khrag gzogs
NK035(ci)001:2924: la mig 'bras thang la 'brul skal ldan snying gi
NK035(ci)001:2925: bu dang 'phrad pa'i tshe zhen pa spongs la de
NK035(ci)001:2926: yi stong grogs gyis des kyang rang rgyas thob la
NK035(ci)001:2927: sems la brnogs sa ma ya rgya rgya rgya na
NK035(ci)001:2929: aa &&&dapala bde ba chen po la phyag 'tshal lo
NK035(ci)001:2930: gsang ba yang zhun po ti smug chung la chos
NK035(ci)001:2931: kyi sde dang grangs ni gsal bya'i phyir gsang ba'i
NK035(ci)001:2932: de bas 'di lhag dang chad med par yid ches
NK035(ci)001:2933: 'jug phyir yi ge 'di la ltos bkod pa chen
NK035(ci)001:2934: po dum bu'i rgyud dag las skabs kyi don ni
NK035(ci)001:2935: rnam pa bcu gnyis yod rmongs pa gdung ba sel
NK035(ci)001:2936: ba yid ches lo rgyus bstan de nyid la ni
NK035(ci)001:2937: gzhung don bcu gnyis las zhus don dang pos ston
NK035(ci)001:2938: pa'i byon tshul bstan zhus don gnyis pas 'jug sgo
NK035(ci)001:2939: gsal bar byas gsum pas bshad bya 'bras bu'i don
NK035(ci)001:2940: tshig gis gzhung gi don la dbri gzhug med par
NK035(ci)001:2941: bstan bzhi pas chos kyi sde dang grangs rnams bstan
NK035(ci)001:2942: lnga pas don gyi gzhung rnams gsal bar bkod drug
NK035(ci)001:2943: pas snying gi rgyud rnams bsdus te bstan bdun pas
NK035(ci)001:2944: skal ldan phyi rabs lung yang bstan brgyad pas bstan
NK035(ci)001:2945: pa'i snying po'i byung khungs bstan dgu pas bstan pa
NK035(ci)001:2946: 'byung ba'i lung yang bstan bcu pas 'bras bu thob
NK035(ci)001:2947: pa'i grangs lung bstan bcu gcig ba dor sangs rgyas
NK035(ci)001:2948: 'byung tshul bstan bcu gnyis rang bzhin sprul skur dbugs
NK035(ci)001:2949: 'byin bstan de dag rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba'i
NK035(ci)001:2950: skabs don no skabs don gnyis pas sems nyid gtan
NK035(ci)001:2951: la phab gsum pa yis ni rgyud lung gsal bar
NK035(ci)001:2952: byas bzhi pa yis ni lha rnams mngon du bsgoms
NK035(ci)001:2953: lnga pa yis ni skye med man ngag bstan drug
NK035(ci)001:2954: pa yis ni chos sku gtan la phab bdun pa
NK035(ci)001:2955: yis ni 'khrul pa'i don rnams bstan brgyad pa yis
NK035(ci)001:2956: ni nyon mongs rang dag bstan dgu pa yis ni
NK035(ci)001:2957: lhag pa'i bsam gtan bstan bcu pa yis ni zhing
NK035(ci)001:2958: khams rang gnad bstan bcu gcig pas ni bya byed
NK035(ci)001:2959: lam du blangs bcu gnyis pas ni bkod pa yongs
NK035(ci)001:2960: rdzogs bstan de ltar skabs don bcu gnyis kyis bkod
NK035(ci)001:2961: pa chen po'i snying po rdzogs gces pa'i snying po
NK035(ci)001:2962: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen ma yis rang don gtan la
NK035(ci)001:2963: phab dpe yis sgron ma dga' rab rdo rje ma
NK035(ci)001:2964: yis gzhan don gtan la phab 'chi ba brtag pa
NK035(ci)001:2965: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen mas ni rang gzhan gnyis kyi
NK035(ci)001:2966: don 'chi ba bslu ba sh+r+ai sim ha mas ni
NK035(ci)001:2967: phal cher rang gi don ye shes mdo yis lta
NK035(ci)001:2968: ba'i snying pos 'bad med grol ba bstan bi ma
NK035(ci)001:2969: la yis rin chen pra khrid snang ba gtan la
NK035(ci)001:2970: phab de dag rnams kyis po ti smug chung rdzogs
NK035(ci)001:2971: gal te phyi ma'i dus kyi snyigs ma la man
NK035(ci)001:2972: ngag dum bu'i de bas mkhas pa bi ma las
NK035(ci)001:2973: mdzad pa rdzogs so las can gcig dang 'phrad par
NK035(ci)001:2974: shog dam pa sangs rgyas kun gyi gdung 'dzin pa'i
NK035(ci)001:2975: rgya gar mkhas pa lnga la bdag phyag 'tshal bdag
NK035(ci)001:2976: 'dra smyon pa lce btsun gyis sangs rgyas rnams kyi
NK035(ci)001:2977: thugs rje'i nyi ma 'di sngon nas sbyangs pa'i stobs
NK035(ci)001:2978: kyis bdag la gter rnams babs gsang ba'i rgyud lung
NK035(ci)001:2979: man ngag phyi mo rnams dam pa'i sprul pa ldang
NK035(ci)001:2980: mas bdag la gtad shin tu dkon pa'i man ngag
NK035(ci)001:2981: po ti bzhi mchims phu dge gong shar gyi pha
NK035(ci)001:2982: bong 'og lcags kyi snod du gdams pa bdag gis
NK035(ci)001:2983: bton khu lung gad steng khyi rtag dben rtsa nas
NK035(ci)001:2984: gnubs kyi ngan sngags brgya dang brgyad cu te shangs
NK035(ci)001:2985: dang rta nag 'dus pa'i ri yi zom spo mthon
NK035(ci)001:2986: rdza nas pad+ma'i chos rnams bton de ltar gter gyi
NK035(ci)001:2987: man ngag bka' 'dus pa'i man ngag kun gyi bdag
NK035(ci)001:2988: por bdag gyur te lung bstan pa bstan pa'i gnas
NK035(ci)001:2989: ma rnyed slar la sa yi 'og tu sba snyam
NK035(ci)001:2990: nas lung dang mthun pa'i gter kha lnga ru sbas
NK035(ci)001:2991: 'di dag nam zhig 'byung ba'i dus byung na skal
NK035(ci)001:2992: ldan lung bstan de dang 'phrad par shog zhwa yi
NK035(ci)001:2993: mgon po khyod kyis bka' 'di srungs rtse la byang
NK035(ci)001:2994: chub rgyal ba yum gyi lha khyod la gtad do
NK035(ci)001:2995: bka' 'di dam du zung zhes gsungs nas gter du
NK035(ci)001:2996: sbas so bdag gis 'di nas ji ltar 'dug pa
NK035(ci)001:2997: bzhin nyams su blangs pas grub pa yang de kho
NK035(ci)001:2998: na bzhin thob pa lags so sa ma ya na
NK035(ci)001:2999: ra kan rjes 'jug rnams kyis 'di ltar nyams su
NK035(ci)001:3000: longs shig 'di bzhin byas na 'tshang rgya ba la
NK035(ci)001:3001: the tshom yod re kan lce btsun bdag gi mgo
NK035(ci)001:3002: khos po ti 'di la 'dra min gnyis min pa
NK035(ci)001:3003: la yin byas pa gcig kyang yod 'di ni yang
NK035(ci)001:3004: dag pa'o dge bar gyur cig 'gro ba thams cad
NK035(ci)001:3005: kyi rgyud la snying po'i bstan pa rgyas pas grol
NK035(ci)001:3006: ba myur du thob par shog //
